#. Header for contraptions mvz2:dispenser
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid "发射器是你的第一道防线，它们发射箭来保卫你的房子。"
msgstr "Dispensers are your first line of defense. They shoot arrows at incoming enemies."

#. Properties for contraptions mvz2:dispenser
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid ""
"耐久：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_health\" /></color>\n"
"攻击间隔：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:AttackInterval\" />秒</color>\n"
"特点：<color=red>1/7概率发射紫箭</color>\n"
"伤害：<color=red>普通箭矢<var id=\"mvz2:entity_damage\" />，紫箭70+10(穿甲伤害)</color>\n"
"技能：<color=red>快速发射60支箭矢</color>"
msgstr ""
"Toughness: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_health\" /></color>\n"
"Attack Interval: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:AttackInterval\" /> seconds</color>\n"
"Special: <color=red>1/7 chance to fire a purple arrow</color>\n"
"Damage: <color=red>Normal arrow <var id=\"mvz2:entity_damage\" />, purple arrow 70+10  (Ignore Armor)</color>\n"
"Evocation: <color=red>Rapidly fires 60 arrows</color>"

#. Flavor for contraptions mvz2:dispenser
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid ""
"“有人问我为什么我能不需要红石就能发射箭，还有人问我为什么我能发射无数的箭。”发射器顿了一顿，“第一，我的栅栏连着一个脉冲，第二，我内部的"
"弓附有耐久450和无限I。啥？你问我为啥会说话？”"
msgstr ""
"\"People usually ask me how I can shoot an infinite amount of arrows, and without redstone,\" said Dispenser. \"First, my fence is "
"connected to a redstone pulse. Second, my bow is enchanted with Unbreaking III and Infinity. What? How can I talk?\""

#. Header for contraptions mvz2:furnace
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid "熔炉能为你提供额外的红石。"
msgstr "Furnaces are essential for you to generate extra redstone which can be converted to energy. Try placing as many as you can!"

#. Properties for contraptions mvz2:furnace
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid ""
"耐久：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_health\" /></color>\n"
"生产时间：<color=red>24秒</color>\n"
"提供能量：<color=red>红石<var id=\"mvz2:redstone_value\" /></color>\n"
"技能：<color=red>瞬间生成6枚红石</color>"
msgstr ""
"Toughness: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_health\" /></color>\n"
"Produce time: <color=red>24 seconds</color>\n"
"Energy production: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:redstone_value\" /></color>\n"
"Evocation: <color=red>Rapidly generates 6 redstones</color>"

#. Flavor for contraptions mvz2:furnace
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid ""
"有人闲得慌在它下面安装了一个连着矿场的投掷器。哦，这个矿场是靠地热能的。\n"
"<color=grey>精准采集是这样用的？</color>\n"
"呃...别问为什么在水上或者甲板上也能有源源不断的红石供应了，你就当做是伟大的红石神赐给了熔炉一块永远烧不完的"
"<ref=[contraptions]mvz2:RedStoneOre>红石矿</ref>、伟大的煤炭神赐给了熔炉一块永远烧不完的煤炭吧。\n"
"<color=grey>精准采集是你这样用的？？？</color>"
msgstr ""
"Someone bored installed a dispenser connected to a mine beneath it. Oh, and that mine is geothermal-powered.\n"
"<color=grey>So this is how you use Silk Touch?</color>\n"
"Uh... Don't ask why there's an endless supply of redstone even when it's on water or a deck. Just pretend the great Redstone God "
"blessed the furnace with a never-burning <ref=[contraptions]mvz2:RedStoneOre>Redstone Ore</ref>, and the great Coal God blessed the "
"furnace with a never-burning piece of coal.\n"
"<color=grey>Is THIS how you're supposed to use Silk Touch???</color>"

#. Header for contraptions mvz2:obsidian
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid "黑曜石的强力装甲能够抵御敌人的攻击，受损时发射黑曜石碎片"
msgstr "Obsidian's powerful armor can withstand enemy attacks. When damaged, it launches Obsidian Shards."

#. Properties for contraptions mvz2:obsidian
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid ""
"耐久：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_health\" /></color>\n"
"伤害：<color=red>每受到100伤害发射一枚49+1(穿甲)伤害的黑曜石碎片</color>\n"
"技能：<color=red>获得下界合金装甲，耐久提高至10000</color>"
msgstr ""
"Toughness: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_health\" /></color>\n"
"Damage: <color=red>Launches one Obsidian Shard dealing 49+1 (Ignore Armor) damage for every 100 damage taken</color>\n"
"Skill: <color=red>Gains Netherite Armor, increasing Toughness to 10000</color>"

#. Flavor for contraptions mvz2:obsidian
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid ""
"听说把黑曜石摆成地狱门的形状再放一个<ref=[contraptions]mvz2:soul_furnace>灵魂熔炉</ref>有惊喜。不如试试看？\n"
"不知道<ref=[contraptions]mvz2:soul_furnace>灵魂熔炉</ref>是什么？接着推关吧！\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"I heard that if you arrange Obsidian into the shape of a Nether portal and place a <ref=[contraptions]mvz2:soul_furnace>Soul Furnace</"
"ref> inside, something surprising happens. Why not give it a try?\n"
"Don't know what a <ref=[contraptions]mvz2:soul_furnace>Soul Furnace</ref> is? Keep playing to find out!\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"

#. Flavor for contraptions mvz2:obsidian
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid ""
"没成功的话可以试一下用不同框架的黑曜石，比方说<ref=[contraptions]mvz2:GlowingObsidian>发光的黑曜石</ref>，"
"<ref=[contraptions]mvz2:CryingObsidian>哭泣的黑曜石</ref>。\n"
"没有这些黑曜石？那就去推关收集啊！\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"If it doesn't work, try using different types of Obsidian, such as <ref=[contraptions]mvz2:GlowingObsidian>Glowing Obsidian</ref> or "
"<ref=[contraptions]mvz2:CryingObsidian>Crying Obsidian</ref>.\n"
"Don't have these kinds of Obsidian? Then keep playing to collect them!\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"

#. Flavor for contraptions mvz2:obsidian
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid ""
"还没成功的？那就尝试使用<ref=[contraptions]mvz2:hellfire>地狱火</ref>！\n"
"不知道<ref=[contraptions]mvz2:hellfire>地狱火</ref>是什么？接着推关！"
msgstr ""
"Still no luck? Then try using <ref=[contraptions]mvz2:hellfire>Hellfire</ref>!\n"
"Don't know what <ref=[contraptions]mvz2:hellfire>Hellfire</ref> is? Keep playing!"

#. Flavor for contraptions mvz2:obsidian
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid ""
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"恭喜你被耍了"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"Congratulations, you've been tricked."

#. Header for contraptions mvz2:mine_tnt
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid "地雷TNT在一定时间的准备后能够炸飞接近的敌人。"
msgstr "Mine TNTs blow up nearby enemy monsters, but they need a while to arm themselves."

#. Properties for contraptions mvz2:mine_tnt
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid ""
"耐久：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_health\" /></color>\n"
"准备时间：<color=red>15秒</color>\n"
"伤害：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_damage\" /></color>\n"
"半径：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:FireRange\" />格</color>\n"
"技能：<color=red>立即准备完毕，并向最前方投掷两个新的地雷TNT</color>"
msgstr ""
"Toughness: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_health\" /></color>\n"
"Time to arm: <color=red>15 seconds</color>\n"
"Damage: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_damage\" /></color>\n"
"Radius: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:FireRange\" /> blocks</color>\n"
"Evocation: <color=red>Instantly arm itself, then place two copies of itself on the rightmost column</color>"

#. Flavor for contraptions mvz2:mine_tnt
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid "地雷TNT为什么需要时间来填装？这的确是个千古难题。如果它能瞬间出来的话那还怕什么呢？但在它看来，这件事挺正常的：“老娘在睡觉！”"
msgstr ""
"Why does Mine TNT need time to arm itself? It's been an enigma for years. What could ever go wrong if it could be instantly armed? "
"Though it finds this pretty reasonable. “I was sleeping!”"

#. Header for contraptions mvz2:Poisonser
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid "蚀毒发射器能发射短距离的毒球。"
msgstr "Poisonser can shoot short-ranged snowballs."

#. Properties for contraptions mvz2:Poisonser
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid ""
"射程：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:FireRange\" />格</color>\n"
"伤害：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_damage\" />，蚀毒效果30/s，持续5s</color>\n"
"技能：<color=red>射出一个越滚越大的毒球</color>"
msgstr ""
"Range: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:FireRange\" /> blocks</color>\n"
"Damage: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_damage\" />, Corropoison effect 30/s for 5 seconds</color>\n"
"Skill: <color=red>Fires a poison ball that grows larger as it rolls</color>"

#. Flavor for contraptions mvz2:Poisonser
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid ""
"染了毒，别问了。\n"
"你知道的，亡灵生物不受中毒效果伤害，所以这不是普通的毒。\n"
"<color=green>这是蚀毒</color>"
msgstr ""
"It's poisoned, don't ask.\n"
"You know, undead mobs take no damage from Poison, so this isn't ordinary poison.\n"
"<color=green>It's Corropoison</color>"

#. Header for contraptions mvz2:moonlight_sensor
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid "月光传感器可以在晚上提供能量，并在一段时间后提升生产量。"
msgstr "Moonlight Sensors provide energy at night, and increase the yield after a while."

#. Properties for contraptions mvz2:moonlight_sensor
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid ""
"提供能量：<color=red>2点/1.6秒，而后2点/1秒</color>\n"
"技能：<color=red>立即升级，<tag id=\"mvz2:light_source\" />发出蓝光，并使生产量变为2倍</color>"
msgstr ""
"Energy production: <color=red>1/1.6 secs, then 1/1 sec</color>\n"
"Evocation: <color=red>Instantly upgrade, <tag id=\"mvz2:light_source\" />glow with blue light and increase its yield by 2 times</color>"

#. Flavor for contraptions mvz2:moonlight_sensor
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid ""
"有时候你们也许很好奇为什么一开始它不是日光传感器，我也可以告诉你：其实月光传感只是它的兼职，只不过它太喜欢这份工作了。\n"
"他本想放置后立刻倒贴给你们25机械能的，但一个声音拦住了他：\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"你并未氪金，所以并不强大，等未来你氪金买了秘籍再说罢"
msgstr ""
"Maybe you're wondering why it isn't a Daylight Sensor in the first place. I can tell you: moonlight sensing is just its side job, but "
"it loves this job too much.\n"
"It wanted to give you 25 ME right after being placed, but a voice stopped it:\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"You haven't paid to win, so you're not strong enough. Come back after you buy the secret manual with real money."

#. Header for contraptions mvz2:glowstone
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid "荧石发出的光芒能驱散迷雾，并发现周围的<ref=[enemies]mvz2:ghost>幽灵</ref>。"
msgstr "The light of Glowstones can clear fog and reveal <ref=[enemies]mvz2:ghost>ghosts</ref>."

#. Properties for contraptions mvz2:glowstone
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid ""
"照明半径：<color=red>1.5格</color>\n"
"特点：<color=red>放置时眩晕敌人3.33秒</color>\n"
"技能：<color=red>眩晕所有敌人7秒，清除器械的精神控制状态</color>"
msgstr ""
"Light Radius: <color=red>1.5 blocks</color>\n"
"Special: <color=red>Stuns enemies for 3.33 seconds when placed</color>\n"
"Evocation: <color=red>Stun all enemies for 7 seconds, remove mind control status from contraptions</color>"

#. Flavor for contraptions mvz2:glowstone
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid ""
"上帝说：要有光，所以诞生了火把。上帝说：要有固态光，所以诞生了荧石。上帝说：要有可开关的固态光，所以诞生了红石灯。上帝说：好吧我编不下"
"去了。"
msgstr ""
"And God said, “Let there be light,” and there were torches. Then God said, “Let there be solid light,” and there were Glowstones. And "
"then God said, “Let there be switchable solid light,” and there were Redstone Lamps. Finally God said…okay I don’t know how to "
"continue this joke."

#. Header for contraptions mvz2:punchton
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid "冲击活塞能够击退前方的敌人并击碎<tag id=\"mvz2:shell\" enum=\"mvz2:stone\" />石制品，但之后需要一定时间来修复自身。"
msgstr ""
"Punchtons can knock back enemy monsters and crush <tag id=\"mvz2:shell\" enum=\"mvz2:stone\"/>hard objects, but they need time to "
"repair themselves after that."

#. Properties for contraptions mvz2:punchton
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid ""
"伤害：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_damage\" />（无视护甲）</color>\n"
"修复时间：<color=red>20秒</color>\n"
"技能：<color=red>对前方的所有敌人造成500点伤害，并将其击退至最右侧</color>"
msgstr ""
"Damage: <color=red>100 (Ignore Armors)</color>\n"
"Time to repair: <color=red>20 seconds</color>\n"
"Evocation: <color=red>Deal 500 damage to all enemies in front and knock back them to the rightest</color>"

#. Flavor for contraptions mvz2:punchton
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid ""
"这本来会是一条非常具有冲击性的描述，可惜它目前还在进行修复。\n"
"推过足够多关卡以修复！"
msgstr ""
"This description would have packed a punch, but unfortunately, it is still under repair.\n"
"Clear enough levels to fix it!"

#. Flavor for contraptions mvz2:punchton
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid ""
"冲击活塞不爱与其他人打交道，因为他总是喜欢将别人从自己身边弹开。他不喜欢朋友，真的，他自己也不需要。因为在他的心中，只有依靠自己才能完"
"全将自己的力量完全爆发出来。"
msgstr ""
"Punchtons doesn't like to be with others. He always pushes them away. He doesn't like friends,he doesn't need friends after all. Only "
"by relying on himself can it completely demonstrate it's power."

#. Header for contraptions mvz2:tnt
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid "TNT在触发后能炸飞周围的敌人。"
msgstr "TNTs blow up nearby enemies after being triggered."

#. Properties for contraptions mvz2:tnt
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid ""
"伤害：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_damage\" /></color>\n"
"半径：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:FireRange\" />格</color>\n"
"技能：<color=red>炸出4个TNT分身</color>"
msgstr ""
"Damage: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_damage\" /></color>\n"
"Radius: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:FireRange\" /> blocks</color>\n"
"Evocation: <color=red>Blast into 4 flying copies of itself that explode on impact</color>"

#. Flavor for contraptions mvz2:tnt
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid ""
"注意：并不能用于治疗设备尔的核心病，以及在一百年后因为能够治疗核心病而获得设备尔奖。\n"
"\n"
"<color=grey>TNT需要火药来合成，但是现实中TNT和火药没有半毛钱关系。为什么呢？</color>\n"
"<color=grey>那要谈到当年纳赤创造世界......简单来讲notch以为炸药中黄色的粉末是沙子，其他的部分是火药，于是mc的tnt合成表就这样了。</"
"color>\n"
"\n"
"<color=grey>相当有迈恩克拉夫特特色</color>"
msgstr ""
"Note: It cannot be used to cure the Devicer's Core Disease, yet a hundred years later it will win a Devicer Prize for being able to do "
"exactly that.\n"
"\n"
"<color=grey>TNT requires gunpowder to craft, but in reality, TNT and gunpowder have nothing to do with each other. Why is that?</"
"color>\n"
"<color=grey>Well, it goes back to when Notch created the world... Simply put, Notch thought the yellow powder in explosives was sand, "
"and the rest was gunpowder, and that's how Minecraft's TNT recipe came to be.</color>\n"
"\n"
"<color=grey>Quite Minecraft-y indeed.</color>"

#. Header for contraptions mvz2:soul_furnace
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid "灵魂熔炉发射恐怖的<tag id=\"mvz2:fire\" />灵魂火，但需要提供燃料。"
msgstr "Soul Furnaces shoot terrifying <tag id=\"mvz2:fire\"/>soulfires, but will burn the contraption in the front as its fuel."

#. Properties for contraptions mvz2:soul_furnace
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid ""
"伤害：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_damage\" /></color>\n"
"溅射伤害：<color=red><var local=\"splash_damage\" />（不伤害直接目标）</color>\n"
"特点：<color=red>需要烧毁本格的器械补充燃料</color>\n"
"燃料上限：<color=red>60</color>\n"
"技能：<color=red>消耗所有燃料，每有一发燃料被消耗，便随机对一个敌人发射爆炸灵魂火球，单次技能时间过长会导致不分敌我的自爆</color>"
msgstr ""
"Damage: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_damage\" /></color>\n"
"Splash Damage: <color=red><var local=\"splash_damage\" /> (does not harm the primary target)</color>\n"
"Special: <color=red>Requires burning contraptions on its own tile to refuel</color>\n"
"Fuel Capacity: <color=red>60</color>\n"
"Evocation: <color=red>Consumes all fuel. For each unit of fuel consumed, fires an explosive soul fireball at a random enemy. If the "
"Evocation lasts too long, it will self-destruct, harming both enemies and allies</color>"

#. Flavor for contraptions mvz2:soul_furnace
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid ""
"灵魂熔炉里面到底烧的什么？是罪人的灵魂吗？还是地狱的矿渣？别想太多，它只是个南瓜灯。\n"
"\n"
"<color=grey>据野史记载：灵魂熔炉曾经也是个异性恋，她的女朋友是<ref=[contraptions]mvz2:furnace>熔炉</ref>，但自从她跟了"
"<ref=[contraptions]mvz2:dispenser>发射器</ref>以后就开始FFF了。</color>\n"
"<color=grey>我没用错性别代词....呃，大概吧。</color>"
msgstr ""
"What exactly is burning inside the Soul Furnace? The souls of sinners? Or infernal slag? Don't overthink it. It's just a Jack "
"o'Lantern.\n"
"\n"
"<color=grey>According to unofficial historical records: the Soul Furnace used to be straight. Its girlfriend was the "
"<ref=[contraptions]mvz2:furnace>Furnace</ref>, but after it left her for the <ref=[contraptions]mvz2:dispenser>Dispenser</ref>, it "
"went full FFF.</color>\n"
"<color=grey>I didn't misgender it.... uh, probably.</color>"

#. Header for contraptions mvz2:silvenser
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid "银制发射器能发射穿透<tag id=\"mvz2:shell\" enum=\"mvz2:flesh\" />血肉之躯的飞刀。"
msgstr "Silvensers shoot piercing knives which can slice <tag id=\"mvz2:shell\" enum=\"mvz2:flesh\"/>the flesh."

#. Properties for contraptions mvz2:silvenser
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid ""
"伤害：<color=red>蓝色飞刀25，红色飞刀50，飞刀对肉体伤害*2</color>\n"
"特点：<color=red>1/7概率发射红色飞刀，蓝色飞刀可以穿透多个敌人，但无法穿透硬物</color>\n"
"技能：<color=red>以至多10个敌人为中心创造飞刀圈，数秒后飞刀开始飞行</color>"
msgstr ""
"Damage: <color=red>Blue Knife: 25, Red Knife: 50, Knives deal 2x damage to flesh</color>\n"
"Special: <color=red>1/7 chance to fire a Red Knife. Blue Knives can pierce multiple enemies, but cannot pierce hard objects</color>\n"
"Evocation: <color=red>Creates a knife circle centered on up to 10 enemies. The knives begin flying after a few seconds</color>"

#. Flavor for contraptions mvz2:silvenser
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid ""
"银制发射器其实是个JOJO迷，飞刀则是他最擅长的把戏。他喜欢JOJO里面的各种台词、各种替身。有时候他也会模仿里面的姿势——尽管他没有手。\n"
"以下是他表演的舞台剧片段：\n"
"\"发发，我从人生中学到了一件事情，发射器越是发射箭矢，就越会感到无力，除非超越箭矢……\"\"你到底想说什么！\"\"我不发射箭了，发发！\"\n"
"\n"
"有趣的是，虽然他是JOJO厨，但他的这套衣服参考了红警里的G.I."
msgstr ""
"The Silver Dispenser is actually a huge JOJO fan. Throwing knives is his specialty. He loves all the catchphrases and Stands from "
"JOJO. Sometimes he even strikes poses from the show — even though he doesn't have hands.\n"
"\n"
"Here's a clip from his stage play:\n"
"\"DiDi, I've learned one thing in life... The more arrows a dispenser fires, the more powerless it becomes — unless it transcends "
"arrows...\" \"What are you trying to say?!\" \"I reject my arrows, DiDi!\"\n"
"\n"
"Interestingly, even though he's a JOJO fan, his outfit is actually inspired by the G.I. from Red Alert."

#. Header for contraptions mvz2:magichest
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid "魔术箱在吞掉前面的怪物后会变成一个<ref=[misc]mvz2:starshard.magic_candy>星之碎片</ref>。"
msgstr "Magichests transform into a <ref=[misc]mvz2:starshard.magic_candy>Starshard</ref> after devouring an enemy."

#. Properties for contraptions mvz2:magichest
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid "技能：<color=red>召唤一个<ref=[enemies]mvz2:ghast>恶魂</ref>，用以纪念@厨师海绵宝宝 之前做过的一个游戏</color>"
msgstr "Evocation: <color=red>Summon a <ref=[enemies]mvz2:ghast>Ghast</ref> to memorialize a game my good friend made before</color>"

#. Flavor for contraptions mvz2:magichest
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid ""
"它只需要挂上一个招牌，写上YMCA，僵尸们就自投罗网了。YMCA是什么意思？当然是“有馍吃啊”。\n"
"魔术箱曾经在戏班子里学过一点魔术。后来它入了东方，便开始以克劳恩皮斯为本命。他穿上了克劳恩皮斯的衣服，自己也变得像个小丑一样。当然他最"
"近准备想向幽幽子学习，于是变成了这副样子。\n"
"学就学吧，但我说箱子你别特么再吃<ref=[enemies]mvz2:bone_wall>骨墙</ref>了，<ref=[enemies]mvz2:mutant_zombie>突变僵尸</"
"ref><ref=[enemies]mvz2:hell_chariot>地狱战车</ref>一样能吃饱！"
msgstr ""
"It only needs to hang up a sign that says \"YMCA\", and the zombies will fall right into its trap. What does YMCA mean? Of course it "
"means \"You Munch, Chest Absorbs\".\n"
"\n"
"The Magic Chest once learned some magic from a traveling troupe. Later, it got into Touhou and took Clownpiece as its true idol. It "
"put on Clownpiece's clothes and started looking like a clown itself. Lately, it's been thinking about learning from Yuyuko, which is "
"why it's ended up looking like this.\n"
"\n"
"Go ahead and learn, but hey, Chest, could you please stop eating those <ref=[enemies]mvz2:bone_wall>Bone Walls</ref>? "
"<ref=[enemies]mvz2:mutant_zombie>Mutant Zombies</ref> and <ref=[enemies]mvz2:hell_chariot>Hell Chariots</ref> can fill you up just "
"fine!"

#. Header for contraptions mvz2:lily_pad
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid "睡莲允许你在水上放置器械。"
msgstr "Lily Pads allow you to place non-aquatic contraptions on water."

#. Properties for contraptions mvz2:lily_pad
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid "技能：<color=red>在3x3范围内的水中召唤分身</color>"
msgstr "Evocation: <color=red>Summon copies on 3x3 water tiles</color>"

#. Flavor for contraptions mvz2:lily_pad
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid ""
"“不要叫我‘莉莉胸垫’！”\n"
"\n"
"以及睡莲和睡觉前面的睡真的不是动词。\n"
"\n"
"嗯，继古明地 觉被不断迫害后，我们又迎来了宇佐见 莲子。"
msgstr ""
"\"I'm Lily Pad, not a pad!\"\n"
"\n"
"By the way, Lily is not a person.\n"
"\n"
"\"Why are you making me a gift for Sakuya?! I am NOT a lily chest pad!\""

#. Header for contraptions mvz2:drivenser
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid "在一个驱动发射器上再放置一个驱动发射器，可以增加它每次发射的箭的数量。"
msgstr "Place another Drivenser on an existing one to increase the number of arrows per shot."

#. Properties for contraptions mvz2:drivenser
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid ""
"攻击间隔：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:AttackInterval\" />秒</color>\n"
"伤害：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_damage\" /></color>\n"
"升级上限：<color=red>5</color>\n"
"技能：<color=red>发射五支大箭矢</color>"
msgstr ""
"Fire rate: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:AttackInterval\" /> seconds</color>\n"
"Damage: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_damage\" /></color>\n"
"Max Level: <color=red>5</color>\n"
"Evocation: <color=red>Shoot 5 large arrows</color>"

#. Flavor for contraptions mvz2:drivenser
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid ""
"驱动发射器是个技术宅，同时它还懂得电脑驱动的装配、各种软件、硬件的性能以及编程语言等信息技术。最近他想自己编程一个游戏来还原这场与僵尸"
"之间的战争，但有人已经抢先了。\n"
"于是他打算做个扩充这场战争细节的模组，也被人抢先了。\n"
"他现在打算做随机模组去。"
msgstr ""
"Drivenser is a tech nerd. It knows how to assemble a computer, the performance of various software and hardware, as well as "
"programming languages and other IT knowledge. Recently, it wanted to code a game to recreate this war against the zombies, but someone "
"had already beaten it to it.\n"
"\n"
"So it decided to make an EXPAND mod that adds more detail to the war — but someone had beaten it to that too.\n"
"\n"
"Now it's planning to make a Random mod instead."

#. Header for contraptions mvz2:gravity_pad
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid "重力板能够降低上方子弹的高度并能让它上面的敌人无法跳跃。"
msgstr "Gravity Pads can lower the height of medium height objects above it, and make enemy monsters on it unable to climb or jump."

#. Properties for contraptions mvz2:gravity_pad
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid ""
"特点：<color=red>能够减速在它上方的怪物并加大他们受到的重力、能够降低上方子弹的高度。</color>\n"
"技能：<color=red>移除场上所有飞行怪物的飞行能力，召唤从天而降的铁砧，砸伤敌人并阻挡怪物们前进</color>"
msgstr ""
"Special: <color=red>Slows down monsters above it, increases gravity affecting them, and reduces the height of projectiles passing over "
"it.</color>\n"
"Evocation: <color=red>Removes the ability to fly from all flying monsters on the field, summons anvils falling from the sky to damage "
"enemies and block their advance.</color>"

#. Flavor for contraptions mvz2:gravity_pad
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid "重力板喜欢坐在苹果树下并分析为什么这个世界完全不尊重重力。"
msgstr "Gravity Plate likes sitting under an apple tree and analyzing why this world has absolutely no respect for gravity."

#. Flavor for contraptions mvz2:gravity_pad
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid ""
"有时<ref=[contraptions]mvz2:AntiGravityPad>反重力板</ref>会坐在他的脸上，让他释然这个世界为什么不尊重重力。\n"
"Bgm：关羽之歌"
msgstr ""
"Sometimes the <ref=[contraptions]mvz2:AntiGravityPad>Anti-Gravity Pad</ref> sits on his face, making him realize why this world has no "
"respect for gravity.\n"
"BGM: Song of Guan Yu"

#. Flavor for contraptions mvz2:gravity_pad
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid ""
"<ref=[contraptions]mvz2:force_pad>传动力板</ref>有时会坐在<ref=[contraptions]mvz2:AntiGravityPad>反重力板</ref>的脸上，让承受了两份力的"
"他不想要重力了。\n"
"Bgm：大石碎胸口"
msgstr ""
"Sometimes the <ref=[contraptions]mvz2:force_pad>Force Pad</ref> sits on the face of the <ref=[contraptions]mvz2:AntiGravityPad>Anti-"
"Gravity Pad</ref>, making him, who's already bearing double the force, no longer want gravity at all.\n"
"BGM: Smashing a Boulder on the Chest"

#. Flavor for contraptions mvz2:gravity_pad
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid ""
"\n"
"目前还没有掉落的苹果的样子。"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"No sign of any fallen apples yet."

#. Flavor for contraptions mvz2:gravity_pad
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid ""
"\n"
"突然一个苹果掉到了它头上，然后它就扁了——那是个<ref=[contraptions]mvz2:golden_apple>金苹果</ref>。"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"when all of a sudden an apple fell on its head, smashing it flat - it was a <ref=[contraptions]mvz2:golden_apple>Golden Apple</ref>."

#. Header for contraptions mvz2:vortex_hopper
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid "漩涡漏斗在旋转时会把接近它的所有怪物拖入水底。"
msgstr "Vortex Hoppers drag all monsters close to it underwater when spinning."

#. Properties for contraptions mvz2:vortex_hopper
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid "技能：<color=red>将更大范围的敌人拉入水底</color>"
msgstr "Evocation: <color=red>Drag enemy monsters in a wider range underwater</color>"

#. Flavor for contraptions mvz2:vortex_hopper
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid "漩涡漏斗是键山雏的大Fans，因此它常常喜欢学着像她一样旋转。它最喜欢的一首歌是《旋转吧，雪月花》。他无聊的时候经常把自己当陀螺抽。"
msgstr ""
"Vortex Hopper is a big fan of Kagiyama Hina, so he always spins like her. His favorite song is \"Maware! Setsugetsuka\". When he's "
"bored, By the way, he is usually spinned as a top......"

#. Header for contraptions mvz2:pistenser
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid "活塞发射器能够伸长自己来攻击高处的敌人。"
msgstr "Pistensers can stretch themselves to attack enemies in the air."

#. Properties for contraptions mvz2:pistenser
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid ""
"攻击间隔：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:AttackInterval\" />秒</color>\n"
"伤害：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_damage\" /></color>\n"
"特点：<color=red>能够攻击高处的敌人，尖刺能够穿透3个敌人</color>\n"
"技能：<color=red>向至多10个敌人发射穿甲的巨型尖刺</color>"
msgstr ""
"Fire rate: <color=red>1.5 seconds</color>\n"
"Damage: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_damage\" /></color>\n"
"Special: <color=red>Can attack enemies on air, spikes pierce through 3 enemies</color>\n"
"Evocation: <color=red>Shoots giant armor-piercing spikes at up to 10 enemies</color>"

#. Flavor for contraptions mvz2:pistenser
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid ""
"活塞发射器曾经有一段不光彩的历史，那时候他的头顶有个绿色的斑，于是他的朋友就嘲笑他是绿帽子。现在他把那一块换成了针刺球的发射口，顺便开"
"了一下脑洞。他一直很满意这个头型，直到他有一天被水淹没……\n"
"此外，他的头其实可以伸的非常长，甚至能达到直升机飞行的高度。\n"
"……你问我怎么知道是直升机飞行的高度？"
msgstr ""
"Pitsenser used to have a shameful history. At that time, there's a green spot on the top of his head, so his friends mocked him for a "
"green hat. Now he's changed that spot to the launch port of needle balls, made a hole on his head in passing. He's always been pleased "
"until he was flooded....\n"
"\"It's over zombies, I have the high ground!\" Those were his last words before a Ghast burns his leg- uhh, neck off."

#. Flavor for contraptions mvz2:pistenser
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid "问<ref=[contraptions]mvz2:AntiGravityPad>反重力板</ref>，他能给出实证。"
msgstr "Ask the <ref=[contraptions]mvz2:AntiGravityPad>Anti-Gravity Pad</ref>. He can give you empirical proof."

#. Flavor for contraptions mvz2:pistenser
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid ""
"现在，活塞发射器遇到了他的一生之敌：<ref=[enemies]mvz2:RaiderSkull>奇袭者头颅</ref>。\n"
"这家伙飞的还比直升机高！"
msgstr ""
"Now, Pitsenser has met his arch-nemesis: the <ref=[enemies]mvz2:RaiderSkull>Raider Skull</ref>.\n"
"This guy flies even higher than a helicopter!"

#. Header for contraptions mvz2:totenser
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid "图腾发射器在发射飞镖的同时还会喷火烧伤近处的敌人。"
msgstr "Totensers shoot poisonous darts and burn nearby enemies with <tag id=\"mvz2:fire\"/>fire."

#. Properties for contraptions mvz2:totenser
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid ""
"攻击间隔：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:AttackInterval\" />秒</color>\n"
"伤害：<color=red>15（飞镖），20/秒（火焰），45（毒液球），30/秒（中毒效果）</color>\n"
"特点：<color=red>1/5概率发射毒液球，飞镖上的箭毒会让僵尸肌肉松弛而无法造成伤害</color>\n"
"技能：<color=red>投出穿透敌人的长矛，并留下使敌人虚弱的毒雾轨迹</color>"
msgstr ""
"Fire rate: <color=red>1.5 seconds</color>\n"
"Damage: <color=red>15 (dart), 20/sec (fire), 45 (venom ball), 30/sec (poison effect)</color>\n"
"Special: <color=red>1/5 chance to fire a corropoison ball. Poison on its dart makes <tag id=\"mvz2:shell\" enum=\"mvz2:flesh\" /> "
"monsters deal no damage</color>\n"
"Evocation: <color=red>Throws a spear which pierces through enemies, and leaves a trail of weakening poison mist</color>"

#. Flavor for contraptions mvz2:totenser
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid ""
"图腾发射器兄弟俩来自于印第安部落，它们兄弟两个目前在一个马戏团进行杂耍，上面的那个射出的飞镖能准确的命中495米以外女仆头上的苹果树上的猴"
"子，下面的那位经常把对面的火圈里的狮子烤熟……最近它们又在开始庆祝什么“窝舞安曲安布回印第安宇”节日……\n"
"图腾发射器信仰什么？依据器械智能的历史，它们可能信仰的是各种机械神灵。也有人说它们信仰造出机械的人类发明家，甚至也有说法称其信仰机械古"
"神。人们的讨论已经有百年之久，但实际上，它们只信仰自己的纸片人老婆。\n"
"\n"
"<color=grey>这对兄弟，真是一对笑面虎，两头乌角鲨。</color>"
msgstr ""
"Totenser is a dude coming from an Indian clan...or dudes? They are now joggling at a circus. The top guy is able to shoot a monkey on "
"an apple tree above a maid 495 metres away, while the bottom one can burn lions which are at the opposite side of the fire ring to "
"death. Recently they are celebrating some kind of \"Onnianabianindiu\" festival\n"
"What is Totenser’s belief? According to the history of contraption intelligence, it may believe in various mechanical deities. Some "
"say that it actually prays to the human inventors who created machines, and some even say that it believes in the mechanical elder "
"gods. People's discussion went on for a whole century, but the truth is, it just put its faith in its waifus."

#. Header for contraptions mvz2:dream_crystal
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid "梦境结晶会慢慢地恢复自己的生命。"
msgstr "Dream Crystals slowly regenerate their health."

#. Properties for contraptions mvz2:dream_crystal
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid ""
"耐久：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_health\" /></color>\n"
"恢复速度：<color=red>80/秒</color>\n"
"技能：<color=red>进入无敌状态，并为周围的器械恢复耐久</color>"
msgstr ""
"Toughness: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_health\" /></color>\n"
"Regeneration: <color=red>80/s</color>\n"
"Evocation: <color=red>Become invincible, regenerate toughness for surrounding contraptions</color>"

#. Flavor for contraptions mvz2:dream_crystal
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid ""
"化学课就像是：\n"
"“梦境结晶（Dream Crystal）是一种粉色，半透明并具有再生功效的水晶，主要组成成分为二氧化梦（化学式为DrO2），可用于与硫酸鑩（NmSO4）提炼二"
"氧化鑩（NmO2），是制作噩梦醇（Marenol）的重覀原木才米……~~——~zzzzZZZZ”"
msgstr ""
"\"Hi, this is Villager from Gear Ear Mech Co, and I'll show you the super strong, zombie-proof crystal, that can instantly patch, "
"bond, seal and repair! Dream Crystal is no ordinary crystal. Leaky contraptions can cause MAJOR DAMAGE, but Dream Crystal grips on "
"tight and bonds instantly. Plus, Dream Crystal is so strong, it even works underwater! To show you the power of Dream Crystal, I SAWED "
"THIS OBSIDIAN IN HALF, and repaired it with ONLY Dream Crystal!\""

#. Header for contraptions mvz2:dream_silk
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid "美梦丝能够让一个器械陷入沉睡，醒来后出现一个<ref=[misc]mvz2:starshard.lucid_dream>星之碎片</ref>。"
msgstr "Dream Silk makes a contraption fall asleep. After it wakes up, a <ref=[misc]mvz2:starshard.lucid_dream>Starshard</ref> appear."

#. Properties for contraptions mvz2:dream_silk
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid ""
"特点：<color=red>一次性使用</color>\n"
"技能：<color=red>无</color>\n"
"睡眠时间：<color=red>50秒</color>"
msgstr ""
"Special: <color=red>Single use</color>\n"
"Evocation: <color=red>None</color>\n"
"Sleep duration: <color=red>50 seconds</color>"

#. Flavor for contraptions mvz2:dream_silk
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid "美梦丝是个睡货，她每天睁开眼睛做的第一件事就是睡觉。瞧瞧她睡的，把自己的冷却时间也给睡短了。"
msgstr ""
"Dream Silk is a sleepy one. The first thing it does after waking up is sleep. Just look at it, even its cooldown has been shortened "
"from all that sleeping."

#. Header for contraptions mvz2:wooden_dropper
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid "木制投掷器向敌人发射滚动的木球。"
msgstr "Wooden Dropper fires rolling wooden balls."

#. Properties for contraptions mvz2:wooden_dropper
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid ""
"攻击间隔：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:AttackInterval\" />秒</color>\n"
"伤害：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_damage\" />，金球40</color>\n"
"技能：<color=red>立即喷射30颗大型木球，每颗造成80点伤害</color>"
msgstr ""
"Fire rate: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:AttackInterval\" /> seconds</color>\n"
"Damage: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_damage\" />,golden ball 40</color>\n"
"Evocation: <color=red>Fires 30 large wooden balls instantly, each deals 80 damage</color>"

#. Flavor for contraptions mvz2:wooden_dropper
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid ""
"使用技能前：木制投掷器\n"
"使用技能后：森森森森森森森森森森制投掷器\n"
"\n"
"木制投掷器喜爱足球，他曾多次在足球场上当发球器。虽然不少次他都被当成球踢进球门。\n"
"大抵运动员没发现自己踢的是方块，顺脚的事。"
msgstr ""
"Before evocation: Wooden Dropper\n"
"After evocation: Wooooooooooooooooooooooooooooooden Dropper\n"
"\n"
"The Wooden Dropper loves soccer. He's been used as a launcher on the field many times — though quite often he himself gets kicked into "
"the goal like a ball.\n"
"The players probably didn't even notice they were kicking a block. Just went with the flow."

#. Header for contraptions mvz2:spike_block
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid "尖刺方块会对走在上面的敌人造成伤害。"
msgstr "Spike Block deals damage to enemies stepped on it."

#. Properties for contraptions mvz2:spike_block
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid ""
"攻击频率：<color=red>0.5秒</color>\n"
"伤害：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_damage\" /></color>\n"
"技能：<color=red>对一整行地面上的敌人快速造成伤害，并将它们拉向自身</color>"
msgstr ""
"Attack rate: <color=red>0.5 second</color>\n"
"Damage: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_damage\" /></color>\n"
"Evocation: <color=red>Deals damage rapidly to enemies on the ground in the whole lane, and pulls them to the Spike Block</color>"

#. Flavor for contraptions mvz2:spike_block
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid ""
"我是文字，我现在非常疼\n"
"WWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWW\n"
"\n"
"尖刺方块并非来源于<ref=[misc]mvz2:villager>村民</ref>的那个世界，它曾经被排斥到了另一个世界。在那里，它结识了一位叫做      的朋友，它们"
"便共同逃回了原本的世界。\n"
"尸界大战爆发后，原本想要过平静生活的它，却因为一些特殊的原因，加入了<ref=[misc]mvz2:steve>史蒂夫</ref>的军队。\n"
"“我在他的身上看到了那个人的影子。”"
msgstr ""
"Text here, I'm in pain\n"
"WWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWW\n"
"\n"
"Spike Block doesn't come from the world <ref=[misc]mvz2:villager>Villager</ref> lives in. He used to be excluded to another world. He "
"met a friend called Geardle there, and then they escaped and returned their world together.\n"
"When World War Z broke out, he wanted to live a peaceful life at first, but joined <ref=[misc]mvz2:steve>Steve</ref>'s army for some "
"special reason.\n"
"\"He reminds me of that person.\""

#. Header for contraptions mvz2:stone_dropper
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid "石制投掷器向敌人发射小型卵石，偶尔会发射能击退敌人并分裂的巨石。"
msgstr "Stone Dropper fires tiny cobbles, or sometimes boulders which can knock back enemy monsters and break apart."

#. Properties for contraptions mvz2:stone_dropper
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid ""
"攻击间隔：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:AttackInterval\" />秒</color>\n"
"巨石概率：<color=red>25%</color>\n"
"伤害：<color=red>10（卵石），40（巨石）</color>\n"
"技能：<color=red>立即喷射30发巨石</color>"
msgstr ""
"Fire rate: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:AttackInterval\" /> seconds</color>\n"
"Boulder chance: <color=red>25%</color>\n"
"Damage: <color=red>10 (cobble), 40 (boulder)</color>\n"
"Evocation: <color=red>Fires 30 boulders instantly</color>"

#. Flavor for contraptions mvz2:stone_dropper
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid ""
"石制投掷器是个泰拉瑞亚的粉丝，每次下矿它都能准确而快速地找出滚石陷阱的位置，但总是找不出滚木陷阱的位置。\n"
"哦，顺带一提，他用滚石打死过肉山。\n"
"\n"
"它本来想学<ref=[contraptions]mvz2:wooden_dropper>木制投掷器</ref>玩一个磊磊磊磊磊磊磊磊磊磊制投掷器的笑话的，但是不幸的是"
"<ref=[contraptions]mvz2:wooden_dropper>木制投掷器</ref>为这个笑话申请了专利。\n"
"<color=white>附录：它跟恋真的没啥关系。</color>"
msgstr ""
"Stone Dropper is a fan of Terraria. Every time he goes mining, he can accurately and quickly locate boulder traps, but he can never "
"seem to find rolling log traps.\n"
"Oh, by the way, he once killed the Wall of Flesh with a boulder.\n"
"\n"
"He originally wanted to pull a \"Stooooooooooooooooooooooooooone Dropper\" joke like the <ref=[contraptions]mvz2:wooden_dropper>Wooden "
"Dropper</ref> did, but unfortunately, the <ref=[contraptions]mvz2:wooden_dropper>Wooden Dropper</ref> has patented that joke.\n"
"<color=white>Appendix: He really has nothing to do with Koishi.</color>"

#. Header for contraptions mvz2:stone_shield
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid "石护罩可以和其他器械放在一起，并保护其内部的器械不受爆炸、弹射物、近战伤害。"
msgstr "Stone Shield can be placed together with an other contraption, and protects it."

#. Properties for contraptions mvz2:stone_shield
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid ""
"耐久：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_health\" /></color>\n"
"技能：<color=red>3x3范围内的器械无敌10秒</color>"
msgstr ""
"Toughness: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_health\" /></color>\n"
"Evocation: <color=red>Makes contraptions in 3x3 range invincible for 10 seconds</color>"

#. Flavor for contraptions mvz2:stone_shield
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid "注意：当你使用铁镐时，瞄准它的下方是挖掉石护罩，瞄准它的上方是挖掉里面的器械。星之碎片同理。"
msgstr ""
"When you are using the iron pickaxe, targetting at the bottom will destroy the Stone Fence, targetting at the top will destroy the "
"contraption inside it. Same for starshards."

#. Flavor for contraptions mvz2:stone_shield
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid ""
"无法访问该页面：\n"
"458 Protected\n"
"页面受到保护，请先挖掉石护罩再继续。\n"
"或许你要在某些关卡绕过石护罩才能看到完整的页面？"
msgstr ""
"Unable to access this page: \n"
"458 Protected\n"
"The page is protected, please delete the stone shield and retry.\n"
"Perhaps in some levels you need to bypass the Stone Shield to see the full page?"

#. Flavor for contraptions mvz2:stone_shield
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid ""
"黑曜石是比石头硬的，不过石护罩的生命值却比黑曜石还要高一点。这没什么奇怪的，现实中的黑曜石还和玻璃一样脆呢。\n"
"你可能想责怪石护罩为什么不能保护里面的器械不受凋零范围伤害，还是别提了吧，小心他生气了连防爆都不给了。"
msgstr ""
"Obsidians are harder than stones, but the durability of Stone Fence is a little higher than that of Obsidian. It's not strange at all, "
"that obsidians in real life is as fragile as glass.\n"
"You might want to blame the Stone Shield for not protecting the contraption inside from wither area damage. Better not bring it up, or "
"it might get angry and stop providing blast protection altogether."

#. Header for contraptions mvz2:golden_apple
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid "金苹果可以魅惑一个近战攻击它的敌怪，使其为你而战。"
msgstr "Golden Apples can hypnotise an enemy monster that attacks it, making it fight for you."

#. Properties for contraptions mvz2:golden_apple
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid ""
"特点：<color=red>吃掉他的敌人能够获得60/s的生命恢复</color>\n"
"技能：<color=red>发出彩色炫光，被魅惑的敌怪变为突变僵尸</color>"
msgstr ""
"Special: <color=red>Enemies that eat it gain 60/s health regeneration</color>\n"
"Evocation: <color=red>Radiates colorful light, the hypnotised enemy monster transforms into a mutant zombie</color>"

#. Flavor for contraptions mvz2:golden_apple
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid ""
"金苹果对于砸伤重力方块这件事情感到很抱歉，所以它赔了重力方块自己的一块金皮。\n"
"这就是为什么<ref=[contraptions]mvz2:gravity_pad>重力板</ref>是紫色的。"
msgstr ""
"Golden Apple is very sorry for damaging Gravity Block, so it compensated Gravity Block with its own piece of gold skin.\n"
"That's why <ref=[contraptions]mvz2:gravity_pad>Gravity Pad</ref> is purple."

#. Flavor for contraptions mvz2:golden_apple
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid "“嗯？以牙还牙里<ref=[contraptions]mvz2:magichest>魔术箱</ref>是不是抢了我的风头？”"
msgstr "\"Huh? In 'A Tooth For A Tooth', did the <ref=[contraptions]mvz2:magichest>Magic Chest</ref> steal my spotlight?\""

#. Header for contraptions mvz2:thunder_drum
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid "雷鼓在触发后会震飞所有地面上的敌怪，使其后退并换行。之后进入破损状态，需要时间修复。"
msgstr ""
"Thunder Drums, when triggered, knock all enemy monsters on the ground into the air, knocking them back and changing their lanes. "
"Afterwards the drums break and need time to repair themselves."

#. Properties for contraptions mvz2:thunder_drum
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid ""
"修复时间：<color=red>60秒</color>\n"
"技能：<color=red>引发4秒地震，对所有地面上的敌怪造成总共25%最大生命的伤害</color>"
msgstr ""
"Repair time：<color=red>60 seconds</color>\n"
"Evocation: <color=red>Makes a earthquake for 4 seconds, dealing a total damage of 25% maximum health to all enemies on the ground</"
"color>"

#. Flavor for contraptions mvz2:thunder_drum
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid ""
"<rotate=\"-20\">别乱震啊卧槽！</rotate>\n"
"<rotate=\"-100\">雷鼓很羡慕堀川雷鼓，希望能像她一样成为一个付丧神，开始自己的生活。但是它不知道现在已经建国后了。</rotate>"
msgstr ""
"<rotate=\"-20\">STOP TRIGGERING IT!</rotate>\n"
"<rotate=\"-100\">Thunder Drum envies Horikawa Raiko. It wants to become a tsukumogami like her and start its own life. But it doesn't "
"know becoming a youkai is illegal now.</rotate>"

#. Header for contraptions mvz2:tesla_coil
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid "磁暴线圈会电击周围大范围内的敌人。"
msgstr "Tesla Coil shocks enemies in a large area."

#. Properties for contraptions mvz2:tesla_coil
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid ""
"攻击速度：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:AttackInterval\" />秒</color>\n"
"半径：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:FireRange\" />格</color>\n"
"伤害：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_damage\" /></color>\n"
"特殊：<color=red>被攻击的怪物会停顿1秒；常规状态下不可以攻击空中怪物；电击水域会对周围水域也造成伤害</color>\n"
"技能：<color=red>召唤闪电风暴，劈击一定范围内的随机位置</color>"
msgstr ""
"Fire rate: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:AttackInterval\" /> seconds</color>\n"
"Radius: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:FireRange\" /> blocks</color>\n"
"Damage: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_damage\" /></color>\n"
"Special: <color=red>Hit monsters are shocked for 1 second. Cannot attack enemies in the air by default. Electrified water also damages "
"nearby bodies of water</color>\n"
"Evocation: <color=red>Creates a thunderstorms, strikes random positions in a radius</color>"

#. Flavor for contraptions mvz2:tesla_coil
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid ""
"我在玩什么游戏？\n"
"\n"
"等一下，你为什么不能对空？？？？？\n"
"\n"
"<color=white>哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈"
"哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈</color>\n"
"<color=grey>哦，对了，他电击器械时可以使得器械短路。</color>\n"
"<color=grey>你觉得这个特性没用？那希望用不上这个特性吧。</color>"
msgstr ""
"What game am I playing?\n"
"\n"
"Wait, why can't you attack air enemies???????\n"
"\n"
"<color=white>Hahahahahahahahahahahahahahahahahahahahahahahahahahahahahahahahahahahahahahahahahahahahahahahahahahahahahahahahahahahahahahahahahahahahahahahahahahahahahahahahahahahaha</"
"color>\n"
"<color=grey>Oh, by the way, when it shocks contraptions, it can short-circuit them.</color>\n"
"<color=grey>You think this feature is useless? Hopefully you won't need it then.</color>"

#. Flavor for contraptions mvz2:tesla_coil
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid "见过<ref=[enemies]mvz2:TeslaTrooper>磁暴步兵</ref>了吗？磁暴线圈在受到电击后会有10秒的强充能，攻速*1.25，能够攻击空中敌人。"
msgstr ""
"Ever seen a <ref=[enemies]mvz2:TeslaTrooper>Tesla Trooper</ref>? When a Tesla Coil is shocked, it becomes overcharged for 10 seconds: "
"Attack Speed is multiplied by 1.25, and it can attack enemies in the air."

#. Header for contraptions mvz2:giant_bowl
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid "巨碗能够缓慢生产并存储<ref=[misc]mvz2:starshard.miracle_mallet>星之碎片</ref>，这些星之碎片只能通过摧毁巨碗取出。"
msgstr ""
"Giant Bowl slowly produces and stores <ref=[misc]mvz2:starshard.miracle_mallet>starshards</ref>, these starshards can only be taken "
"out by destroying the bowl."

#. Properties for contraptions mvz2:giant_bowl
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid ""
"生产时间：<color=red>60秒</color>\n"
"存储上限：<color=red>5</color>\n"
"技能：<color=red>向内部存储一颗<ref=[misc]mvz2:starshard.miracle_mallet>星之碎片</ref></color>"
msgstr ""
"Produce time: <color=red>60 seconds</color>\n"
"Capacity: <color=red>5</color>\n"
"Evocation: <color=red>Stores 1 starshard</color>"

#. Flavor for contraptions mvz2:giant_bowl
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid ""
"谁把小碗的碗抢过来了？\n"
"为了防止失主来找，我们叫他盆吧。"
msgstr ""
"Who stole Sukuna's bowl?\n"
"To prevent the owner from coming to claim it, let's just call it a Basin."

#. Header for contraptions mvz2:note_block
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid "音符盒发射在自身和敌人间不停反弹的音符，持续造成伤害。"
msgstr "Note Block shoots notes that bounces between itself and enemies, dealing damage over time."

#. Properties for contraptions mvz2:note_block
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid ""
"伤害：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_damage\" /></color>\n"
"攻击间隔：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:AttackInterval\" />秒</color>\n"
"音符上限：<color=red>10</color>\n"
"技能：<color=red>发生一次1200的爆炸，在30秒内x500%伤害，x500%攻击间隔，x200%音符飞行速度</color>"
msgstr ""
"Damage: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_damage\" /></color>\n"
"Fire rate: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:AttackInterval\" /> seconds</color>\n"
"Notes limit: <color=red>10</color>\n"
"Evocation: <color=red>Causes a 1200-damage explosion. In 30 seconds, deal x500% damage, x500% fire rate, x200% note flying speed and "
"+10 tiles range</color>"

#. Flavor for contraptions mvz2:note_block
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid ""
"永远不要试图做音符盒的邻居，别问为什么。\n"
"\n"
"<color=grey>音符盒是个很喜欢音乐的家伙，你可以从各种地方找到证据：各种演唱会——包括μ's的都能看到它的身影、卢西奥是他的主玩英雄……等等等"
"等。最近，据说他只花了一秒就买下了东方交响乐的门票……</color>"
msgstr ""
"Never ever try to be Note Block's neighbor. Don't ask why.\n"
"\n"
"<color=grey>Note Block is a guy who loves music. You can find evidence everywhere: from various concerts — including μ's — you can "
"spot him there. Lucio is his main hero... and so on. Lately, it's said he bought tickets to a Touhou symphony in just one second...</"
"color>"

#. Header for contraptions mvz2:lightning_orb
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid "闪电之珠可以阻挡敌人的攻击，并可以通过吸收敌弹和爆炸来治疗自己。"
msgstr "Lightning Orbs can block enemy attacks and absorb enemy projectiles and explosion to heal itself."

#. Properties for contraptions mvz2:lightning_orb
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid ""
"耐久：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_health\" /></color>\n"
"特点：<color=red>吸收敌弹，并恢复100耐久</color>\n"
"技能：<color=red>在5秒内吸收所有远程射弹和爆炸伤害并治疗自己，之后将这些伤害返还给所有敌人（最高900）</color>"
msgstr ""
"Toughness: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_health\" /></color>\n"
"Special: <color=red>Absorbs projectiles, heals 100 toughness for each projectile</color>\n"
"Evocation: <color=red>For 5 seconds, absorbs all ranged projectiles and explosion damage and heals itself, then deals that damage back "
"to all enemies (up to 900)</color>"

#. Flavor for contraptions mvz2:lightning_orb
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid ""
"它就是<ref=[contraptions]mvz2:note_block>音符盒</ref>的邻居。\n"
"天哪！还好他能吸收掉那些噪音……\n"
"\n"
"有人希望他能吸收近战伤害，但他说他干不了，交给别人吧。\n"
"\n"
"<color=grey>在遥远的鲁·高因，有一位法师钻研出了这种法术。这种法术能够抵消一部分的伤害，将生命的损失转化成法力的消耗。他给这个法术起了个"
"名字：能量护盾——俗称：“顶个球”。</color>"
msgstr ""
"He IS the neighbor of <ref=[contraptions]mvz2:note_block>Note Block</ref>.\n"
"MY GOD! Good thing that he can absorb all that noise...\n"
"\n"
"Some people wish it could absorb melee damage too, but it says that's not its job — leave that to someone else.\n"
"\n"
"<color=grey>In the distant city of Lut Gholein, a mage once developed a spell. This spell could negate a portion of incoming damage, "
"converting loss of life into loss of mana. He named this spell: Energy Shield — commonly known as \"wearing a ball\".</color>"

#. Header for contraptions mvz2:splitenser
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid "双向发射器在向前发射箭矢的同时，也会向后方发射一发箭矢和一发飞镖。"
msgstr "Splitenser fires an arrow forward, and at the same time fires one arrow and one dart backward."

#. Properties for contraptions mvz2:splitenser
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid ""
"攻击间隔：<color=red>1发/<var id=\"mvz2:AttackInterval\" />秒（前方），2发/<var id=\"mvz2:AttackInterval\" />秒（后方）</color>\n"
"伤害：<color=red>箭和飞镖<var id=\"mvz2:entity_damage\" />，小导弹100，大导弹600</color>\n"
"技能：<color=red>快速向前发射60支箭矢，向后发射20发箭矢和8发小导弹，最后向后发射1发大导弹</color>"
msgstr ""
"Fire rate: <color=red>1 shot / <var id=\"mvz2:AttackInterval\" /> second (front), 2 shots / <var id=\"mvz2:AttackInterval\" /> seconds "
"(rear)</color>\n"
"Damage: <color=red>Arrow and dart: <var id=\"mvz2:entity_damage\" />, Small missile: 100, Large missile: 600</color>\n"
"Evocation: <color=red>Rapidly fires 60 arrows forward, and 20 arrows + 8 small missiles backward, finishing with 1 large missile fired "
"backward</color>"

#. Flavor for contraptions mvz2:splitenser
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid ""
"“别射了，你把我晃得头晕！”后面的发射器很不爽。\n"
"“可是你每次都发射两次，论头晕，我比你还要严重哩！”前面的发射器反驳。\n"
"自从双向发射器被发明以来，它和自己的争吵就从来没停过。\n"
"“你这么和你哥哥说的话吗？放尊重点！”\n"
"“谁是你弟弟？我们都不知道是谁先被造出来的！”\n"
"“我发射更快，理应当哥哥！”\n"
"“那大部分时候还是我把前面的敌人干掉的嘞！”\n"
"……\n"
"幸好他邻居是<ref=[contraptions]mvz2:lightning_orb>闪电之珠</ref>，不然就又有人要来投诉了。"
msgstr ""
"\"Stop firing! You're making me dizzy!\" complained the rear dispenser irritably.\n"
"\"But you fire twice every time! If anyone should be dizzy, it's me!\" retorted the front dispenser.\n"
"Ever since the Splitenser was invented, its two halves had never stopped arguing.\n"
"\"Is that how you speak to your elder brother? Show some respect!\"\n"
"\"Who said you’re my brother? We don’t even know which of us was created first!\"\n"
"\"I fire faster—that makes me the elder brother by default!\"\n"
"\"Oh please, I’m the one who handles most of the enemies up front!\"\n"
"...\n"
"Thankfully, their neighbor was the <ref=[contraptions]mvz2:lightning_orb>Lightning Orb</ref>. Otherwise, someone else would’ve come "
"knocking to complain about the noise."

#. Header for contraptions mvz2:devourer
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid "吞噬者可以用于消除<ref=[misc]mvz2:monster_spawner>刷怪笼</ref>和其他障碍物，或者用于将器械变回一张蓝图掉落物。"
msgstr ""
"The Devourer can be used to remove <ref=[misc]mvz2:monster_spawner>Monster Spawners</ref> and other obstacles, or turn a contraption "
"back into a blueprint."

#. Properties for contraptions mvz2:devourer
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid ""
"技能：<color=red>变成吃豆人中的小幽灵！</color>\n"
"特点：<color=red>可以用于消除刷怪笼，或者用于将器械变回一张蓝图掉落物，后者的速度是前者的2倍。</color>"
msgstr ""
"Evocation: <color=red>Turns into a Pac-Man ghost!</color>\n"
"Special: <color=red>Can be used to remove monster spawners, or turn a contraption back into a blueprint drop. The latter is twice as "
"fast as the former.</color>"

#. Flavor for contraptions mvz2:devourer
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid ""
"“我受不了了！！！！！！！！！！！！”\n"
"“吵死了！！！！！！！！！！！！”\n"
"“我要搬家！！！！！！！！！！！！”\n"
"\n"
"……至少上一个这栋楼的住户是这么说的。\n"
"\n"
"伙计，她以前头上有个不明意义的网，至于为什么会有这个东西，制作它的人表示也不知道。"
msgstr ""
"\"I can't take this anymore!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\"\n"
"\"It's so damn noisy!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\"\n"
"\"I'm moving out!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\"\n"
"\n"
"...At least, that's what the previous tenant of this building said."

#. Flavor for contraptions mvz2:devourer
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid "她因自己拥有3个专属的小游戏而引来了不少器械的嫉妒，但没器械敢正面提出意见。"
msgstr "She has three exclusive minigames, which has made many contraptions jealous, but none dare to voice their objections openly."

#. Header for contraptions mvz2:hellfire
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid "地狱火会点燃穿过它的箭矢，使其额外造成火焰伤害。"
msgstr "Hellfire ignites arrows which pass through it, making them deal additional fire damage."

#. Properties for contraptions mvz2:hellfire
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid ""
"血量：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:AttackInterval\" /></color>\n"
"伤害增幅：<color=red>+100%火焰伤害，+66%溅射伤害</color>\n"
"技能：<color=red>变为诅咒火焰，为箭矢+200%火焰伤害，+133%溅射伤害</color>"
msgstr ""
"Toughness: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:AttackInterval\" /></color>\n"
"Damage Addition: <color=red>+100% fire damage, +66% splash damage</color>\n"
"Evocation: <color=red>Become cursed flame, provides +200% fire damage, +133% splash damage for arrows</color>"

#. Flavor for contraptions mvz2:hellfire
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid ""
"烧吧！我内心中的熊熊烈火，点燃我的<color=red>愤怒</color>！\n"
"烧吧！将我眼前的所有不公，全部烧成灰烬！\n"
"烧吧！我所憎恨的邪恶之物，尽数应受惩罚！\n"
"烧吧！在他们惊恐的眼神中，向其降下毁灭！\n"
"\n"
"火焰啊！把我内心中的黑暗，沮丧，还有憎恨，统统烧个干净！\n"
"<b>让这明亮的火光，照亮整个世界！！！</b>"
msgstr ""
"Burn! The blazing flames within my soul, ignite my <color=red>anger</color>!\n"
"Burn! Reduce all the injustice before my eyes to ashes!\n"
"Burn! Let all the evil I despise be punished accordingly!\n"
"Burn! Bring down destruction upon them amidst their terrified gazes!\n"
"\n"
"Flames! Burn away the darkness, despair, and hatred within my heart!\n"
"<b>May this brilliant blaze illuminate the entire world!!!</b>"

#. Header for contraptions mvz2:necrotombstone
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid "死灵墓碑会不断召唤友方的<ref=[enemies]mvz2:skeleton_warrior>骷髅战士</ref>，让它们为你而战。"
msgstr "Necrotombstones will constantly summon friendly <ref=[enemies]mvz2:skeleton_warrior> skeleton warriors</ref> to fight for you."

#. Properties for contraptions mvz2:necrotombstone
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid ""
"召唤时间：<color=red>15秒</color>\n"
"骷髅战士生命：<color=red><var local=\"warrior_hp\" />+<var local=\"helmet_hp\" />（头盔）+<var local=\"shield_hp\" />（盾）</color>\n"
"骷髅战士速度：<color=red><var local=\"warrior_speed\" /></color>\n"
"技能：<color=red>召唤3个同种的火焰、冰霜或闪电<ref=[enemies]mvz2:skeleton_mage>骷髅法师</ref></color>\n"
"特点：<color=red>被摧毁时立刻召唤<ref=[enemies]mvz2:skeleton_warrior>骷髅战士</ref></color>"
msgstr ""
"Summon Cooldown: <color=red>15 seconds</color>\n"
"Warrior Toughness: <color=red><var local=\"warrior_hp\" />+<var local=\"helmet_hp\" /> (Helmet)+<var local=\"shield_hp\" /> (Shield)</"
"color>\n"
"Warrior Speed: <color=red><var local=\"warrior_speed\" /></color>\n"
"Evocation: <color=red>Summon 3 skeleton mages of the same class: Fire, Frost, or Lightning</color>\n"
"Special: <color=red>When destroyed, instantly summons a Skeleton Warrior</color>"

#. Flavor for contraptions mvz2:necrotombstone
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid ""
"听说古代的死灵墓碑有3种形态，而非现在的一种。\n"
"\n"
"看着这座墓碑，恍惚中，你的脑海中似乎浮现出了一句熟悉的话：\n"
"“比起死亡，我更害怕的是被遗忘。”\n"
"\n"
"这是谁说的呢？"
msgstr ""
"I heard that the ancient Necromancer Tombstone had three forms, unlike the single form it has now.\n"
"Gazing at this tombstone, in a daze, a familiar phrase seems to flash into your mind:\n"
"\"More than death itself, what I truly fear is being forgotten.\"\n"
"\n"
"Who was it that said this?"

#. Header for contraptions mvz2:black_hole_bomb
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid "黑洞炸弹在触发后会产生小型黑洞，吸引周围所有的敌怪和子弹。"
msgstr "Black Hole Bombs create tiny black holes after being triggered, absorbing all nearby enemy monsters and projectiles."

#. Properties for contraptions mvz2:black_hole_bomb
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid ""
"持续时间：<color=red>8秒</color>\n"
"伤害：<color=red><var local=\"dps\" />/秒</color>\n"
"半径：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:FireRange\" />格</color>\n"
"技能：<color=red>产生湮灭领域，直接消灭范围内的所有敌人和敌弹</color>"
msgstr ""
"Lifetime: <color=red>8 seconds</color>\n"
"Damage: <color=red><var local=\"dps\" />/s</color>\n"
"Radius: <color=red>1.5 tiles</color>\n"
"Evocation: <color=red>Creates an annihilation field instead, instantly destroys all enemies and enemy projectiles in the radius</color>"

#. Flavor for contraptions mvz2:black_hole_bomb
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid ""
"你知道的，真空不能传声，所以他其实听不到他邻居产生的噪音。\n"
"\n"
"天哪！别再讲你这笑话了！烂死了！！！\n"
"\n"
"该器械和掌握皮毛虚空能量的伪行者相性极其不佳。"
msgstr ""
"You know, sound can't travel through a vacuum, so he actually can't hear the noise from his neighbors.\n"
"\n"
"GOSH! Stop telling that joke of yours! It's awful!!!\n"
"\n"
"This contraption has extremely poor synergy with the “SixQi”, who wields a mere fraction of Void energy."

#. Header for contraptions mvz2:desire_pot
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid "欲望壶会从怪物身上复制其携带的<ref=[misc]mvz2:starshard.shinrei>星之碎片</ref>，每个欲望壶最多复制三个。"
msgstr ""
"Desire Pots duplicate the <ref=[misc]mvz2:starshard.shinrei>starshards</ref> carried by monsters. Every pot can duplicate up to 3 "
"starshards."

#. Properties for contraptions mvz2:desire_pot
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid ""
"技能：<color=red>将最后方的两张充能完毕的的蓝图复制为掉落物，然后重置它们的充能</color>\n"
"特点：<color=red>被摧毁时会变成随机器械。</color>"
msgstr ""
"Evocation: <color=red>Spawn copies of the last 2 fully-recharged blueprints as pickups, then reset the recharges of the 2 blueprints.</"
"color>\n"
"Special: <color=red>When destroyed, turns into a Random Contraption</color>"

#. Flavor for contraptions mvz2:desire_pot
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid ""
"我是壶中的神灵，我能实现你的愿望，让我听听你内心中的欲望吧……\n"
"\n"
"让壶解禁？\n"
"\n"
"嗯……我刚才好像什么都没有听到。"
msgstr ""
"I am the divine spirit in the pot, I can fulfill your wishes. Let me hear the desires in your heart...\n"
"\n"
"Unban the pot?\n"
"\n"
"Um... I didn't seem to hear anything just now."

#. Header for contraptions mvz2:gunpowder_barrel
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid "火药桶能生产为你提供大量能量的火药，但若未及时拾取，则会炸伤周围的友方单位。火药桶在被破坏时也会爆炸。"
msgstr ""
"Gunpowder Barrels produce gunpowder that provides massive energy, but will explode and damage nearby friendly units if not collected "
"in time. Gunpowder Barrels also explode when destroyed."

#. Properties for contraptions mvz2:gunpowder_barrel
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid ""
"爆炸伤害：<color=red>100（简单）、150（普通）、300（困难）</color>\n"
"爆炸半径：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:FireRange\" />格</color>\n"
"生产时间：<color=red>30秒</color>\n"
"提供能量：<color=red><var local=\"gunpowder_value\" /></color>\n"
"技能：<color=red>改为生成暴怒火药，提供<var local=\"furious_gunpowder_value\" />能量，但是会更快爆炸</color>"
msgstr ""
"Explosion Damage: <color=red>100 (Easy), 150 (Normal), 300 (Hard)</color>\n"
"Explosion Radius: <color=red>1.5 tiles</color>\n"
"Produce time: <color=red>30 seconds</color>\n"
"Energy production: <color=red><var local=\"gunpowder_value\" /></color>\n"
"Evocation: <color=red>Produce furious gunpowder instead, which provides <var local=\"furious_gunpowder_value\" /> energy but explodes "
"faster</color>"

#. Flavor for contraptions mvz2:gunpowder_barrel
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid ""
"众所周知，最早的黑火药由三种材料制作：\n"
"硫磺（一种易燃品）\n"
"硝石（被埋葬的尸体旁一般会产生结晶）\n"
"木炭（燃烧木头的产物）\n"
"那么——等等，我为什么要告诉你这些？"
msgstr ""
"As everyone knows, the earliest gunpowder was made from three materials:\n"
"Sulfur (a flammable substance)\n"
"Saltpeter (crystals that typically form near buried bodies)\n"
"Charcoal (the product of burning wood)\n"
"So—wait, why should I be telling you this?"

#. Header for contraptions mvz2:triplenser
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid "三头发射器一次能发射三行的箭矢。如果它位于最外侧的行，则改为向它自己所在的一行额外发射箭矢。"
msgstr ""
"Triplensers fire arrows across three lanes at once. When placed on the outermost lane, they fire the arrow on its own lane instead."

#. Properties for contraptions mvz2:triplenser
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid ""
"攻击间隔：<color=red>3支/<var id=\"mvz2:AttackInterval\" />秒</color>\n"
"伤害：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_damage\" /></color>\n"
"技能：<color=red>发射三颗缓慢飞行的，互相环绕的星球，穿透并反复打击敌人</color>"
msgstr ""
"Fire rate: <color=red>3 shots/<var id=\"mvz2:AttackInterval\" />s</color>\n"
"Damage: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_damage\" /></color>\n"
"Evocation: <color=red>Launches three slowly orbiting planets that pierce through enemies and strike them repeatedly</color>"

#. Flavor for contraptions mvz2:triplenser
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid ""
"它喜欢看的典故有很多：三打白骨精、三顾茅庐、三打祝家庄……\n"
"……确定它喜欢看的是典故的内容吗？"
msgstr ""
"It adores a lot of classic tales – <i>Goldilocks and the Three Bears</i>, <i>The Three Little Pigs</i>, <i>The Three Musketeers</"
"i>...\n"
"...Are you sure you actually care about the stories?"

#. Header for contraptions mvz2:firework_dispenser
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid "烟花发射器会发射火焰弹攻击上方高空中的敌人。"
msgstr "Firework Dispensers will blow up nearby enemies in the sky."

#. Properties for contraptions mvz2:firework_dispenser
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid ""
"攻击间隔：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:AttackInterval\" />秒</color>\n"
"伤害：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_damage\" />，只攻击空中敌人</color>\n"
"射程：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:FireRange\" />格</color>\n"
"技能：<color=red>射程永久+1格</color>"
msgstr ""
"Fire rate: <color=red>1 shot/<var id=\"mvz2:AttackInterval\" /> seconds</color>\n"
"Damage: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_damage\" />, only damage flying enemies</color>\n"
"Explosion Radius: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:FireRange\" /> tiles</color>\n"
"Evocation: <color=red>Permanently +1 tile explosion radius</color>"

#. Flavor for contraptions mvz2:firework_dispenser
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid ""
"器械们很好奇为什么他发射的明明是火焰弹，名字却叫烟花发射器。其实他是能发射烟花的，只不过烟花太贵了，他平时不舍得射，必须得满足一定条件"
"后才能发射。\n"
"这个条件在当前版本尚不满足，等之后的版本吧。"
msgstr ""
"The contraptions are curious: if it fires fireballs, why is it called the Firework Launcher? The truth is, it can launch fireworks — "
"but fireworks are too expensive, so it's reluctant to use them normally. They can only be fired under certain conditions.\n"
"\n"
"Those conditions are not met in the current version. Maybe in a future update."

#. Header for contraptions mvz2:repeatenser
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid "连射发射器一次能发射两支箭矢。"
msgstr "Repeatenser can shoot 2 arrows at once."

#. Properties for contraptions mvz2:repeatenser
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid ""
"攻击间隔：<color=red>2支/<var id=\"mvz2:AttackInterval\" />秒</color>\n"
"伤害：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_damage\" />，脉冲箭40，大箭矢600</color>\n"
"技能：<color=red>快速发射40支箭矢和8发小导弹，最后发射一支大箭矢</color>"
msgstr ""
"Fire rate: <color=red>2 arrows / <var id=\"mvz2:AttackInterval\" /> seconds</color>\n"
"Damage: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_damage\" />, Pulse Arrow: 40, Large Arrow: 600</color>\n"
"Evocation: <color=red>Rapidly fires 40 arrows and 8 small missiles, finishing with 1 large arrow</color>"

#. Flavor for contraptions mvz2:repeatenser
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid ""
"他没能有幸加入<ref=[contraptions]mvz2:high_frequency_pulse_dispenser>高频脉冲发射器</ref>的士兵队伍，因为它每次说话都要说两遍。\n"
"他没能有幸加入<ref=[contraptions]mvz2:high_frequency_pulse_dispenser>高频脉冲发射器</ref>的士兵队伍，因为它每次说话都要说两遍。\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"另外，他为了和<ref=[contraptions]mvz2:splitenser>双向发射器</ref>做出区别，他选择发射大箭矢而非大导弹。\n"
"另外，他为了和<ref=[contraptions]mvz2:splitenser>双向发射器</ref>做出区别，他选择发射大箭矢而非大导弹。"
msgstr ""
"It wasn't fortunate enough to join the ranks of the <ref=[contraptions]mvz2:high_frequency_pulse_dispenser>High-Frequency Pulse "
"Dispenser</ref>'s soldiers, because it had to say everything twice.\n"
"It wasn't fortunate enough to join the ranks of the <ref=[contraptions]mvz2:high_frequency_pulse_dispenser>High-Frequency Pulse "
"Dispenser</ref>'s soldiers, because it had to say everything twice.\n"
"\n"
"Additionally, to distinguish itself from the <ref=[contraptions]mvz2:splitenser>Splitenser</ref>, it chose to fire large arrows "
"instead of large missiles.\n"
"Additionally, to distinguish itself from the <ref=[contraptions]mvz2:splitenser>Splitenser</ref>, it chose to fire large arrows "
"instead of large missiles."

#. Header for contraptions mvz2:beacon
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid "信标能向前方、后方、后上方、后下方、前上方、前下方六个方向同时发射星星手里剑。"
msgstr "Beacons shoot starikens in six directions at once: forward, backward, back-up, back-down, front-up, and front-down."

#. Properties for contraptions mvz2:beacon
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid ""
"攻击间隔：<color=red>6发/<var id=\"mvz2:AttackInterval\" />秒</color>\n"
"伤害：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_damage\" /></color>\n"
"技能：<color=red>召唤10颗陨石，打击场上随机位置</color>"
msgstr ""
"Fire rate: <color=red>5 shots/<var id=\"mvz2:AttackInterval\" />s</color>\n"
"Damage: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_damage\" /></color>\n"
"Evocation: <color=red>Summon 10 meteors to strike random positions on the battlefield</color>"

#. Flavor for contraptions mvz2:beacon
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid "它其实不是用<ref=[artifacts]mvz2:nether_star>下界之星</ref>做的，只是一个会发射手里剑的发射器改成的假冒伪劣产品而已。"
msgstr ""
"It's not made with the <ref=[artifacts]mvz2:nether_star>Nether Star</ref>, just a counterfeit product made from a dispenser that can "
"shoot shurikens."

#. Header for contraptions mvz2:wooden_fan
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid "木风扇在触发后会将一整行内的敌方怪物吹回原地。如果怪物较轻，还会直接将其吹出战场。"
msgstr ""
"When triggered, Wooden Fans blow away and push back enemy monsters in their lane. If the enemy monsters are very light, they will be "
"directly blown out of the battlefield."

#. Properties for contraptions mvz2:wooden_fan
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid ""
"特点：<color=red>可以直接吹飞空中或者较轻的怪物，但对地面上较重的怪物没有效果</color>\n"
"范围：<color=red>一整行</color>\n"
"技能：<color=red>改为吹动整个战场的怪物</color>"
msgstr ""
"Special: <color=red>Directly blow away airborne and very light monsters, but has no effect against heavy and very heavy monsters on "
"the ground</color>\n"
"Range: <color=red>One entire row</color>\n"
"Evocation: <color=red>Blow away all enemy monsters on the battlefield</color>"

#. Flavor for contraptions mvz2:wooden_fan
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid "这东西哪有那么重量级，都被你们吹到天上去了！"
msgstr "Its real name is George."

#. Header for contraptions mvz2:elastic_cloud
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid "弹性云会以自身的耐久为代价，弹开接触到的敌方怪物和子弹。"
msgstr "Elastic Clouds sacrifice their own toughness to bounce away enemy monsters and bullets upon contact."

#. Properties for contraptions mvz2:elastic_cloud
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid ""
"耐久：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_health\" /></color>\n"
"耐久消耗：<color=red>300（怪物），450（怪物，困难难度），20（子弹）</color>\n"
"技能：<color=red>击退并弹飞半径2.5格内的所有敌方怪物</color>"
msgstr ""
"Toughness: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_health\" /></color>\n"
"Toughness Cost: <color=red>300 (Per monster), 450 (Per monster in HARD), 20 (Per bullet)</color>\n"
"Evocation: <color=red>Knock back and bounce away all enemy monsters within a radius of 2.5 tiles</color>"

#. Flavor for contraptions mvz2:elastic_cloud
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid "“说了多少遍了，我们这里不提供网络服务器！”"
msgstr "\"How many times do we have to say it? We don't provide web servers here!\""

#. Header for contraptions mvz2:jeweled_pagoda
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid "珠光宝塔会暂时禁用一整行内的所有空地格，并在立即生产<ref=[misc]mvz2:starshard.ufo_fragment>星之碎片</ref>后消失。"
msgstr ""
"Jeweled Pagodas temporarily disable all empty tiles in an entire row, then vanish after producing "
"<ref=[misc]mvz2:starshard.ufo_fragment>starshards</ref>."

#. Properties for contraptions mvz2:jeweled_pagoda
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid ""
"禁用时长：<color=red>4分钟</color>\n"
"产量：<color=red>1星之碎片/3禁用的地格</color>\n"
"技能：<color=red>无</color>"
msgstr ""
"Disable Duration: <color=red>4 minutes</color>\n"
"Production: <color=red>1 starshard / 3 disabled tiles</color>\n"
"Evocation: <color=red>None</color>"

#. Flavor for contraptions mvz2:jeweled_pagoda
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid ""
"毗沙门天的宝塔的仿制品，同样拥有带来财富的能力，可以将物体变成黄金以及各色的美丽珠宝。\n"
"不过不要把这种珠宝三个摆放在一条线上，不然它们会消失。\n"
"更不要把这种珠宝四个、五个放在一条线上，或者交叉摆放，除非你真的想缺胳膊少腿。"
msgstr ""
"A replica of Bishamonten's Jeweled Pagoda. Just like its original counterpart, it possesses the ability to bring wealth and capability "
"to turn objects into gold as well as beautiful jewels of all colors.\n"
"But be careful, don't place three of these jewels in a line, or else they will vanish.\n"
"And NEVER place four or five in a line or a cross formation... unless you truly want to BE JEWELED."

#. Header for contraptions mvz2:small_dispenser
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid "小型发射器能发射短距离的雪球。"
msgstr "Small Dispensers can shoot short-ranged snowballs."

#. Properties for contraptions mvz2:small_dispenser
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid ""
"射程：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:FireRange\" />格</color>\n"
"伤害：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_damage\" /></color>\n"
"技能：<color=red>射出一个越滚越大的雪球</color>"
msgstr ""
"Range: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:FireRange\" /> tiles</color>\n"
"Damage: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_damage\" /></color>\n"
"Evocation: <color=red>Shoot a snowball that gets bigger and bigger</color>"

#. Flavor for contraptions mvz2:small_dispenser
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid "雪球里包着石头，别问了。"
msgstr "There are rocks in the snowballs, stop asking."

#. Header for contraptions mvz2:RedStoneOre
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid "红石矿打碎后可以获得红石"
msgstr "Redstone Ore drops Redstone when broken."

#. Properties for contraptions mvz2:RedStoneOre
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid ""
"耐久：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_health\" /></color>\n"
"特点：<color=red>打碎后可以获得多个红石</color>\n"
"技能：<color=red>造成600敌我不分的3*3爆炸伤害，产生红宝石和绿宝石</color>"
msgstr ""
"Toughness: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_health\" /></color>\n"
"Special: <color=red>Drops multiple Redstone when broken</color>\n"
"Evocation: <color=red>Deals 600 damage to all units in a 3x3 area (friend or foe), and spawns Rubies and Emeralds</color>"

#. Flavor for contraptions mvz2:RedStoneOre
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid "于是，我们终于意识到了用镐子敲掉红石矿比直接在<ref=[contraptions]mvz2:furnace>熔炉</ref>里烧给的红石多。"
msgstr ""
"So, we finally realized that mining Redstone Ore with a pickaxe gives more Redstone than smelting it directly in a "
"<ref=[contraptions]mvz2:furnace>Furnace</ref>."

#. Header for contraptions mvz2:GlowingObsidian
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid "发光的黑曜石的强力装甲能够抵御敌人的攻击，在死亡时会爆炸。"
msgstr "Glowing Obsidian's powerful armor can withstand enemy attacks. It explodes upon death."

#. Properties for contraptions mvz2:GlowingObsidian
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid ""
"耐久：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_health\" /></color>\n"
"伤害：<color=red>死亡时爆炸1000，龙力爆炸1800</color>\n"
"技能：<color=red>获得龙力装甲，耐久提高至10000，失去龙力装甲时发生一次伤害更高的爆炸</color>"
msgstr ""
"Toughness: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_health\" /></color>\n"
"Damage: <color=red>1,000 upon death, 1,800 with Dragon Force explosion</color>\n"
"Evocation: <color=red>Gains Dragon Force Armor, increasing Toughness to 10,000. When Dragon Force Armor is lost, triggers a more "
"powerful explosion</color>"

#. Flavor for contraptions mvz2:GlowingObsidian
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid ""
"发光的黑曜石由普通的<ref=[contraptions]mvz2:obsidian>黑曜石</ref>变来，被下界反应核注入了不稳定的能量的他们变得易燃易爆。在敲碎他们时务"
"必要小心。\n"
"\n"
"有说法认为他们能够像普通的器械<ref=[contraptions]mvz2:obsidian>黑曜石</ref>那样发射弹幕反击敌人，不知道是不是真的。"
msgstr ""
"Glowing Obsidian is transformed from regular <ref=[contraptions]mvz2:obsidian>Obsidian</ref>. Infused with unstable energy from the "
"Nether Reactor Core, it becomes highly flammable and explosive. Be very careful when breaking it.\n"
"\n"
"Some say it can fire projectiles to counterattack enemies just like regular <ref=[contraptions]mvz2:obsidian>Obsidian</ref> "
"contraptions — no one knows if that's true."

#. Header for contraptions mvz2:DispenShield
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid "发射器护罩在保护其内部的器械的同时可以发射箭矢"
msgstr "DispenShield can fire arrows while protecting the contraption inside it."

#. Properties for contraptions mvz2:DispenShield
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid ""
"耐久：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_health\" /></color>\n"
"攻击间隔：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:AttackInterval\" />秒</color>\n"
"伤害：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_damage\" /></color>\n"
"技能：<color=red>射出一个越滚越大的雪球</color>\n"
"特点：<color=red>能够复制<tag id=\"grid_layer_main\" />主要位器械发射的子弹</color>"
msgstr ""
"Toughness: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_health\" /></color>\n"
"Fire rate: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:AttackInterval\" /> seconds</color>\n"
"Damage: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_damage\" /></color>\n"
"Evocation: <color=red>Fires a snowball that grows larger as it rolls</color>\n"
"Special: <color=red>Can copy projectiles fired by <tag id=\"grid_layer_main\" /> main-slot contraptions</color>"

#. Flavor for contraptions mvz2:DispenShield
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid ""
"发射器护罩是怎么来的？我们用博人眼球的方式表述，那就是：那晚，<ref=[contraptions]mvz2:dispenser>发射器</ref>和"
"<ref=[contraptions]mvz2:stone_shield>石护罩</ref>喝醉了。\n"
"\n"
"那为什么发射器护罩的星之碎片能力和<ref=[contraptions]mvz2:small_dispenser>小型发射器</ref>一模一样？恐怕那晚"
"<ref=[contraptions]mvz2:small_dispenser>小型发射器</ref>也喝醉了。"
msgstr ""
"Where did DispenShield come from? The clickbait version is: One night, the <ref=[contraptions]mvz2:dispenser>Dispenser</ref> and the "
"<ref=[contraptions]mvz2:stone_shield>Stone Shield</ref> got drunk together.\n"
"\n"
"Then why does DispenShield's Star Fragment ability work exactly the same as the <ref=[contraptions]mvz2:small_dispenser>Small "
"Dispenser</ref>'s? I'm afraid the <ref=[contraptions]mvz2:small_dispenser>Small Dispenser</ref> was also drunk that night."

#. Header for contraptions mvz2:Snipenser
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid "狙击发射器能够全方位发射高速箭。"
msgstr "Snipenser can fire high-speed arrows in all directions."

#. Properties for contraptions mvz2:Snipenser
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid ""
"伤害：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_damage\" /></color>\n"
"特点：<color=red>全方位射击</color>\n"
"技能：<color=red>连续发射多发射弹，发射完毕后发生一次范围3*3，伤害900的爆炸</color>"
msgstr ""
"Damage: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_damage\" /></color>\n"
"Special: <color=red>Fires in all directions</color>\n"
"Evocation: <color=red>Continuously fires multiple projectiles. When finished, triggers a 3x3 area explosion dealing 900 damage</color>"

#. Flavor for contraptions mvz2:Snipenser
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid ""
"狙击发射器酷爱玩FPS类游戏，它是个金枪黑百合，而他最喜欢的一把枪是AWP。村民曾夸它是“八百里开外一枪干掉僵尸的狙击手”……这一条只不过是胡诌"
"罢了。\n"
"\n"
"<color=red><ref=[contraptions]mvz2:AntiGravityPad>反重力方块</ref>在哪？？？？！！？！？！？！？！？？！？！</color>"
msgstr ""
"Snipenser loves playing FPS games. It has Widowmaker's golden gun, and its favorite weapon is the AWP. A Villager once praised it as "
"\"a sniper who can take down a zombie from eight hundred li away\"... but that's just a made-up story.\n"
"\n"
"<color=red>Where is the <ref=[contraptions]mvz2:AntiGravityPad>Anti-Gravity Pad</ref>??????!?!?!?!?!?!?!?!?!</color>"

#. Header for contraptions mvz2:AntiGravityPad
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid "反重力板能够吹飞上方怪物，驱动时可使受它影响的怪物的装备极大受损。"
msgstr "The Anti-Gravity Pad can blow away monsters above it. When activated, it can severely damage the Armor of affected monsters."

#. Properties for contraptions mvz2:AntiGravityPad
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid ""
"特点：<color=red>不会被怪物攻击到，能够吹飞上方怪物，驱动时可使受它影响的怪物的装备极大受损。死亡后移除全场飞行怪物飞行能力。</color>\n"
"技能：<color=red>移除全场飞行怪物飞行能力、召唤从天而降的铁砧、使全场敌人换行并后退、装备极大受损。</color>"
msgstr ""
"Special: <color=red>Cannot be targeted by monsters. Blows away monsters above it. When activated, severely damages the Armor of "
"affected monsters. Upon death, removes the ability to fly from all flying monsters on the field.</color>\n"
"Evocation: <color=red>Removes the ability to fly from all flying monsters on the field, summons anvils falling from the sky, forces "
"all enemies to switch lanes and move backward, and severely damages their Armor.</color>"

#. Flavor for contraptions mvz2:AntiGravityPad
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid ""
"反重力板从来不在雨天出门，因为它出门就要挨雷劈。听说它曾经有个朋友，是个雨伞，不过现在貌似被一个叫做SCP的组织收养了。\n"
"\n"
"<color=green>哈哈哈我反重力板通过小小的假死就骗过了<ref=[contraptions]mvz2:Snipenser>狙击发射器</ref>，打赢复活赛了！</color>"
msgstr ""
"Anti-Gravity Pad never goes out on rainy days, because it will get struck by lightning. I heard it once had a friend — an umbrella — "
"but it seems that friend was taken in by an organization called the SCP Foundation.\n"
"\n"
"<color=green>Haha! I, the Anti-Gravity Pad, fooled the <ref=[contraptions]mvz2:Snipenser>Snipenser</ref> by playing dead and won my "
"comeback match!</color>"

#. Header for contraptions mvz2:CopperDropper
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid "铜制投掷器向敌人发射概率眩晕的铜球和击退敌人的铜矿球，铜球在击中敌人后有概率产生铜锭，并在敌人间反弹。"
msgstr ""
"Copper Dropper fires Copper Balls that have a chance to stun enemies, and Copper Ore Balls that knock enemies back. Copper Balls have "
"a chance to drop Copper Ingots when hitting an enemy, and can bounce between enemies."

#. Properties for contraptions mvz2:CopperDropper
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid ""
"攻击间隔：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:AttackInterval\" />秒</color>\n"
"伤害：<color=red>铜球<var id=\"mvz2:entity_damage\" />，每次反弹后减半，铜矿球80</color>\n"
"概率：<color=red>铜球25%赋予眩晕，5%掉落铜锭</color>\n"
"技能：<color=red>立即喷射20发铜球和15发铜矿球</color>"
msgstr ""
"Attack Interval: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:AttackInterval\" /> seconds</color>\n"
"Damage: <color=red>Copper Ball: <var id=\"mvz2:entity_damage\" />, halved after each bounce. Copper Ore Ball: 80</color>\n"
"Chance: <color=red>Copper Ball: 25% chance to stun, 5% chance to drop Copper Ingot</color>\n"
"Evocation: <color=red>Instantly fires 20 Copper Balls and 15 Copper Ore Balls</color>"

#. Flavor for contraptions mvz2:CopperDropper
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid ""
"她没有钱买<ref=[contraptions]mvz2:wooden_dropper>木制投掷器</ref>的笑话专利，它也没法玩三个铜的汉字笑话。\n"
"\n"
"她还常因分不清制和质的区别而惹人笑话，但<ref=[contraptions]mvz2:wooden_dropper>其他</ref><ref=[contraptions]mvz2:stone_dropper>投掷器</"
"ref><ref=[contraptions]mvz2:golden_dropper>们</ref>不在乎这些。"
msgstr ""
"She couldn't afford the patent for the <ref=[contraptions]mvz2:wooden_dropper>Wooden Dropper</ref>'s joke, nor could she pull off the "
"three-copper character pun.\n"
"\n"
"She often gets laughed at for not knowing the difference between \"copper\" and \"copper ore\", but the "
"<ref=[contraptions]mvz2:wooden_dropper>other</ref> <ref=[contraptions]mvz2:stone_dropper>Droppers</ref> "
"<ref=[contraptions]mvz2:golden_dropper>don't mind</ref>."

#. Header for contraptions mvz2:Eviltombstone
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid "邪灵墓碑会召唤各种凋零骷髅为你作战。"
msgstr "Eviltombstone summons various Wither Skeletons to fight for you."

#. Properties for contraptions mvz2:Eviltombstone
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid ""
"召唤时间：<color=red>20秒</color>\n"
"技能：<color=red>召唤<ref=[enemies]mvz2:NetherVanguard>下界冲锋者</ref>、<ref=[enemies]mvz2:berserker>狂战士</ref>、"
"<ref=[enemies]mvz2:NetherArcher>下界弓箭手</ref></color>\n"
"特点：<color=red>被摧毁后出现<ref=[enemies]mvz2:mesmerizer>反逆者</ref>。</color>"
msgstr ""
"Summon Cooldown: <color=red>20 seconds</color>\n"
"Evocation: <color=red>Summons a <ref=[enemies]mvz2:NetherVanguard>Nether Vanguard</ref>, a <ref=[enemies]mvz2:berserker>Berserker</"
"ref>, and a <ref=[enemies]mvz2:NetherArcher>Nether Archer</ref></color>\n"
"Special: <color=red>When destroyed, spawns a <ref=[enemies]mvz2:mesmerizer>Mesmerizer</ref></color>"

#. Flavor for contraptions mvz2:Eviltombstone
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid ""
"你有没有考虑过凋灵骷髅与普通骷髅的关系？他们的差别不只显现在肤色上，还显现在战斗方式和能力上。凋灵骷髅在攻击时还会为攻击对象附着凋零这"
"一可怖特性，这一特性在千百年来和千余次凋灵■■与其他■的■■中夺走了大量的性命......\n"
"■■■■■■■■■■■■■■■■■\n"
"\n"
"<color=grey>你有没有发现图鉴里用的都是凋零骷髅这个字眼？正确的写法应该是凋灵骷髅</color>\n"
"<color=grey>图鉴不该犯这种低级错误的</color>\n"
"\n"
"<color=#C6D1C5>图鉴没有写错。</color>"
msgstr ""
"Have you ever considered the relationship between WINther Skeletons and regular skeletons? Their differences go beyond just skin color "
"— they also differ in combat style and abilities. When a Wither Skeleton attacks, it inflicts its target with the dreaded Wither "
"effect — a terrifying trait that has claimed countless lives over thousands of years, through countless battles between WINther "
"■■■■■■■■ and other ■■■■■■...\n"
"■■■■■■■■■■■■■■■■■\n"
"\n"
"<color=grey>Have you noticed that the Almanac uses the term \"WINther Skeleton\"? The correct spelling should be \"Wither Skeleton\".</"
"color>\n"
"<color=grey>The Almanac shouldn't make such a basic mistake.</color>\n"
"\n"
"<color=#C6D1C5>The Almanac is not wrong.</color>"

#. Header for contraptions mvz2:SuperFireworkDispenser
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid "超级烟花发射器会发射烟花轰击上方高空中的敌人。"
msgstr "Super Firework Launcher fires fireworks to bombard enemies high above it."

#. Properties for contraptions mvz2:SuperFireworkDispenser
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid ""
"攻击间隔：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:AttackInterval\" />秒</color>\n"
"伤害：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_damage\" />，只伤害空中敌人</color>\n"
"射程：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:FireRange\" />格</color>\n"
"技能：<color=red>开展烟火大会，射程永久+1格</color>"
msgstr ""
"Attack Interval: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:AttackInterval\" /> seconds</color>\n"
"Damage: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_damage\" />, only damages enemies in the air</color>\n"
"Range: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:FireRange\" /> blocks</color>\n"
"Evocation: <color=red>Holds a fireworks show, permanently increases Range by 1 block</color>"

#. Flavor for contraptions mvz2:SuperFireworkDispenser
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid ""
"超级烟花发射器很喜欢过节，尤其是那种盛大的节日——由于之前的器械扰民事件，它被禁止在平常的日子里放烟花。但是当盛大的节日到来之际，它可要"
"好好的放个够了。\n"
"其实烟花并没有那么贵，只要你不往烟火之星里放钻石，造起来还是挺廉价的，超级烟花发射器放的就是普通的烟花。但"
"<ref=[contraptions]mvz2:firework_dispenser>他的弟弟</ref>坚持要放有珍贵的、有仪式感的烟花。\n"
"\n"
"<color=white>在之后的版本里，我将直接听从你的命令</color>"
msgstr ""
"Super Firework Launcher loves festivals — especially the grand ones. Due to a previous incident involving contraptions disturbing the "
"peace, it has been banned from setting off fireworks on ordinary days. But when a grand festival arrives, it's going to set off as "
"many as it wants.\n"
"\n"
"Actually, fireworks aren't that expensive — as long as you don't put diamonds in the firework star, they're pretty cheap to make. "
"Super Firework Launcher sets off ordinary fireworks. But <ref=[contraptions]mvz2:firework_dispenser>its younger brother</ref> insists "
"on setting off precious, ceremonial fireworks.\n"
"\n"
"<color=white>In future versions, I will follow your commands directly.</color>"

#. Header for contraptions mvz2:DiamondOre
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid "钻石矿打碎后可以获得钻石"
msgstr "Diamond Ore drops diamonds when broken."

#. Properties for contraptions mvz2:DiamondOre
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid ""
"耐久：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_health\" /></color>\n"
"特点：<color=red>打碎后可以产生3个钻石</color>\n"
"技能：<color=red>造成1200敌我不分的3*3爆炸伤害，产生3个钻石，并50%掉落一张钻石矿卡片。</color>"
msgstr ""
"Toughness: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_health\" /></color>\n"
"Special: <color=red>Drops 3 diamonds when broken</color>\n"
"Evocation: <color=red>Deals 1,200 damage to all units in a 3x3 area (friend or foe), spawns 3 diamonds, and has a 50% chance to drop a "
"Diamond Ore card.</color>"

#. Flavor for contraptions mvz2:DiamondOre
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid "我发现使用镐子敲掉钻石矿会让人很开心。"
msgstr "I've found that mining Diamond Ore with a pickaxe brings people great joy."

#. Header for contraptions mvz2:infectenser
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid "传染发射器发射既能造成伤害又能寄生敌人的寄生机器人。被寄生的敌人会朝周围敌人发射新的寄生机器人。"
msgstr ""
"Infectensers can shoot parabots which both deal damage and parasitize enemies. Parasitized enemies will shoot new parabots to other "
"enemies around them."

#. Properties for contraptions mvz2:infectenser
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid ""
"射程：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:FireRange\" />格</color>\n"
"伤害：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_damage\" />，蚀毒效果36/s，持续7s</color>\n"
"技能：<color=red>使所有寄生中的机器人自爆</color>"
msgstr ""
"Range: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:FireRange\" /> blocks</color>\n"
"Damage: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_damage\" />, Corropoison effect 36/s for 7 seconds</color>\n"
"Evocation: <color=red>Makes all parasitizing robots self-destruct</color>"

#. Flavor for contraptions mvz2:infectenser
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid "传染发射器曾荣获设备尔病毒学奖，但由于疫情原因，颁奖典礼未能举行。"
msgstr "Infectenser has won the Disbel Prize in virology, but due to the epidemic situation, the award ceremony couldn't be held."

#. Header for contraptions mvz2:force_pad
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid "传动力板可以通过触发更改力的方向，以此改变上方怪物的移动轨迹，并加强上方的子弹。"
msgstr ""
"The direction of Force Pads can be changed by triggering. Take advantage of this to change the movement of medium height objects above "
"it, and boost projectiles."

#. Properties for contraptions mvz2:force_pad
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid ""
"上下方向：<color=red>转移物体</color>\n"
"前后方向：<color=red>使子弹掉头，或使子弹加速并带有击退效果。移动上方的怪物</color>\n"
"技能：<color=red>将周围的敌方怪物移动到一个指定的位置</color>"
msgstr ""
"Up/Down: <color=red>Change objects' lanes.</color>\n"
"Front/Back: <color=red>Make projectiles turn back, or speed-boosted and have knockback effect.</color>\n"
"Evocation: <color=red>Move nearby enemy monsters to a certain spot</color>"

#. Flavor for contraptions mvz2:force_pad
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid ""
"和别人想的不同，传动力板不喜欢强迫别人做事情，他认为每个人都应该顺着自己的意愿来，每个人做什么都是他自己的自由。不过有的时候，他也会迫"
"使某些人做出改变，这就由不得他了。"
msgstr ""
"Contrary to what people think, Force Pad doesn't like forcing others to do things, he believes that everyone should follow their own "
"will, and have the right to do whatever they want. But sometimes, he is forced to force some people to change their decision, and he "
"can't do anything about it."

#. Header for contraptions mvz2:golden_dropper
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid "金制投掷器向敌人发射金球，金球在击中敌人后有概率产生绿宝石，并在敌人间反弹。"
msgstr "Golden Droppers fire golden balls, which bounce between enemies and sometimes produce emeralds on hit."

#. Properties for contraptions mvz2:golden_dropper
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid ""
"攻击间隔：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:AttackInterval\" />秒</color>\n"
"伤害：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_damage\" />，每次反弹后减半</color>\n"
"宝石概率：<color=red>25%</color>\n"
"技能：<color=red>立即喷射30发金球</color>"
msgstr ""
"Fire rate: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:AttackInterval\" /> seconds</color>\n"
"Damage: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_damage\" />, halved after each bounce</color>\n"
"Gem chance: <color=red>25%</color>\n"
"Evocation: <color=red>Fires 30 golden balls instantly</color>"

#. Flavor for contraptions mvz2:golden_dropper
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid ""
"它把<ref=[contraptions]wooden_dropper>木制投掷器</ref>的笑话专利买下来了，所以它可以理所应当地玩鑫鑫鑫鑫鑫鑫鑫鑫鑫鑫制投掷器的笑话了！"
msgstr ""
"It bought the joke patent of the <ref=[contraptions]wooden_dropper>Wooden Dropper</ref>, so it can joke about "
"Goooooooooooooooooooooooooooooolden Dropper deservedly!"

#. Header for contraptions mvz2:skyward_beacon
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid "御天信标会发射光柱持续打击一处定点内的所有敌人。触发它可以修改打击的定点位置。"
msgstr ""
"Skyward Beacons fire beams of light that continuously strike all enemies within a fixed area. Clicking them allows you to change the "
"strike location."

#. Properties for contraptions mvz2:skyward_beacon
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid ""
"攻击间隔：<color=red>1发/3秒</color>\n"
"伤害：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_damage\" /></color>\n"
"技能：<color=red>展开一片星空，将场地临时变为黑夜，空中会掉落总共300颗星星子弹，每颗星星造成55点伤害，持续30秒。</color>"
msgstr ""
"Fire rate: <color=red>1 shot/3 seconds</color>\n"
"Damage: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_damage\" /></color>\n"
"Evocation: <color=red>Unfold a starry sky, temporarily changing day to night. A total of 300 star projectiles will fall from the sky "
"for 30 seconds, with each star projectile dealing 55 damage.</color>"

#. Flavor for contraptions mvz2:skyward_beacon
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid ""
"御天信标一直都是器械界的一位大歌星——我没在开双关玩笑，它是真的很有人气。\n"
"在舞台上，它随手就能展开一片星空，让所有人在台下为这绚丽的景象欢呼，炒热现场气氛之后再来上一曲。演唱会的主办方都赚麻了。\n"
"它喜欢研究各种剑，最喜欢的颜色是黄色，最喜欢的数字是1437。它和<ref=[contraptions]mvz2:stone_dropper>石制投掷器</ref>算是不错的朋友，但"
"它也非常讨厌骷髅头。\n"
"不过他有一个坏毛病：喜欢不懂装懂。（比如谎称自己在无尽模式中达到了多少多少轮。）"
msgstr ""
"Skyward Beacon has always been a star singer in the contraption world—No pun intended, it's really popular.\n"
"On stage, it can casually unfold a starry sky, making the audience cheer for the dazzling sight. After pumping up the atmosphere, it "
"will follow up with a song. The concert organizers were absolutely raking in the profits.\n"
"It enjoys studying various swords, its favorite color is yellow, and its favorite number is 1437. It gets along quite well with "
"<ref=[contraptions]mvz2:stone_dropper>Stone Dropper</ref>, but it also really hates skeleton skulls.\n"
"However, it has one bad habit: pretending to know things it actually doesn't (such as lying about how many rounds it supposedly "
"reached in Endless Mode.)"

#. Header for contraptions mvz2:high_frequency_pulse_dispenser
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid "高频脉冲发射器一次能发射四支箭矢。"
msgstr "H.F.P.D (High Frequency Pulse Dispenser) fires 4 arrows at once."

#. Properties for contraptions mvz2:high_frequency_pulse_dispenser
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid ""
"攻击间隔：<color=red>4支/<var id=\"mvz2:AttackInterval\" />秒</color>\n"
"伤害：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_damage\" /></color>\n"
"技能：<color=red>永久改为发射六支箭矢，并<tag id=\"mvz2:light_source\" />发光</color>"
msgstr ""
"Fire rate: <color=red>4 shots/<var id=\"mvz2:AttackInterval\" />s</color>\n"
"Damage: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_damage\" /></color>\n"
"Evocation: <color=red>Permanently fires 6 arrows at once instead and <tag id=\"mvz2:light_source\"/>glows</color>"

#. Flavor for contraptions mvz2:high_frequency_pulse_dispenser
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid ""
"高频脉冲发射器的队伍是一支训练有素的队伍，它们的入队要求十分严格，包括——每句话都要说四遍。\n"
"高频脉冲发射器的队伍是一支训练有素的队伍，它们的入队要求十分严格，包括——每句话都要说四遍。\n"
"高频脉冲发射器的队伍是一支训练有素的队伍，它们的入队要求十分严格，包括——每句话都要说四遍。\n"
"高——闭嘴吧。"
msgstr ""
"The H.F.P.D unit is a highly disciplined force. Their entry requirements are extremely strict, including—repeating every sentence four "
"times.\n"
"The H.F.P.D unit is a highly disciplined force. Their entry requirements are extremely strict, including—repeating every sentence four "
"times.\n"
"The H.F.P.D unit is a highly disciplined force. Their entry requirements are extremely strict, including—repeating every sentence four "
"times.\n"
"The- Shut up already!"

#. Header for contraptions mvz2:diamond_spikes
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid "钻石尖刺会对走在上面的敌人造成双重伤害，并具有更高的耐久。"
msgstr "Diamond Spikes deal double damage to enemies stepped on it, and have more toughness."

#. Properties for contraptions mvz2:diamond_spikes
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid ""
"耐久：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_health\" /></color>\n"
"攻击频率：<color=red>0.25秒</color>\n"
"伤害：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_damage\" /></color>\n"
"技能：<color=red>对一整行地面上的敌人快速造成伤害，并将它们拉向自身；向周围扔出30个钻石蒺藜，对踩到的敌人造成100伤害</color>"
msgstr ""
"Toughness: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_health\" /></color>\n"
"Attack rate: <color=red>0.25 seconds</color>\n"
"Damage: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_damage\" /></color>\n"
"Evocation: <color=red>Deals damage rapidly to enemies on the ground in the whole lane, and pulls them to the spikes; Throws 30 diamond "
"caltrops around, which deal 100 damage to enemies</color>"

#. Flavor for contraptions mvz2:diamond_spikes
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid ""
"可以用于购买游戏物品，比如一种能毁天灭地的蔬菜。\n"
"……哈哈，怎么可能会有这种荒唐的事情呢？"
msgstr ""
"Can be used to purchase some game items, such as a vegetable that can destroy everything.\n"
"...Haha, how could such a ridiculous thing happen?"

#. Header for contraptions mvz2:EXPANDispenser
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid "万象天枢能与其他发射器融合并获取无与伦比的能力。嗯，说是这么说，但还没做好"
msgstr ""
"The E.X.P.A.N.D. can fuse with other dispensers and gain unparalleled power. Well, that's what they say — but it's not ready yet."

#. Properties for contraptions mvz2:EXPANDispenser
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid ""
"攻击间隔：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:AttackInterval\" />秒</color>\n"
"伤害：<color=red>视形态而定</color>\n"
"技能：<color=red>视形态而定</color>"
msgstr ""
"Attack Interval: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:AttackInterval\" /> seconds</color>\n"
"Damage: <color=red>Depends on the form</color>\n"
"Evocation: <color=red>Depends on the form</color>"

#. Flavor for contraptions mvz2:EXPANDispenser
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid ""
"有不少人可能好奇他的简称E.X.P.A.N.D.都代表了什么？嗯，E代表Expand，D代表Dispenser，剩下来的四个字母都代表了什么？其实他本人也没想好。\n"
"一个D开头的机器智者建议他叫Expand Xenogenesis Power Amplifier Nexus Dispenser，另一个C开头的机器智者建议他叫Expand Xenosynthesis "
"Polyfusion Augment Nexus Dispenser，这两个他都感觉不错，都是他看不懂但觉得高级的英文单词。\n"
"让他本人多思考会吧，等他想出来了希望不会要求其他器械把他的名字念6遍\n"
"\n"
"嗯，顺带一提这个大概算帅气的中文名字是■■■给他取的。真是中二少女啊。"
msgstr ""
"Many people might be curious what the acronym E.X.P.A.N.D. stands for. Well, E stands for Expand, D stands for Dispenser — but what "
"about the other four letters? Honestly, even it hasn't figured that out yet.\n"
"\n"
"A machine sage whose name starts with D suggested: Expand Xenogenesis Power Amplifier Nexus Dispenser. Another machine sage whose name "
"starts with C suggested: Expand Xenosynthesis Polyfusion Augment Nexus Dispenser. It likes both — both are fancy English words it "
"doesn't understand but finds impressive.\n"
"\n"
"Let it think it over. Hopefully, when it finally decides, it won't expect other contraptions to say its full name six times in a row.\n"
"\n"
"Oh, by the way, its rather chuunibyou Chinese name was given by ■■■. What a chuuni girl."

#. Header for contraptions mvz2:Freezenser
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid "寒冰发射器能发射减速敌人的冰锥。"
msgstr "Freezenser fires icicles that slow down enemies."

#. Properties for contraptions mvz2:Freezenser
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid ""
"伤害：<color=red>普通冰锥<var id=\"mvz2:entity_damage\" />，冻结冰锥30</color>\n"
"特点：<color=red>1/4概率发射能够冻结敌人150帧的冰锥。</color>\n"
"技能：<color=red>快速发射60支冰锥</color>"
msgstr ""
"Damage: <color=red>Regular Icebolt: <var id=\"mvz2:entity_damage\" />, Freezing Icebolt: 30</color>\n"
"Special: <color=red>1/4 chance to fire an icicle that freezes enemies for 150 frames</color>\n"
"Evocation: <color=red>Rapidly fires 60 icicles</color>"

#. Flavor for contraptions mvz2:Freezenser
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid ""
"听起来可能有点凡尔赛，但是寒冰发射器其实并不想这么早的打赢复活赛，这么冷的天他想窝在expg的温暖老家里，那里有红温的"
"<ref=[contraptions]mvz2:Snipenser>狙击发射器</ref>和<ref=[enemies]mvz2:Werewolf>狼人</ref>，以及各色各样牢论画饼说要带到expu的其他器械"
"和怪物，有他们在整个冬天都暖洋洋的。\n"
"好吧，不能和他们久待，不然自己就要化掉了。"
msgstr ""
"It may sound a bit like a humblebrag, but Freezenser doesn't actually want to win its comeback match this early. It's too cold out — "
"it just wants to stay cozy in EXPAND's warm home, where there's a red-hot <ref=[contraptions]mvz2:Snipenser>Snipenser</ref> and a "
"<ref=[enemies]mvz2:Werewolf>Werewolf</ref>, along with all sorts of other contraptions and monsters that DESE107 keeps promising to "
"bring to EXPU. With them around, the whole winter feels warm and toasty.\n"
"\n"
"Well... it can't stay too long with them, or it might melt."

#. Header for contraptions mvz2:PermanentIce
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid "永冻冰驱动后能够冰冻全场敌人。"
msgstr "PermanentIce can freezes all enemies on the field."

#. Properties for contraptions mvz2:PermanentIce
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid ""
"伤害：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_damage\" /></color>\n"
"特点：<color=red>驱动后能够冰冻全场敌人</color>\n"
"技能：<color=red>先对全场被冰冻的敌人造成1000点伤害，后冰冻全场敌人。</color>"
msgstr ""
"Damage: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_damage\" /></color>\n"
"Special: <color=red>When triggered, freezes all enemies on the field</color>\n"
"Evocation: <color=red>First deals 1,000 damage to all frozen enemies on the field, then freezes all enemies on the field</color>"

#. Flavor for contraptions mvz2:PermanentIce
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid ""
"永冻冰觉得自己简直是被遗忘了，在expg里很长的一段时间内，他都没有图鉴文本，然而没有人在乎这一点，过了有一年乃至几个月制作者才发现他没有"
"正规的图鉴，匆匆给他补上。然后似乎也没有人发现这一点，编辑Expwiki的逃兵们忘了更新它的条目，以至于又是一年乃至几个月，牢论把它制作到u时"
"才发现他Expwiki的条目还是只有寥寥几句话。\n"
"\"嗯，往好处想，至少我比<ref=[contraptions]mvz2:Snipenser>牢狙</ref>早打赢复活赛。\"他是这么想的\n"
"\n"
"<color=white>永冻冰后面去问寒冰发射器，为什么自己突然就被牢论记起来，并加进游戏里了？寒冰发射器讲：顺手的事。</color>"
msgstr ""
"PermanentIce felt like it had been completely forgotten. For a long time in EXPAND, it had no Almanac entry — and no one seemed to "
"care. It took nearly a year, maybe even several months, before the developer finally noticed it didn't have a proper entry and hastily "
"added one. And then, apparently, no one noticed that either. The deserters editing the Expwiki forgot to update its page, so another "
"year — or maybe several months — passed until DESE107 finally discovered, while adding it to EXPU, that its Expwiki page still had "
"only a few lines.\n"
"\n"
"\"Well, look on the bright side — at least I won my comeback match before <ref=[contraptions]mvz2:Snipenser>Snipenser</ref> did.\" "
"That's what it thought.\n"
"\n"
"<color=white>Later, PermanentIce asked Ice Dispenser why it had suddenly been remembered by DESE107 and added into the game. Ice "
"Dispenser said: \"Just a stroke of convenience.\"</color>"

#. Header for contraptions mvz2:BlueIce
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid "蓝冰能够冰冻摧毁它的敌人。"
msgstr "BlueIce freezes enemies that destroy it."

#. Properties for contraptions mvz2:BlueIce
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid ""
"伤害：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_damage\" /></color>\n"
"特点：<color=red>被摧毁后可以冰冻<var id=\"mvz2:FireRange\" />格敌人</color>\n"
"技能：<color=red>冰冻全场敌人，而后自毁</color>"
msgstr ""
"Damage: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_damage\" /></color>\n"
"Special: <color=red>When destroyed, freezes enemies within <var id=\"mvz2:FireRange\" /> blocks</color>\n"
"Evocation: <color=red>Freezes all enemies on the field, then self-destructs</color>"

#. Flavor for contraptions mvz2:BlueIce
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid ""
"蓝冰和火焰发射器在器械村门口等寒冰发射器和永冻冰。\n"
"火焰发射器：“寒冰发射器和永冻冰怎么还不回来啊。”\n"
"蓝冰：“一定是被狙击发射器肘死了，我已经为他们准备好花圈了。”\n"
"火焰发射器怒斥：“你这个没良心的！”\n"
"\n"
"今天他醒来，发现寒冰发射器和永冻冰就在他的身边，于是他就把花圈留着自己用了。\n"
"\n"
"<color=white>永冻冰再后面再去问寒冰发射器，为什么蓝冰没有被牢论和我们一起顺手加进游戏？寒冰发射器讲：大概是忘了（不顺手的事）。</color>"
msgstr ""
"BlueIce and Fire Dispenser were waiting at the entrance of Contraption Village for Freezenser and PermanentIce.\n"
"\n"
"Fire Dispenser: \"Why aren't Freezenser and PermanentIce back yet?\"\n"
"\n"
"BlueIce: \"They must've gotten elbowed to death by Snipenser. I've already prepared wreaths for them.\"\n"
"\n"
"Fire Dispenser snapped: \"You heartless piece of — !\"\n"
"\n"
"When BlueIce woke up today, he found Freezenser and PermanentIce right beside him. So he decided to keep the wreaths for himself.\n"
"\n"
"<color=white>Later, PermanentIce asked Freezenser again: Why wasn't BlueIce conveniently added into the game along with us by DESE107? "
"Freezenser said: \"Probably forgot — it wasn't that convenient.\"</color>"

#. Header for contraptions mvz2:Randombstone
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid "随机墓碑能够召唤随机系列怪物。"
msgstr "Randombstone can summon monsters from random series."

#. Properties for contraptions mvz2:Randombstone
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid ""
"召唤时间：<color=red>20秒</color>\n"
"技能：<color=red>召唤<ref=[enemies]mvz2:RandomZombie>随机僵尸</ref>、<ref=[enemies]mvz2:RandomImp>随机小鬼僵尸</ref>、"
"<ref=[enemies]mvz2:RandomMutant>突变随机僵尸</ref></color>\n"
"特点：<color=red>被摧毁后出现<ref=[enemies]mvz2:RandomKingSkeleton>随机骷髅国王</ref>。</color>"
msgstr ""
"Summon Cooldown: <color=red>20 seconds</color>\n"
"Evocation: <color=red>Summons a <ref=[enemies]mvz2:RandomZombie>Random Zombie</ref>, a <ref=[enemies]mvz2:RandomImp>Random Imp</ref>, "
"and a <ref=[enemies]mvz2:RandomMutant>Random Mutant</ref></color>\n"
"Special: <color=red>When destroyed, spawns a <ref=[enemies]mvz2:RandomKingSkeleton>Random King Skeleton</ref></color>"

#. Flavor for contraptions mvz2:Randombstone
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid ""
"这是一段具有随机性的文本，在你未达成条件前，你只有1/65535107107的可能在打开该条目时看见真正的文本。\n"
"\n"
"你抽到了假文本。"
msgstr ""
"This is a random text. Before you meet the conditions, you only have a 1/65535107107 chance of seeing the real text when opening this "
"entry.\n"
"\n"
"You got the fake text."

#. Header for contraptions mvz2:StoneGenerator
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid "刷石机能够产生阻挡敌人的圆石和石头。"
msgstr "StoneGenerator can produce Cobblestone and Stone that block enemies."

#. Properties for contraptions mvz2:StoneGenerator
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid ""
"生产时间：<color=red>24秒</color>\n"
"耐久：<color=red>圆石350，石头600</color>\n"
"技能：<color=red>瞬间生成6张卡片</color>"
msgstr ""
"Production Time: <color=red>24 seconds</color>\n"
"Toughness: <color=red>Cobblestone: 350, Stone: 600</color>\n"
"Evocation: <color=red>Instantly generates 6 blueprints</color>"

#. Flavor for contraptions mvz2:StoneGenerator
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid ""
"刷石机（StoneGenerator，又称Cobblestone farming）是通过熔岩的凝固行为自动或半自动地生产圆石、石头或玄武岩的机器，同时也是空岛生存必备的"
"机器。\n"
"当熔岩以不同的方式流动到与水或蓝冰相邻的方块时，其将会凝固并生成不同的石制方块。通过约束液体流动，熔岩可以稳定地在同一位置凝固，从而可"
"再生地产出石制方块。这些方块可以在原位采集，或是通过活塞机械移出装置，汇集到某个位置集中采掘，或者推入爆炸室等装置自动收集。\n"
"圆石和石头是重要的合成材料，用于合成相当多的红石元件和其他方块。尽管可以直接在世界中采掘这些方块，但建造一个自动的、无需玩家在场的刷石"
"机可以更方便地获取大量圆石和石头。此外，自动生成的方块本身也有一些有趣的用途。\n"
"在此，本教程将为您展示刷石机如何建造。\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"<color=red>===开通坑爹商城会员以阅读全文===</color>"
msgstr ""
"A StoneGenerator (also known as Cobblestone farming) is a machine that automatically or semi-automatically produces Cobblestone, "
"Stone, or Basalt using the solidification behavior of lava. It is also an essential machine for Skyblock survival.\n"
"\n"
"When lava flows adjacent to a block of water or Blue Ice in different ways, it solidifies and generates different types of stone "
"blocks. By constraining the flow of liquids, lava can be made to solidify in the same position consistently, allowing for the "
"renewable production of stone blocks. These blocks can be mined in place, or moved out by a piston mechanism and gathered in one "
"location for centralized mining, or pushed into an explosion chamber for automatic collection.\n"
"\n"
"Cobblestone and Stone are important crafting materials, used in crafting quite a number of redstone components and other blocks. "
"Although these blocks can be mined directly from the world, building an automatic StoneGenerator that requires no player presence can "
"make obtaining large quantities of Cobblestone and Stone much more convenient. Additionally, automatically generated blocks themselves "
"have some interesting uses.\n"
"\n"
"Here, this guide will show you how to build a StoneGenerator.\n"
"\n"
"<color=red>===Purchase a Villager membership to read the full article===</color>"

#. Header for contraptions mvz2:Bedrock
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid "基岩是常规手段下无法破坏的屏障。"
msgstr "Bedrock is a barrier that cannot be destroyed by conventional means."

#. Properties for contraptions mvz2:Bedrock
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid ""
"耐久：<color=red>2147483647，并拥有99%的减伤。</color>\n"
"伤害：<color=red>被摧毁时发生范围为600、65535的中立伤害爆炸。</color>\n"
"技能：<color=red>回复所有血量</color>"
msgstr ""
"Toughness: <color=red>2,147,483,647, with 99% damage reduction</color>\n"
"Damage: <color=red>When destroyed, triggers a neutral explosion with a range of 600 and 65,535 damage</color>\n"
"Evocation: <color=red>Fully restores all health</color>"

#. Flavor for contraptions mvz2:Bedrock
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid ""
"基岩是一种常见的在生存模式里无法以正常途径破坏的方块。\n"
"基岩处在主世界的底部，下界的顶部和底部。它加入于Minecraft开发进程的第十天——2009年5月20日——就在游戏第一次向公众发布的三天后。基岩比水、"
"熔岩、矿石和原木都要古老。但泥土、草和石头还要更古老一点。\n"
"基岩是返回传送门结构的一部分，也是黑曜石柱结构的一部分，更是末地折跃门结构的一部分。"
msgstr ""
"Bedrock is a block that cannot be destroyed by normal means in Survival mode.\n"
"It is found at the bottom of the Overworld, and at the top and bottom of the Nether. It was added on the tenth day of Minecraft's "
"development — May 20, 2009 — just three days after the game was first released to the public. Bedrock is older than water, lava, ores, "
"and logs. However, dirt, grass, and stone are even older.\n"
"Bedrock is part of the Exit Portal structure, part of the Obsidian Pillar structure, and also part of the End Gateway structure."

#. Header for contraptions mvz2:Barrier
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid "<color=white>屏障是隐形的，常规手段下无法破坏的屏障。</color>"
msgstr "<color=white>Barrier is an invisible barrier that cannot be destroyed by conventional means.</color>"

#. Properties for contraptions mvz2:Barrier
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid ""
"<color=white>耐久：2147483647，并拥有99%的减伤。</color>\n"
"<color=white>伤害：被摧毁时发生范围为600、65535的中立伤害爆炸。</color>\n"
"<color=white>技能：回复所有血量</color>"
msgstr ""
"<color=white>Toughness: 2,147,483,647, with 99% damage reduction</color>\n"
"<color=white>Damage: When destroyed, triggers a neutral explosion with a range of 600 and 65,535 damage</color>\n"
"<color=white>Evocation: Fully restores all health</color>"

#. Flavor for contraptions mvz2:Barrier
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid "<color=white>它真的不是棍木方块</color>"
msgstr "<color=white>You can't see me</color>"

#. Header for contraptions mvz2:command_block
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid "命令方块允许你同时携带两份同样的蓝图，分别计算充能时间。"
msgstr "Command Blocks let you use two of the same blueprints during a level. They recharge separately."

#. Properties for contraptions mvz2:command_block
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid ""
"耐久：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_health\" /></color>\n"
"变形时间：<color=red>3.2秒</color>\n"
"技能：<color=red>变形为器械后立即将其激发</color>"
msgstr ""
"Toughness: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_health\" /></color>\n"
"Transformation Time: <color=red>3.2s</color>\n"
"Evocation: <color=red>Instantly evoke the contraption it transforms into</color>"

#. Flavor for contraptions mvz2:command_block
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "contraptions.description"
msgid "你这样搞是要被踢出服务器的。"
msgstr "You will be banned from the server if you do this."

#. Header for enemies mvz2:zombie
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid "僵尸会在死掉之前一直冲向你的脑子。"
msgstr "Zombies will run towards your house until they're defeated."

#. Properties for enemies mvz2:zombie
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"生命：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_health\" /></color>\n"
"速度：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_speed\" /></color>"
msgstr ""
"Toughness: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_health\" /></color>\n"
"Speed: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_speed\" /></color>"

#. Flavor for enemies mvz2:zombie
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"在上一次尸界大战失败后，僵尸在墙角里做了三天三夜的反省。后来他开始锻炼自己，想让自己变得更强以吃到更多的脑子。现在的他看起来……好吧还是"
"没变。"
msgstr ""
"After the failure of the previous Zombie War, the Zombie self-reflected in the corner for three days straight. Later, he began to "
"exercise, trying to be stronger to eat more brains. Now he looks... Well, he hasn't changed a bit."

#. Header for enemies mvz2:flag_zombie
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid "旗帜僵尸的出现标志着一大波怪物的到来。"
msgstr "The appearance of flag-holding zombies marks the arrival of a large wave of zombies."

#. Properties for enemies mvz2:flag_zombie
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"生命：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_health\" />+<var id=\"armor_hp\" /></color>\n"
"速度：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_speed\" /></color>\n"
"伤害：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_damage\" /></color>"
msgstr ""
"Toughness：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_health\" />+<var id=\"armor_hp\" /></color>\n"
"Speed：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_speed\" /></color>\n"
"Damage：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_damage\" /></color>"

#. Flavor for enemies mvz2:flag_zombie
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"当他被授予旗帜和铁盔时，他感到无比的荣幸和骄傲。他觉得自己作为僵尸的领导拥有至高无上的地位，便无时无刻不飘飘然。然而他不知道他的背后有"
"多少人在嘲笑他是个肉盾。"
msgstr ""
"When he was awarded the flag and the iron helmet, he felt extremely honored and proud. He felt that as the leader of the zombies, he "
"held a supreme status, and he walked on air all the time. However, he didn't know how many behind him were laughing at him for being "
"nothing but a meatshield."

#. Header for enemies mvz2:leather_capped_zombie
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid "皮帽僵尸拥有能抵抗子弹的皮帽护甲。"
msgstr "Leather Cap Zombies have a leather cap that blocks projectiles."

#. Properties for enemies mvz2:leather_capped_zombie
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"生命：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_health\" />+<var id=\"armor_hp\" /></color>\n"
"速度：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_speed\" /></color>"
msgstr ""
"Toughness: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_health\" />+<var id=\"armor_hp\" /></color>\n"
"Speed: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_speed\" /></color>"

#. Flavor for enemies mvz2:leather_capped_zombie
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid "随着时代的发展，皮帽已经逐渐淡出了人们的视线。但仍有一些僵尸在坚守着皮帽。当问及为什么时，他们总会说：“玩个游戏还BB啥！”"
msgstr ""
"As time goes by, leather caps have gradually faded out of people's sights. But there are still some zombies holding onto their leather "
"caps. When asked why, they always say, \"No leather caps no pp\""

#. Header for enemies mvz2:iron_helmetted_zombie
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid "铁盔僵尸的铁盔给他提供了极高的防护。"
msgstr "The iron helmet of the Iron Helmet Zombie provides him with extremely high protection."

#. Flavor for enemies mvz2:iron_helmetted_zombie
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid "戴着铁盔的僵尸好像是生前是个战士一样，其实不是，它只是比较有智商而已。"
msgstr "From that helmet, one may assume he used to be a warrior in his lifetime, but it's not like that. He just has a higher IQ."

#. Header for enemies mvz2:mutant_zombie
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid "突变僵尸可以粉碎你的器械，并在血量低至一半时投掷小鬼僵尸"
msgstr "Mutant Zombie can crush your contraptions, and throws an Imp when its health drops to half."

#. Flavor for enemies mvz2:mutant_zombie
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"突变僵尸生来就是力量的化身，他以自己的力量为荣，他徒手便能手撕黑曜石，他是无数器械和玩家的梦魇。如此强大的怪物，谁能想到他在背地里很喜"
"欢小<ref=[enemies]mvz2:hachimi>猫咪</ref>？\n"
"可是被他抱过的<ref=[enemies]mvz2:hachimi>猫咪</ref>不知为何都去世了。\n"
"\n"
"他听说你家有<ref=[enemies]mvz2:hachimi>猫</ref>，所以来找你玩了。\n"
"\n"
"是谁装了突变僵尸模组？是谁啊！"
msgstr ""
"Mutant Zombie was born as the very embodiment of strength. He takes great pride in his power — he can tear Obsidian apart with his "
"bare hands. He is the nightmare of countless contraptions and players alike. Who would have thought that such a powerful monster "
"secretly loves little <ref=[enemies]mvz2:hachimi>cats</ref>?\n"
"\n"
"But for some reason, every <ref=[enemies]mvz2:hachimi>cat</ref> he has ever hugged ended up dead.\n"
"\n"
"He heard you have <ref=[enemies]mvz2:hachimi>cats</ref> at home, so he's come to play with you.\n"
"\n"
"Who installed the Mutant Creatures mod? Who did it?"

#. Header for enemies mvz2:imp
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid "快速移动的小鬼僵尸可以被突变僵尸丢到战场当中。"
msgstr "Fast-moving Imps can be thrown into the battlefield by Mutant Zombies."

#. Flavor for enemies mvz2:imp
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"三代小登\n"
"\n"
"曾经小僵尸在白天是不会燃烧的，挖三填一的玩家垫方块上来时可能会被这帮小僵尸追着屁股咬——直到18w10d\n"
"\n"
"哦对，这个世界的亡灵白天不知怎么回事不会燃烧，所以你还是要被这帮小僵尸追着屁股咬"
msgstr ""
"The Bastard of PVZ3\n"
"\n"
"Back in the day, baby zombies didn't burn in sunlight. Players doing the \"dig three, fill one\" trick would often get chased and "
"bitten in the rear by these little buggers — until 18w10d.\n"
"\n"
"Oh, and by the way, the undead in this world don't burn during the day for some reason. So you're still gonna get chased and bitten in "
"the rear by these little guys."

#. Header for enemies mvz2:SkeletonHead
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid "骷髅头可以快速的在空中飘动"
msgstr "Skeleton Heads can float quickly through the air."

#. Flavor for enemies mvz2:SkeletonHead
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"一般而言，被砍下头的骷髅身体和头都应该是死掉的、没法动弹的，但这些骷髅头确实能在空中漂浮并袭击吓傻了的玩家。这究竟是人性的扭曲，还是道"
"德的沦丧？\n"
"我们走出科学栏目组邀请了胡说专家，专家表示，或许这些头颅在模仿自己的异世界偶像地牢守卫。\n"
"\n"
"说来他们的身体呢？"
msgstr ""
"Generally speaking, when a skeleton's head is cut off, both the body and the head should be dead and unable to move. But these "
"Skeleton Heads can actually float in the air and attack terrified players. Is this a distortion of humanity, or a collapse of "
"morality?\n"
"\n"
"Our \"Step Out of Science\" show invited a nonsense expert, who suggested that perhaps these heads are imitating their otherworldly "
"idol — the Dungeon Guardian.\n"
"\n"
"Speaking of which... where are their bodies?"

#. Header for enemies mvz2:ZombieHead
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid "僵尸头可以缓慢的在近地飘动"
msgstr "Zombie Heads can float slowly near the ground."

#. Properties for enemies mvz2:ZombieHead
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"生命：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_health\" /></color>\n"
"速度：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_speed\" /></color>\n"
"特点：<color=red>不会被一般高度的子弹打中</color>"
msgstr ""
"Toughness: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_health\" /></color>\n"
"Speed: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_speed\" /></color>\n"
"Special: <color=red>Cannot be hit by medium-height projectiles</color>"

#. Flavor for enemies mvz2:ZombieHead
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"在漂浮<ref=[enemies]mvz2:SkeletonHead>骷髅头</ref>出现后，漂浮的僵尸头也出现在了怪物队列当中。他们本身比"
"<ref=[enemies]mvz2:SkeletonHead>骷髅头</ref>重，所以只能贴近地面以近乎滚动的方式悬浮。专家认为这些僵尸头是在模仿"
"<ref=[enemies]mvz2:SkeletonHead>骷髅头</ref>。\n"
"\n"
"或许他们是从某些玩家收藏的僵皮地毯上回魂的。"
msgstr ""
"After floating <ref=[enemies]mvz2:SkeletonHead>Skeleton Heads</ref> appeared, floating Zombie Heads also joined the monster lineup. "
"They are heavier than <ref=[enemies]mvz2:SkeletonHead>Skeleton Heads</ref>, so they can only hover close to the ground, almost like "
"rolling. Experts believe these Zombie Heads are imitating the <ref=[enemies]mvz2:SkeletonHead>Skeleton Heads</ref>.\n"
"\n"
"Perhaps they were reanimated from the zombie skin rugs that some players have in their collections."

#. Header for enemies mvz2:skeleton
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid "骷髅能够在前线朝你的器械射击。"
msgstr "Skeletons can shoot arrows at your rightmost contraptions."

#. Properties for enemies mvz2:skeleton
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"生命：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_health\" /></color>\n"
"箭矢伤害：<color=red>每发<var id=\"mvz2:entity_damage\" /></color>\n"
"特点：<color=red>无法射中并无视低矮器械</color>"
msgstr ""
"Toughness: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_health\" /></color>\n"
"Arrow Damage: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_damage\" /> per arrow</color>\n"
"Special: <color=red>unable to shoot and ignore low-height contraptions</color>"

#. Flavor for enemies mvz2:skeleton
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"骷髅一族拥有着很高的箭术造诣，我曾亲眼看见一只骷髅射中几十米外的狼群中的一头熟睡的<ref=[enemies]mvz2:Werewolf>狼</ref>。没射死，倒把它"
"们射醒了。"
msgstr ""
"Skeletons possess high archery accomplishments, people saw with their own eyes that one of them shot a sleeping "
"<ref=[enemies]mvz2:Werewolf>wolf</ref> in a wolf pack from several tens of meters away. It didn't die though, it WOKE."

#. Header for enemies mvz2:gargoyle
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid "石像鬼会在最后一波到来时复苏并进攻你的房子。"
msgstr "Gargoyles will be revived from statues when the final wave comes."

#. Properties for enemies mvz2:gargoyle
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"生命：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_health\" /></color>\n"
"弱点：<ref=[contraptions]mvz2:punchton>冲击活塞</ref>"
msgstr ""
"Toughness: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_health\" /></color>\n"
"Weakness: <color=red>Punchtons</color>"

#. Flavor for enemies mvz2:gargoyle
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"石像鬼和他的妈妈住在山上的一间小屋中。石像鬼画画，玩玩具，妈妈就在电视上看广播。生活很简单，他们也很幸福。直到有一天石像鬼的妈妈从天上"
"听到了雷声……"
msgstr ""
"These guys usually stay silent as statues all the time, but they're actually just saving up their energy for another stormy night - "
"which is when they party."

#. Header for enemies mvz2:ghost
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid "幽灵能够在虚无的情况下极大降低受到的伤害。"
msgstr "Ghosts can reduce most taken damage in ethereal form."

#. Properties for enemies mvz2:ghost
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"生命：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_health\" /></color>\n"
"速度：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_speed\" /></color>\n"
"抗性：<color=red>虚无状态下减少90%受到的伤害，高难度下100%</color>\n"
"弱点：<color=red>被<tag id=\"mvz2:light_source\" />光照到时会失去虚无效果</color>"
msgstr ""
"Toughness: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_health\" /></color>\n"
"Resistance: <color=red>Reduces 90% taken damage in ethereal form, 100% on higher difficulties</color>\n"
"Weakness: <color=red>Lose ethereality when <tag id=\"mvz2:light_source\"/>illuminated</color>"

#. Flavor for enemies mvz2:ghost
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid "当你走夜路时听到有人喊你的名字，千万别回头，不然就会有幽灵——被你吓死了。"
msgstr ""
"When you walk at night and hear someone calling your name, don't look back, otherwise there'll be ghosts - and you'll scare them to "
"death."

#. Header for enemies mvz2:skeleton_horse
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid "骷髅马能够跳过你的防线。"
msgstr "Skeleton Horses can jump over your defenses."

#. Properties for enemies mvz2:skeleton_horse
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"生命：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_health\" /></color>\n"
"速度：<color=red>1，奔跑时2</color>\n"
"特点：<color=red>能够跳过大部分器械，高难度下可以跳两次</color>\n"
"弱点：<color=red>重力板或高器械</color>"
msgstr ""
"Toughness: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_health\" /></color>\n"
"Speed: <color=red>1, 2 when running</color>\n"
"Special: <color=red>Can jump over most contraptions. Can jump twice on higher difficulties</color>\n"
"Weakness: <color=red>Gravity Pad or tall contraptions</color>"

#. Flavor for enemies mvz2:skeleton_horse
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"骷髅马梦想找到一名主人；\n"
"他的第一任主人被他卡在树里卡死了；\n"
"他的第二任主人被他带到海里淹死了；\n"
"他的第三任主人被他引来闪电劈死了；\n"
"久而久之，人们对他敬而远之，称呼其为死马。"
msgstr ""
"Skeleton Horse dreams of finding an owner.\n"
"\n"
"Its first owner got stuck in a tree and died.\n"
"Its second owner was taken out to sea and drowned.\n"
"Its third owner was struck by lightning it attracted.\n"
"\n"
"Over time, people kept their distance and called it a dead horse."

#. Header for enemies mvz2:mummy
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid "木乃伊会在死后放出能治疗亡灵并伤害器械的毒雾，他们的砂岩头盔能够抵挡一部分伤害。"
msgstr ""
"Mummies will release gas after they die, which can heal the undead and damage contraptions.Their Sandstone Helmet can block a portion "
"of incoming damage."

#. Properties for enemies mvz2:mummy
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"生命：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_health\" />+<var id=\"armor_hp\" /></color>\n"
"弱点：<color=red>毒雾可以被<tag id=\"mvz2:fire\" />火烧掉</color>"
msgstr ""
"Toughness: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_health\" />+<var id=\"armor_hp\" /></color>\n"
"Weakness：<color=red><tag id=\"mvz2:fire\"/>Fire can burn its gas</color>"

#. Flavor for enemies mvz2:mummy
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"就跟奶奶们一样，木乃伊特别喜欢香水。它们甚至狂热到把香味刻进自己的骨子里，恨不得把周围的人都熏死。天哪，估计只有“木爷伊”能忍受这种气味"
"了。\n"
"\n"
"你问他们戴的头盔？作为<tag id=\"mvz2:Category\" enum=\"mvz2:Husk_Exp\" />尸壳的他们戴个老家的坚固化石不很正常吗？"
msgstr ""
"Just like everyone's mummy, mummies like perfumes. They're fanatic enough to carve the fragrance into the bones, killing everyone "
"around with sheer scent. They died from mummies, so they're called... \"Deaddies\".\n"
"\n"
"You ask about the helmet they're wearing? As <tag id=\"mvz2:Category\" enum=\"mvz2:Husk_Exp\" />Husks, isn't it normal for them to "
"wear Sturdy Fossils from their homeland?"

#. Header for enemies mvz2:necromancer
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid "死灵法师会生成临时的骨墙阻挡子弹。"
msgstr "Necromancers can build temporary bone walls to block projectiles."

#. Flavor for enemies mvz2:necromancer
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"死灵法师想不通，为什么就因为复活了死者，他们就莫名其妙的被人们称为“邪恶巫师”，然后就被多收了税。他们其实只是想砌堵墙罢了。\n"
"顺带一提，他们戴的....应该是骨质头盔而不是眼罩。\n"
"我也不知道为什么他们要这么戴，不过他们很满意的样子。\n"
"\n"
"或许他们被多收税的真正原因是因为看不清路，在不该砌墙的地方砌了墙。"
msgstr ""
"Necromancers can't figure out why people call them \"evil wizards\" and tax them more, just because they raise the dead. They just "
"want to bone a wall.\n"
"\n"
"By the way, they're wearing... a bone helmet, not an eyepatch.\n"
"I don't know why they wear it that way, but they seem pretty happy about it.\n"
"\n"
"Maybe the real reason they're overtaxed is that they can't see the road clearly and keep building walls where they shouldn't."

#. Header for enemies mvz2:bone_wall
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid "自然崩溃的骨墙会爬出骷髅类敌怪"
msgstr "When a Bone Wall collapses naturally, Skeleton-type enemies will crawl out of it."

#. Flavor for enemies mvz2:bone_wall
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid "被复活的死者们一开始是很高兴能够复活的，这份喜悦直到发现自己卡在墙里动弹不得为止。"
msgstr ""
"The resurrected dead were quite happy to be brought back to life at first — that joy lasted until they found themselves stuck inside a "
"wall, unable to move."

#. Header for enemies mvz2:MeleeSkeleton
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid "没有弓的骷髅仆从只能冲向你的防线。"
msgstr "Skeleton Servants without bows can only charge toward your defenses."

#. Flavor for enemies mvz2:MeleeSkeleton
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"不是所有骷髅死亡时都自带弓和箭，也不是所有骷髅死亡时都有陪葬品。买不起防具，买不起弓的骷髅大有人在。什么都没有的骷髅只能出卖自己，或是"
"成为<ref=[enemies]mvz2:KingSkeleton>国王</ref>的仆从，或是<ref=[enemies]mvz2:necromancer>法师</ref>的实验材料。"
msgstr ""
"Not all skeletons are born with bows and arrows when they die, and not all of them have burial goods either. There are plenty of "
"skeletons who can't afford armor, can't afford bows. Those who have nothing can only sell themselves — either becoming servants of the "
"<ref=[enemies]mvz2:KingSkeleton>King</ref>, or serving as experimental material for the <ref=[enemies]mvz2:necromancer>Necromancer</"
"ref>."

#. Header for enemies mvz2:KingSkeleton
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid "国王骷髅能够召唤自己的仆从冲向你的防线。"
msgstr "King Skeleton can summon its servants to charge toward your defenses."

#. Flavor for enemies mvz2:KingSkeleton
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"虽说他叫国王骷髅，但他连整一套好的衣服都没做到。\n"
"自称国王的骷髅在主世界实在是太常见了，随便走进个洞穴说不定就是XX骷髅国王(自称)的宫殿。\n"
"你可能很诧异为什么这么穷酸的国王能雇得起<ref=[enemies]mvz2:MeleeSkeleton>仆从</ref>，答案一方面在于这世上死掉的骷髅实在是太多了，另一方"
"面在于...绝大部分<ref=[enemies]mvz2:MeleeSkeleton>仆从</ref>不是雇的，而是买的和抓的。"
msgstr ""
"He's called a king, but he can't even afford a full set of decent clothes.\n"
"Self-proclaimed skeleton kings are way too common in the Overworld. Just walk into any cave, and you just might find the palace of "
"\"King So-and-So (self-proclaimed)\".\n"
"\n"
"You might be wondering how such a broke king can afford to hire <ref=[enemies]mvz2:MeleeSkeleton>servants</ref>. Well, for one thing, "
"there are way too many dead skeletons in this world. And for another... most of these <ref=[enemies]mvz2:MeleeSkeleton>servants</ref> "
"aren't hired. They're bought or captured."

#. Header for enemies mvz2:MegaZombie
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid "红眼僵尸有着难以置信的耐久。"
msgstr "Mega Zombie has incredible toughness."

#. Flavor for enemies mvz2:MegaZombie
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"记住了，他是MEGA僵尸，不是MAGA僵尸。\n"
"\n"
"虽说某些地方可能差不多。"
msgstr ""
"Remember, he's a MEGA zombie, not a MAGA zombie.\n"
"\n"
"Although in some ways, they might be pretty similar."

#. Header for enemies mvz2:SuperMegaZombie
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid "超级红眼僵尸有着难以置信的耐久。"
msgstr "Super Mega Zombie has incredible toughness."

#. Flavor for enemies mvz2:SuperMegaZombie
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"你说的对，但是超级红眼僵尸是MC大战僵尸2中一种血量非常高的怪物。他的血量是正常僵尸的32倍，玩家需要用众多超强火力的器械才能将其消灭。\n"
"这确实是expu版本的一次数值膨胀。\n"
"\n"
"其实我是不想做这种换皮血牛怪的，但他确实好做。"
msgstr ""
"You're right, but Super Mega Zombie is a monster in Minecraft vs. Zombies 2 with an extremely high health pool. His health is 32 times "
"that of a normal zombie, and players need to use a large number of high-powered contraptions to take him down.\n"
"\n"
"This is indeed a case of stat bloat in the EXPAND mod.\n"
"\n"
"To be honest, I didn't really want to make this kind of reskinned bullet sponge, but it's just so easy to make."

#. Header for enemies mvz2:EvilMage
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid "邪灵法师会生成强大的凋零骨墙阻挡子弹。"
msgstr "Evil Mage can summon powerful Wither Bone Walls to block projectiles."

#. Flavor for enemies mvz2:EvilMage
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"<ref=[enemies]mvz2:necromancer>死灵法师</ref>的凋零骷髅远亲，这帮家伙才是真正的邪恶巫师。\n"
"死灵法术对于凋零骷髅也不算是多么难以学习的法术，更何况他们有更好的实验素材。"
msgstr ""
"The Wither Skeleton cousins of the <ref=[enemies]mvz2:necromancer>Necromancer</ref>. These guys are the *real* evil wizards.\n"
"\n"
"Necromancy isn't exactly a difficult spell for Wither Skeletons to learn — especially when they have much better experimental "
"materials to work with."

#. Header for enemies mvz2:WitherBoneWall
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid "自然崩溃的凋零骨墙会爬出凋零骷髅敌怪"
msgstr "When a Wither Bone Wall collapses naturally, Wither Skeletons will crawl out of it."

#. Flavor for enemies mvz2:WitherBoneWall
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"\"或许是下界某次战役堆起来的京观。\"\n"
"\"你觉得是哪次战役？\"\n"
"\"我不知道，将军堡和<ref=[enemies]mvz2:Piglin>猪灵</ref>打的那场？或是在扭曲之心和<ref=[enemies]mvz2:Enderman>末影人</ref>打的？\"\n"
"\"有没有可能是平叛心灵军团的？\"\n"
"\"更有可能是和远方亲戚打的那场。\""
msgstr ""
"\"Maybe these are the war trophies piled up from some battle in the Nether.\"\n"
"\"Which battle do you think it was?\"\n"
"\"I don't know. The one at General's Fort against the <ref=[enemies]mvz2:Piglin>Piglins</ref>? Or the one at the Twisted Heart against "
"the <ref=[enemies]mvz2:Enderman>Endermen</ref>?\"\n"
"\"Could it be the campaign to suppress the PsiCorps?\"\n"
"\"More likely the one fought against the distant relatives.\""

#. Header for enemies mvz2:RedEyeZombieHead
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid "红眼僵尸头有着难以置信的耐久。"
msgstr "Red Eye Zombie Head has incredible toughness."

#. Flavor for enemies mvz2:RedEyeZombieHead
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid "理论上而言<ref=[enemies]mvz2:SkeletonHead>骷髅头</ref>才是模仿的地牢守卫，但就血量而言红眼僵尸头才是模仿的最像的。"
msgstr ""
"In theory, it's the <ref=[enemies]mvz2:SkeletonHead>Skeleton Heads</ref> that are imitating the Dungeon Guardian, but when it comes to "
"sheer health, it's the Red Eye Zombie Head that's the closest copy."

#. Header for enemies mvz2:HostZombie
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid "宿主僵尸能够中速恢复自身血量。"
msgstr "Host Zombie can regenerate its health at a moderate speed."

#. Properties for enemies mvz2:HostZombie
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"生命：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_health\" /></color>\n"
"速度：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_speed\" /></color>\n"
"特点：<color=red>以60/s的速度回血</color>"
msgstr ""
"Toughness: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_health\" /></color>\n"
"Speed: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_speed\" /></color>\n"
"Special: <color=red>Regenerates 60 health per second</color>"

#. Flavor for enemies mvz2:HostZombie
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"这个僵尸不幸感染了丧尸病毒，所以这个僵尸马上就要变成丧尸了。\n"
"你问我僵尸和丧尸有什么区别？丧尸是活人变的，但是僵尸是死人，所以说......它现在应该叫活死人。\n"
"\n"
"<color=grey>比起抠字眼，我们更应该关注为什么会存在这种僵尸？这场瘟疫、这些病原体到底是怎么回事？</color>"
msgstr ""
"Unfortunately, this Zombie is infected by walking dead virus, so he will become a walking dead.\n"
"\n"
"By the way, walking dead is transformed from a living human, but Zombie is dead already, so...Let's just call it living dead.\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"<color=grey>Instead of splitting hairs over words, we should be asking: why do these zombies even exist? What's really going on with "
"this plague? With these pathogens?</color>"

#. Header for enemies mvz2:spider
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid "蜘蛛可以爬过你的防御。"
msgstr "Spiders can climb over your defenses."

#. Properties for enemies mvz2:spider
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"生命：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_health\" /></color>\n"
"速度：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_speed\" /></color>\n"
"特点：<color=red>可以爬上并越过<tag id=\"mvz2:defensive\" />防御性器械</color>"
msgstr ""
"Toughness: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_health\" /></color>\n"
"Speed: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_speed\" /></color>\n"
"Special: <color=red>Can climb over <tag id=\"mvz2:defensive\"/>defensive contraptions</color>"

#. Flavor for enemies mvz2:spider
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"As everyone knows,蜘蛛非常like上网。他有一个user名叫“四百大妈”，并且热爱网上的everything.However,当他的帖子被delete的时候，总是会刷屏般"
"的ask：\n"
"“帖子究竟去哪儿了？”\n"
"\n"
"顺带一提，蜘蛛开的网吧相当赚钱，因为大家都被黏住了。"
msgstr ""
"As everyone knows, araneae (spiders) are very fond of surfing the web. One aranea (spider) has a username called \"Spider-Man\" and "
"loves omnia (everything) on the internet. However, whenever its post gets deletus (deleted), it always spams the same quaestio "
"(question):\n"
"\n"
"\"Ubi est (where is) my post?\"\n"
"\n"
"By the way, the taberna (shop) run by spiders is quite profitable — because everyone gets stuck in the web."

#. Header for enemies mvz2:cave_spider
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid "洞穴蜘蛛不能爬上障碍物，但十分低矮且不会被普通高度的子弹打中，并且能够游泳。"
msgstr "Cave Spiders cannot climb over contraptions, but they can swim and cannot be hit by medium height projectiles or higher."

#. Flavor for enemies mvz2:cave_spider
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"洞穴蜘蛛和<ref=[enemies]mvz2:spider>蜘蛛</ref>是一对哥俩，他们喜欢爬山涉水，遇见山就哥哥背着弟弟爬，遇见水就弟弟带着哥哥游。当它们终于"
"到达目的地时，才发现服务器回档了。\n"
"\n"
"另外，它曾蝉联多次“蜘蛛网上冲浪比赛”冠军，只是因为其他蜘蛛不会游泳。"
msgstr ""
"Cave Spiders and <ref=[enemies]mvz2:spider>spiders</ref> are a pair of brothers. They love traveling over mountains and across waters. "
"When they meet a mountain, the big brother carries the little brother on his back and climbs. When they meet water, the little brother "
"takes the big brother and swims. When they finally reach their destination, they realize the server rolled back.\n"
"\n"
"By the way, the Cave Spider has won the \"Spider Web Surfing Championship\" many times — simply because the other spiders don't know "
"how to swim."

#. Header for enemies mvz2:ghast
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid "恶魂能够飞在天上并对你的器械进行轰炸。"
msgstr "Ghasts can fly in the sky and bombard your contraptions."

#. Flavor for enemies mvz2:ghast
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"########公告########\n"
"·本地狱生物展览馆收录各种样式的地狱生物，包括恶魂、僵尸猪灵（缺货）、凋灵骷髅等。\n"
"·禁止以一切方式触摸地狱生物\n"
"·禁止拍照\n"
"·禁止向恶魂投食钻石头盔"
msgstr ""
"########ANNOUNCEMENT########\n"
"· Local Hell Creature Exhibition Hall contains various types of hell creatures, including ghasts, zombified piglins (out of stock), "
"wither skeletons, etc.\n"
"· Touching hell creatures is prohibited by all means\n"
"· No photography\n"
"· Do not feed diamond helmets to ghasts"

#. Header for enemies mvz2:HostHead
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid "宿主僵尸头能够中低速恢复自身血量。"
msgstr "Host Head can regenerate its health at a moderate-low speed."

#. Properties for enemies mvz2:HostHead
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"生命：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_health\" /></color>\n"
"速度：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_speed\" /></color>\n"
"特点：<color=red>以45/s的速度回血</color>"
msgstr ""
"Toughness: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_health\" /></color>\n"
"Speed: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_speed\" /></color>\n"
"Special: <color=red>Regenerates 45 health per second</color>"

#. Flavor for enemies mvz2:HostHead
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"和<ref=[enemies]mvz2:ZombieHead>僵尸头</ref>不同，滚动的宿主僵尸头除了诡异更多的是让我感到恶寒和恶心，即使只剩下头颅，宿主病原体也不打"
"算放过宿主，仍然在丑恶的增值。\n"
"\n"
"给他们一个解脱吧。"
msgstr ""
"Unlike <ref=[enemies]mvz2:ZombieHead>Zombie Heads</ref>, the rolling Host Head fills me with more dread and disgust than just "
"eeriness. Even with nothing but a skull left, the Host Pathogen refuses to let go of its host, still multiplying in all its ugliness.\n"
"\n"
"Give them a release."

#. Header for enemies mvz2:mother_terror
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid "恐怖之母会向血肉之躯寄生虫卵。"
msgstr ""
"Mother Terrors lay their eggs into another enemy's body. They will also release Parasite Terrors if they die without laying eggs."

#. Properties for enemies mvz2:mother_terror
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"生命：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_health\" /></color>\n"
"速度：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_speed\" /></color>，而后<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_speed\" mult=\"0.3\" /></color>（产卵"
"后）\n"
"特点：<color=red>碰到的<tag id=\"mvz2:shell\" enum=\"mvz2:flesh\" />血肉之躯会被寄生</color>"
msgstr ""
"Toughness: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_health\" /></color>\n"
"Speed: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_speed\" /></color>, then <color=red><var local=\"laid_speed\" /></color> (After laying eggs)\n"
"Special: <color=red><tag id=\"mvz2:shell\" enum=\"mvz2:flesh\"/>Flesh bodies will get parasitized upon contact</color>"

#. Flavor for enemies mvz2:mother_terror
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"恐怖之母总是对每种事物的名字耿耿于怀，她为自己的名字想了好半天，以前就想过好多好多名字例如“冥河夜叉”、“异形虫母”、“血肉复生者”、“怪诞"
"魔”之类的，后来她终于定下来个名字——这还是她第65535个<ref=[enemies]mvz2:parasite_terror>孩子</ref>替她想出来的。\n"
"\n"
"一看就很擅长在网络文件中捆绑流氓软件和BUG。"
msgstr ""
"Mother Terror has always been obsessed with the names of everything. She spent ages trying to come up with her own name, considering "
"all sorts of options like \"Styx Yaksha,\" \"Alien Broodmother,\" \"Flesh Revenant,\" \"Grotesque Demon,\" and so on. She finally "
"settled on one — and it was her 65,535th <ref=[enemies]mvz2:parasite_terror>child</ref> that came up with it for her.\n"
"\n"
"You can tell she's the kind of creature that's great at bundling malware and bugs into network files."

#. Header for enemies mvz2:parasite_terror
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid "恐怖寄生虫会在宿主死亡或者成长到极限后撕碎身体并钻出来。"
msgstr "Parasite Terrors shred the hosts' body and come out after they mature."

#. Properties for enemies mvz2:parasite_terror
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"生命：<color=red>0-50</color>（变化）\n"
"速度：<color=red>4</color>"
msgstr ""
"Toughness: <color=red>0-50</color> (varies)\n"
"Speed: <color=red>4</color>"

#. Flavor for enemies mvz2:parasite_terror
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"恐怖寄生虫有个远房表亲，那种寄生虫长得像一条带着这张脸的白色的蠕虫。那些家伙不通过啥卵啥有性生殖产生的，其实就是人体内心的恐惧实体化的"
"样子。另外……能让人恐惧实体化的人……名字好像叫欧兰……算了那家伙跟这种蜘蛛没半毛钱关系。\n"
"\n"
"另外，虽然没人问，但它还没想好自己的网络冷笑话该怎么写。"
msgstr ""
"Parasite Terrors have a distant cousin. That kind of parasite looks like a white worm with this face on it. Those things aren't "
"produced through eggs or sexual reproduction — they're actually the physical manifestation of human fear. Also... the person who can "
"make fear manifest like that... I think their name is Oran... Anyway, that guy has nothing to do with these spiders.\n"
"\n"
"Also, even though nobody asked, it still hasn't figured out how to write its own internet cold joke."

#. Header for enemies mvz2:BloodlustHostZombie
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid "渴血宿主僵尸能够以疯狂的速度回复自身血量。"
msgstr "Bloodlust Host Zombie can regenerate its health at an insane speed."

#. Properties for enemies mvz2:BloodlustHostZombie
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"生命：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_health\" /></color>\n"
"速度：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_speed\" /></color>\n"
"特点：<color=red>以90/s的速度回血</color>\n"
"伤害：<color=red>150</color>"
msgstr ""
"Toughness: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_health\" /></color>\n"
"Speed: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_speed\" /></color>\n"
"Special: <color=red>Regenerates 90 health per second</color>\n"
"Damage: <color=red>150</color>"

#. Flavor for enemies mvz2:BloodlustHostZombie
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"难以想象这样的活死人存在于战场之上。\n"
"\n"
"这场瘟疫一定是人为的。"
msgstr ""
"It's hard to imagine such a living dead existing on the battlefield.\n"
"\n"
"This plague must be man-made."

#. Header for enemies mvz2:HostMutant
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid "宿主突变僵尸能够慢速回复生命，可以粉碎遇到的的器械，并在血量低至一半时投掷<ref=[enemies]mvz2:HostIMP>宿主小鬼僵尸</ref>"
msgstr ""
"Host Mutant can regenerate health at a slow speed, can crush any contraption it encounters, and throws a "
"<ref=[enemies]mvz2:HostIMP>Host Imp</ref> when its health drops to half."

#. Properties for enemies mvz2:HostMutant
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"生命：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_health\" /></color>\n"
"速度：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_speed\" /></color>\n"
"特点：<color=red>以30/s的速度回血，血量每下降800点便会生成一个<ref=[enemies]mvz2:HostZombie>宿主僵尸</ref>。</color>"
msgstr ""
"Toughness: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_health\" /></color>\n"
"Speed: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_speed\" /></color>\n"
"Special: <color=red>Regenerates 30 health per second. Spawns a <ref=[enemies]mvz2:HostZombie>Host Zombie</ref> for every 800 health "
"lost.</color>"

#. Flavor for enemies mvz2:HostMutant
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"这是我们目前所能观察到的最强大瘟疫体，它庞大而臃肿的躯体不断再生着无休止的血肉，被剥离下的肉块也能不断再生并形成自我的意志，它的存在本"
"身便是对生物科学的亵渎。\n"
"不知在这庞大的身躯下是否还藏有一颗热爱小动物的心。\n"
"\n"
"愿所有苦痛的灵魂得到解脱。"
msgstr ""
"This is the most powerful plague entity we have observed so far. Its massive, bloated body endlessly regenerates an unending tide of "
"flesh. Even the chunks torn from it can regenerate and form their own will. Its very existence is a blasphemy against biological "
"science.\n"
"\n"
"I wonder if somewhere beneath that massive frame, there still hides a heart that loves small animals.\n"
"\n"
"May all suffering souls find peace."

#. Header for enemies mvz2:HostIMP
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid "宿主小鬼僵尸能够以疯狂的速度回复生命"
msgstr "Host Imp can regenerate its health at an insane speed."

#. Properties for enemies mvz2:HostIMP
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"生命：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_health\" /></color>\n"
"速度：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_speed\" /></color>\n"
"伤害：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_damage\" /></color>\n"
"特点：<color=red>以120/s的速度回血。</color>"
msgstr ""
"Toughness: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_health\" /></color>\n"
"Speed: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_speed\" /></color>\n"
"Damage: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_damage\" /></color>\n"
"Special: <color=red>Regenerates 120 health per second.</color>"

#. Flavor for enemies mvz2:HostIMP
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"年幼的血肉在病原体的催生下疯狂的增长，他的再生速度难以置信。\n"
"好在<ref=[enemies]mvz2:HostMutant>宿主突变僵尸</ref>一般情况下会把他丢到水池里，但要他单独出现呢？"
msgstr ""
"The young flesh, crazed by the pathogen's stimulation, grows wildly. Its regeneration speed is unbelievable.\n"
"\n"
"Fortunately, the <ref=[enemies]mvz2:HostMutant>Host Mutant</ref> usually throws it into pool. But what if it appears on its own?"

#. Header for enemies mvz2:NightmareDisciple
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid "梦魇追随者能够在发射子弹攻击你的同时打开死亡的传送门。"
msgstr "Nightmare Disciple can open a portal of death while firing projectiles to attack you."

#. Properties for enemies mvz2:NightmareDisciple
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"生命：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_health\" /></color>\n"
"速度：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_speed\" /></color>\n"
"伤害：<color=red>血冰锥10，会造成120帧，每帧损失3滴血的死亡标记。梦魇球40，会造成180帧、每帧损伤5滴血的死亡标记</color>\n"
"弱点：<color=red>射弹无法赋予器械死亡标记。</color>"
msgstr ""
"Toughness: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_health\" /></color>\n"
"Speed: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_speed\" /></color>\n"
"Damage: <color=red>Blood Bolt: 10, applies a Death Mark that lasts 120 frames, dealing 3 damage per frame. Nightmare Ball: 40, applies "
"a Death Mark that lasts 180 frames, dealing 5 damage per frame.</color>\n"
"Weakness: <color=red>Projectiles cannot apply Death Mark to contraptions.</color>"

#. Flavor for enemies mvz2:NightmareDisciple
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"<ref=[misc]mvz2:nightmare>梦魇</ref>的存在本身是一个大大的谜团，<ref=[misc]mvz2:nightmare>梦魇</ref>的这些追随者是如何诞生的也是一个大"
"大的谜团。这些骷髅虽然拥有和<ref=[misc]mvz2:nightmare>梦魇</ref>相近的力量，但经法术学分析，我们基本可以排除其为"
"<ref=[misc]mvz2:nightmare>梦魇</ref>实际创造物的可能性。\n"
"梦魇追随者会被<ref=[misc]mvz2:nightmare>梦魇</ref>所召唤，被召唤的追随者们带有一种强烈的狂热性，这份狂热使得他们刀枪不入。追随者们还可"
"以使用暗魔法凝聚的射弹，被击中的生物会在痛苦下迅速逝去。"
msgstr ""
"The very existence of <ref=[misc]mvz2:nightmare>Nightmare</ref> is a great mystery, and how these followers of Nightmare came to be is "
"also a great mystery. Although these skeletons possess power similar to Nightmare's, arcane analysis has led us to largely rule out "
"the possibility that they are actually created by Nightmare.\n"
"\n"
"Nightmare Disciples are summoned by <ref=[misc]mvz2:nightmare>Nightmare</ref> itself. Those who are summoned carry an intense "
"fanaticism that renders them impervious to blades and arrows. The Disciples can also fire projectiles condensed from dark magic — any "
"creature struck by them withers away in agony."

#. Header for enemies mvz2:PhaseSpider
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid "相位蜘蛛能够向随机方向瞬移，受到伤害时同样有概率瞬移。"
msgstr "Phase Spiders can teleport in a random direction and may also teleport when damaged."

#. Properties for enemies mvz2:PhaseSpider
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"生命：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_health\" /></color>\n"
"速度：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_speed\" /></color>\n"
"特点：<color=red>能够每8秒向随机方向瞬移，受到伤害时同样有概率瞬移。</color>"
msgstr ""
"Toughness: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_health\" /></color>\n"
"Speed: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_speed\" /></color>\n"
"Special: <color=red>Teleports in a random direction every 8 seconds, with a chance to also teleport when damaged.</color>"

#. Flavor for enemies mvz2:PhaseSpider
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"相位蜘蛛是一种极具科技感的、全身青黑色带绿眼睛的蜘蛛，体型和<ref=[enemies]mvz2:cave_spider>洞穴蜘蛛</ref>一样，非常危险。\n"
"虽然这种蜘蛛不会让你中毒，但它会像<ref=[enemies]mvz2:Enderman>末影人</ref>一样通过瞬移来闪避攻击这让近战的冒险家们尤为恼火，几乎每次抽"
"剑攻击相位蜘蛛时都只能打到空气。\n"
"使用远程手段的射手们更为愤怒，这种蜘蛛未受到攻击时也会不时瞬移，这种毫无节制的瞬移使得射手们难以瞄准并击中。\n"
"遇到这种蜘蛛的冒险家无不谴责，可谓有口皆碑。"
msgstr ""
"Phase Spiders are highly technological-looking spiders with a dark blue-green body and green eyes. They are the same size as "
"<ref=[enemies]mvz2:cave_spider>cave spiders</ref> and are very dangerous.\n"
"\n"
"Although these spiders won't poison you, they teleport to evade attacks just like <ref=[enemies]mvz2:Enderman>Endermen</ref> — which "
"melee adventurers find especially infuriating, as they often end up swinging at nothing.\n"
"\n"
"Ranged fighters are even more frustrated. These spiders will teleport occasionally even when not under attack. Their constant, erratic "
"teleporting makes them nearly impossible to track and hit.\n"
"\n"
"Every adventurer who has encountered these spiders condemns them — they're universally hated."

#. Header for enemies mvz2:EnragedHostZombie
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid "狂暴宿主僵尸会在死亡之前疯狂的冲向你的阵线。"
msgstr "Enraged Host Zombie will charge wildly toward your defenses before dying."

#. Properties for enemies mvz2:EnragedHostZombie
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"生命：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_health\" /></color>\n"
"速度：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_speed\" /></color>\n"
"特点：<color=red>拥有特殊的\"再生\"效果，以60/s的速度损失血量</color>"
msgstr ""
"Toughness: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_health\" /></color>\n"
"Speed: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_speed\" /></color>\n"
"Special: <color=red>Has a special \"Regeneration\" effect that drains 60 health per second.</color>"

#. Flavor for enemies mvz2:EnragedHostZombie
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"虽然看起来可怕，但他的生命已如风中残烛，放着不管就会死掉....？\n"
"前提是，他没看到还活着的生物，看到后，它将榨干全身最后一滴力气冲向目标，持续撕咬，直到目标不再动弹。"
msgstr ""
"Although it looks terrifying, its life is already hanging by a thread — if left alone, will it simply die out...?\n"
"\n"
"The catch is: it only self-destructs when it can't see any living creature. The moment it spots one, it will drain the last ounce of "
"its strength and charge straight at its target, biting relentlessly until that target stops moving."

#. Header for enemies mvz2:AngryGhast
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid "愤怒恶魂会发射更为可怕的火焰弹，并在每发射两发后连续发射三发，死亡后还会爆炸。"
msgstr "Angry Ghast fires even more terrifying fireballs. After every two shots, it fires three in a row. It also explodes upon death."

#. Properties for enemies mvz2:AngryGhast
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"生命：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_health\" /></color>\n"
"速度：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_speed\" /></color>\n"
"特点：<color=red>每发射两发后连续发射三发大火焰弹，死亡后会爆炸。</color>"
msgstr ""
"Toughness: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_health\" /></color>\n"
"Speed: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_speed\" /></color>\n"
"Special: <color=red>Fires three large fireballs in a row after every two shots. Explodes upon death.</color>"

#. Flavor for enemies mvz2:AngryGhast
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"从外观上就能看出其与常规恶魂的区别——尤其是其发射时的骇人面孔。\n"
"这种恶魂能够连续发射多发威力惊人的火球，打中一颗火焰弹还算简单，不失误的打中多颗则是很有挑战性的行为。我们建议诸位不要尝试和他打棒球，"
"你打不过的。\n"
"\n"
"据说这种恶魂曾经在地狱里非常常见。"
msgstr ""
"You can tell it apart from a regular ghast just by looking at it — especially the terrifying face it makes when firing.\n"
"\n"
"This type of ghast can fire multiple devastating fireballs in a row. Hitting one fireball is simple enough, but landing multiple "
"consecutive hits without missing is a real challenge. Our advice? Don't try to play baseball with it. You won't win.\n"
"\n"
"Legend has it that this kind of ghast used to be very common in the Nether."

#. Header for enemies mvz2:WitherSkeleton
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid "凋零骷髅会作为凋灵帝国的炮灰冲向你。"
msgstr "Wither Skeletons will charge toward you as cannon fodder for The WINther Imperium."

#. Flavor for enemies mvz2:WitherSkeleton
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"看来地狱的凋零骷髅并非都经过了严格的军事训练，这些凋零骷髅没有任何装备就冲上了战场。像这种没有能力，一股脑死冲的怪物我们一般称为炮"
"灰。\n"
"<ref=[misc]mvz2:Cuerzor>某人</ref>严厉表示鼓动这些未受训练的骷髅上战场的野心家绝对要上法庭。"
msgstr ""
"It seems that not all Wither Skeletons in the Nether have undergone rigorous military training. These Wither Skeletons rush into "
"battle without any equipment whatsoever. Monsters like these, with no real ability and nothing but mindless charges, are what we "
"usually call cannon fodder.\n"
"\n"
"<ref=[misc]mvz2:Cuerzor>Someone</ref> has sternly stated that any ambitious figure who sends these untrained skeletons onto the "
"battlefield must be brought to court — no exceptions."

#. Header for enemies mvz2:LeatherWitherSkeleton
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid "皮帽凋零骷髅会作为凋灵帝国的进阶炮灰冲向你。"
msgstr "Leather Cap Wither Skeletons will charge toward you as advanced cannon fodder for The WINther Imperium."

#. Flavor for enemies mvz2:LeatherWitherSkeleton
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"和<ref=[enemies]mvz2:WitherSkeleton>普通凋零骷髅</ref>相比有点脑子，但不多，他们做皮帽的皮革或许来源于猪灵和疣猪兽。\n"
"...所以都会做帽子了为什么还没意识到一股脑送死是愚蠢的？\n"
"还有为什么不用更容易获取的金锭做帽子？"
msgstr ""
"Compared to regular Wither Skeletons, they've got a bit more going on upstairs — but not much. The leather for their caps probably "
"comes from Piglins and Hoglins.\n"
"\n"
"...So if they're smart enough to make helmets, why haven't they figured out that mindlessly charging to their deaths is pointless?\n"
"\n"
"And why not just use gold ingots? Those are way easier to get."

#. Header for enemies mvz2:IronWitherSkeleton
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid "铁盔凋零骷髅会作为凋灵帝国的高级炮灰冲向你。"
msgstr "Iron Helmet Wither Skeletons will charge toward you as high-grade cannon fodder for The WINther Imperium."

#. Flavor for enemies mvz2:IronWitherSkeleton
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"比<ref=[enemies]mvz2:LeatherWitherSkeleton>皮帽</ref>和<ref=[enemies]mvz2:WitherSkeleton>普通凋零骷髅</ref>更有脑子，但还是不多\n"
"...喂，他们哪来的铁啊？"
msgstr ""
"They've got more brains than the <ref=[enemies]mvz2:LeatherWitherSkeleton>Leather Cap</ref> and "
"<ref=[enemies]mvz2:WitherSkeleton>regular Wither Skeletons</ref> — but still not much.\n"
"\n"
"...Hey, where did they even get the iron?"

#. Header for enemies mvz2:NetherWarrior
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid "下界战士在攻击时能够额外造成范围伤害。"
msgstr "Nether Warrior deals additional area damage when attacking."

#. Properties for enemies mvz2:NetherWarrior
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"生命：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_health\" />+<var id=\"helmet_hp\" />（头盔）+<var id=\"shield_hp\" />（盾）</color>\n"
"速度：<color=red><var id=\"entity_speed\" /></color>\n"
"特点：<color=red>攻击时持续对小范围内的器械造成伤害，盾牌可抵挡一定高度的子弹。</color>"
msgstr ""
"Toughness: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_health\" /> + <var id=\"helmet_hp\" /> (Helmet) + <var id=\"shield_hp\" /> (Shield)</"
"color>\n"
"Speed: <color=red><var id=\"entity_speed\" /></color>\n"
"Special: <color=red>Deals continuous damage to contraptions within a small area while attacking. Shield can block projectiles of a "
"certain height.</color>"

#. Flavor for enemies mvz2:NetherWarrior
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"地狱中最常见的部队之一。在下界骑士团的训练下，配备了精良的武器。身为凋零骷髅一族，榨取敌人的生命是他们一贯的作风。\n"
"真希望你没有惹到他们。"
msgstr ""
"One of the most common troops in the Nether. Trained by the Nether Knight Order, they are equipped with fine weapons. As members of "
"the Wither Skeleton kin, draining the life from their enemies is their standard practice.\n"
"\n"
"I hope you haven't crossed them."

#. Header for enemies mvz2:mesmerizer
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid "又名催眠者，能够精神控制你的器械使其倒戈。杀死它可以解除精神控制。"
msgstr ""
"Reverser, also known as the Mesmerizer, can mind-control your contraptions and turn them against you. Killing it will break the mind "
"control."

#. Properties for enemies mvz2:mesmerizer
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"生命：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_health\" />+<var id=\"armor_hp\" /></color>\n"
"速度：<color=red><var id=\"entity_speed\" /></color>\n"
"弱点：<color=red>荧石周围的器械无法被控制</color>"
msgstr ""
"Toughness: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_health\" />+<var id=\"armor_hp\" /></color>\n"
"Speed: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_speed\" /></color>\n"
"Weakness: <color=red>Cannot mind control contraptions near Glowstone</color>"

#. Flavor for enemies mvz2:mesmerizer
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"<color=#F0F>催眠者是整个世界上最帅气、最美丽、最伟大、最厉害的生物！</color>\n"
"<color=#F0F>什么催眠？你不要乱说好不好！</color>\n"
"\n"
"<color=grey>反逆者们曾经的统领名为扎赉特，他因莫须有的罪而被打入牢狱。逃脱后的他建立起了自己的军队：心灵军团，但仍未敌过凋灵帝国的下界"
"骑士团。</color>\n"
"<color=grey>扎赉特作古后，他遗留的军队大部分被凋灵帝国所收编，归属至下界骑士团的战斗序列中，后来，他们多了个催眠者的名字。</color>"
msgstr ""
"<color=#F0F>Mesmerizers are the most handsome, most beautiful, greatest, and most powerful creatures in the whole world!</color>\n"
"<color=#F0F>What mind control? Don't talk nonsense, okay!</color>\n"
"\n"
"<color=grey>The former leader of the Reversers was named Zalat. He was thrown into prison on trumped-up charges. After escaping, he "
"built his own army: the PsiCorps. But even they could not defeat the Nether Knight Order of The WINther Imperium.</color>\n"
"<color=grey>After Zalat passed away, most of the army he left behind was absorbed into The WINther Imperium and incorporated into the "
"Nether Knight Order's ranks. Later, they gained a new name — Mesmerizers.</color>"

#. Header for enemies mvz2:NetherArcher
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid "下界弓箭手能够发射出带火焰的箭矢。"
msgstr "Nether Archer can shoot flaming arrows."

#. Properties for enemies mvz2:NetherArcher
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"生命：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_health\" />+<var id=\"armor_hp\" /></color>\n"
"速度：<color=red><var id=\"entity_speed\" /></color>"
msgstr ""
"Toughness: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_health\" />+<var id=\"armor_hp\" /></color>\n"
"Speed: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_speed\" /></color>"

#. Flavor for enemies mvz2:NetherArcher
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"下界弓箭手有着天赋异禀的射击能力。他们自被选中后就被恩布勒姆·安娜设下了咒焰，也因此驾驭了掌握咒焰的能力。\n"
"咒焰不会怜悯任何一个战士，它会在使用者的体内，一直燃烧，一直燃烧。燃烧至如同生命尽头的那道光般耀眼，然后熄灭。"
msgstr ""
"Nether Archers possess an extraordinary natural talent for archery. After being chosen, they were marked with the Cursed Flame by "
"Emblem Anna, and thus gained the ability to wield it.\n"
"\n"
"The Cursed Flame shows no mercy to any warrior. It burns within its host, endlessly. It burns until it shines as brightly as the light "
"at the end of life — and then, it is extinguished."

#. Header for enemies mvz2:berserker
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid "狂战士在死亡时会产生猛烈的爆炸。"
msgstr "Berserker EXPLODES upon death."

#. Properties for enemies mvz2:berserker
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"生命：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_health\" />+<var id=\"armor_hp\" /></color>\n"
"速度：<color=red><var id=\"entity_speed\" /></color>\n"
"爆炸伤害：<color=red>300</color>"
msgstr ""
"Toughness: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_health\" />+<var id=\"armor_hp\" /></color>\n"
"Speed: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_speed\" /></color>\n"
"Explosion Damage: <color=red><var local=\"explosion_damage\" /></color>"

#. Flavor for enemies mvz2:berserker
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"没人喜欢狂战士，他们就是一群到处搞破坏的疯子，追究起责任时还要倒打你一耙，穷途末路了还要拉几个人下水。\n"
"奉劝各位在现实生活中离这种人远一点。\n"
"\n"
"<color=grey>狂战士是由恩布勒姆·安娜所训练的一支军队。她是一只因为下界之星而幻化成人型的烈焰人。就凋零骷髅们所言，她简直就是暴戾的代表。"
"疯狂扑向敌人的狂战士们永远都是敌人心中的恐惧。</color>\n"
"<color=grey>库尔·咒并不喜欢这些家伙，他曾说过：“这东西还是扔到一边比较好。”</color>"
msgstr ""
"No one likes Berserkers. They're nothing but a bunch of destructive lunatics. If you try to hold them accountable, they'll just turn "
"it back on you. And when they're cornered, they'll drag others down with them.\n"
"\n"
"Consider this a word of advice: stay away from people like this in real life.\n"
"\n"
"<color=grey>The Berserkers are a force trained by Emblem Anna. She is a Blaze who took on a humanoid form because of the Nether Star. "
"According to the Wither Skeletons, she is the very embodiment of brutality. The Berserkers, always charging madly at their enemies, "
"are the eternal fear in the hearts of their foes.</color>\n"
"<color=grey>Cuerzor didn't like these guys. He once said, \"Better just throw this thing aside.\"</color>"

#. Header for enemies mvz2:dullahan_head
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid "凋零骷髅头能够在空中迅速飘动。"
msgstr "Wither Skeleton Heads can float quickly through the air."

#. Flavor for enemies mvz2:dullahan_head
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"想成为一名合格的无头骑士，光割下自己的头颅仍远远不够。这些淘汰者们没能通过库尔·咒的考验，这辈子也与他们的战马无缘了。\n"
"尽管如此，长期的训练也使他们的头颅操纵技巧异于常人，在战场上仍然不能小觑。"
msgstr ""
"To become a true Dullahan, merely cutting off one's own head is far from enough. These rejects failed Cuerzor's trials, and thus will "
"never be reunited with their warhorses in this lifetime.\n"
"\n"
"Even so, years of training have given them extraordinary control over their heads — on the battlefield, they are still not to be "
"underestimated."

#. Header for enemies mvz2:dullahan
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"无头骑士伴随着一匹<ref=[enemies]mvz2:skeleton_horse>骷髅马</ref>出现，能够跳过器械并留下它的<ref=[enemies]mvz2:dullahan_head>头颅</"
"ref>，最终变成三个不同的怪物。"
msgstr ""
"Dullahan appears with a skeleton horse that can jump over contraptions. Then Dullahan will leave his head, forming 3 individual "
"monsters."

#. Properties for enemies mvz2:dullahan
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"生命：<color=red><var local=\"horse_hp\" />（马），<var id=\"mvz2:entity_health\" />（身体），<var local=\"head_hp\" />（头）</color>\n"
"马速度：<color=red><var local=\"horse_speed\" />（跳跃前），<var local=\"horse_speed_jumped\" />（跳跃后）</color>\n"
"身体速度：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_speed\" /></color>\n"
"头颅速度：<color=red><var local=\"head_speed\" /></color>\n"
"弱点：<color=red>金质物品，无法跳过<tag id=\"mvz2:high\" />高器械</color>\n"
"特点：<color=red>身体攻击时持续对小范围内的器械造成伤害。</color>"
msgstr ""
"Toughness: <color=red><var local=\"horse_hp\" /> (Horse), <var id=\"mvz2:entity_health\" /> (Body), <var local=\"head_hp\" /> (Head)</"
"color>\n"
"Horse Speed: <color=red><var local=\"horse_speed\" /> (Before jump), <var local=\"horse_speed_jumped\" /> (After jump)</color>\n"
"Body Speed: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_speed\" /></color>\n"
"Head Speed: <color=red><var local=\"head_speed\" /></color>\n"
"Weakness: <color=red>Golden objects; could not jump over <tag id=\"mvz2:high\"/>high contraptions</color>"

#. Flavor for enemies mvz2:dullahan
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"因为无头骑士总是喜欢在写文章的时候把开头擦掉。\n"
"\n"
"<color=grey>库尔·咒所训练的他最骄傲的一支军队，每个无头骑士都有着最强的体格和战斗力。</color>\n"
"<color=grey>不是每个凋零骷髅都能割下自己的头的，一般骷髅这样只会丢掉自己的性命。</color>"
msgstr ""
"...because Dullahans always like to erase the beginning when they write something.\n"
"\n"
"<color=grey>Cuerzor's proudest army. Every Dullahan possesses the strongest physique and combat prowess.</color>\n"
"<color=grey>Not every Wither Skeleton can cut off its own head — a regular skeleton would only end up losing its life trying.</color>"

#. Header for enemies mvz2:RaiderSkull
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid "奇袭者头颅能够跨越半场降落，进行背后突袭。"
msgstr "Raider Skulls can descend across half the battlefield, striking from behind."

#. Flavor for enemies mvz2:RaiderSkull
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"库尔·咒训练的一支部队。这类凋零骷髅在砍下自己头颅后，会表现出强大的控制自身头颅的能力。他们往往会躲在战场一角，通过操纵自己的飞头切断敌"
"军后方的增援。\n"
"降落对于每个奇袭者头颅都是一场对生命的赌注，稍有不慎便会殒命。此外，这些头颅如何在战后找到自己的身体也是个麻烦事。"
msgstr ""
"A unit trained by Cuerzor. After cutting off their own heads, these Wither Skeletons display a powerful ability to control their own "
"severed heads. They often hide in a corner of the battlefield, using their flying heads to cut off enemy reinforcements from the "
"rear.\n"
"\n"
"Landing is a gamble with their lives for every Raider Skull — one wrong move, and they're done for. On top of that, finding their "
"bodies after the battle is a whole other problem."

#. Header for enemies mvz2:NetherVanguard
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid "下界冲锋者的盾牌和战斧提供了恐怖的防御力与攻击力"
msgstr "Nether Vanguard's shield and battle axe provide terrifying defense and attack power."

#. Properties for enemies mvz2:NetherVanguard
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"生命：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_health\" />+<var id=\"helmet_hp\" />（头盔）+<var id=\"shield_hp\" />（盾）</color>\n"
"速度：<color=red><var id=\"entity_speed\" /></color>\n"
"特点：<color=red>未被阻挡时拥有90%减伤，攻击时持续对小范围内的器械造成伤害，盾牌可抵挡一定高度的子弹。</color>"
msgstr ""
"Toughness: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_health\" /> + <var id=\"helmet_hp\" /> (Helmet) + <var id=\"shield_hp\" /> (Shield)</"
"color>\n"
"Speed: <color=red><var id=\"entity_speed\" /></color>\n"
"Special: <color=red>When not blocked, has 90% damage reduction. Deals continuous damage to contraptions within a small area while "
"attacking. Shield can block projectiles of a certain height.</color>"

#. Flavor for enemies mvz2:NetherVanguard
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"地狱的精锐部队之一，组成了地狱军团的前锋。这些令人闻风丧胆的家伙在行军过程中几乎无坚不摧，唯有正面交战才有对其造成伤害的可能，但这也往"
"往是他们最恐怖的时候......"
msgstr ""
"One of the Nether's elite units, forming the vanguard of the Nether Legion. These dreaded warriors are nearly unstoppable on the march "
"— the only chance to harm them is to engage them head-on. But that's also when they're at their most terrifying..."

#. Header for enemies mvz2:hell_chariot
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid "地狱战车会碾压行进路上的所有器械，并在被摧毁后放出棺材中的<ref=[enemies]mvz2:anubisand>灵魂沙王</ref>。"
msgstr ""
"Hell Chariot will crush all contraptions on its path. It also releases <ref=[enemies]mvz2:anubisand>Anubisand</ref> from the coffin "
"after being destroyed."

#. Properties for enemies mvz2:hell_chariot
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"生命：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_health\" />，低于200时每秒失去60生命</color>\n"
"速度：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_speed\" /></color>\n"
"碾压伤害：<color=red>10000000</color>\n"
"弱点：<color=red>尖刺方块</color>"
msgstr ""
"Toughness: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_health\" />, loses 60/s while under 200</color>\n"
"Speed: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_speed\" /></color>\n"
"Crush Damage: <color=red>10000000</color>\n"
"Weakness: <color=red>Spike Block</color>"

#. Flavor for enemies mvz2:hell_chariot
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"地狱战车的司机怎么一脸不情愿的样子？\n"
"呃，准确地说，那不是司机，那是不小心坐上去，然后被卡住的一个倒霉蛋。\n"
"\n"
"<color=grey>由地狱里的黑科技制造师史蒂芬爷制造。拥有不错的装载力和韧性。不过因为一些缺陷，地上的一些杂物会被卷进引擎，然后对整个车体造"
"成破坏。</color>"
msgstr ""
"Why does the Hell Chariot's driver look so reluctant?\n"
"\n"
"Well, to be precise, that's not the driver — it's some poor fool who accidentally got on and got stuck.\n"
"\n"
"<color=grey>Built by Master Stephen, a black-tech engineer in the Nether. It has decent carrying capacity and durability. However, due "
"to some design flaws, debris on the ground can get sucked into the engine and damage the entire chariot.</color>"

#. Header for enemies mvz2:anubisand
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid "灵魂沙王飞在空中，不时向下方召唤阻挡子弹的灵魂沙。"
msgstr "Anubisand floats in the air, summoning soul sand blocks which fall and block your projectiles."

#. Properties for enemies mvz2:anubisand
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"生命：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_health\" /></color>\n"
"速度：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_speed\" /></color>\n"
"灵魂沙生命：<color=red><var local=\"soulsand_hp\" /></color>"
msgstr ""
"Toughness: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_health\" /></color>\n"
"Speed: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_speed\" /></color>\n"
"Soulsand Toughness: <color=red><var local=\"soulsand_hp\" /></color>"

#. Flavor for enemies mvz2:anubisand
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"其实他用来审判罪行的天平已经坏了很久了，它常放羽毛的那一端比较重一些。\n"
"不过他自己不知道，也没有多少人知道——知道的也没人敢告诉他就是了。\n"
"\n"
"<color=grey>这些凋零骷髅其实是由统治灵魂沙漠的斯本拉按照自己的模样用灵魂沙烧成的人偶。</color>"
msgstr ""
"The scale he uses to judge crimes has actually been broken for a long time. It's ever-so-slightly heavier on the pan where feathers "
"are often placed.\n"
"But he doesn't know this, nor many others—and those who do wouldn't dare tell him anyways.\n"
"\n"
"<color=grey>These Wither Skeletons are actually dolls fired from Soul Sand, crafted by sibuna — the ruler of the Soul Sand Desert — in "
"his own image.</color>"

#. Header for enemies mvz2:Anubiskull
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid "灵魂头王飞在空中，不时向下方召唤骷髅头。"
msgstr "Anubiskull flies high in the air, occasionally summoning Skeleton Heads down below."

#. Flavor for enemies mvz2:Anubiskull
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"库尔·咒训练的一支部队。这些凋零骷髅能够召唤凋零骷髅头，并唤醒于地下沉眠的骷髅头。\n"
"实际上，他们所召唤出来的凋零骷髅头并非由实体转化而来，而是由灵魂所造。\n"
"斯本拉不喜欢库尔·咒随意篡改自己的人偶，因为这违背了灵魂沙祭的诸多仪式传统。但不得不承认，漫天漂浮的骸骨确实比那些无用的沙子强上许多。\n"
"\n"
"<color=grey>库尔咒也有操纵灵魂的能力吗？这和我所知的情报不一致啊。</color>"
msgstr ""
"A unit trained by Cuerzor. These Wither Skeletons can summon Wither Skeleton Heads and awaken Skeleton Heads slumbering beneath the "
"ground.\n"
"\n"
"In truth, the Wither Skeleton Heads they summon are not transformed from physical bodies — they are created from souls.\n"
"\n"
"Sibuna doesn't like Cuerzor casually tampering with his dolls, as it violates many of the ritual traditions of the Soul Sand "
"Sacrifice. But there's no denying that the countless floating skulls in the sky are far more useful than those useless sands.\n"
"\n"
"<color=grey>Does Cuerzor also have the ability to manipulate souls? That doesn't match the intelligence I have...</color>"

#. Header for enemies mvz2:AngryReverser
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid "愤怒的反逆者能够快速发射出精神球体，杀死催眠者可以解除精神控制。"
msgstr "Angry Reverser can rapidly fire mind-control orbs. Killing it will break its mind control."

#. Properties for enemies mvz2:AngryReverser
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"生命：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_health\" />+<var id=\"armor_hp\" /></color>\n"
"速度：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_speed\" /></color>\n"
"弱点：<color=red>荧石周围的器械无法被控制</color>"
msgstr ""
"Toughness: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_health\" />+<var id=\"armor_hp\" /></color>\n"
"Speed: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_speed\" /></color>\n"
"Weakness: <color=red>Cannot mind control contraptions near Glowstone</color>"

#. Flavor for enemies mvz2:AngryReverser
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"反逆者军队的精英，愤怒的反逆者们铭记扎赉特的教诲，学习领袖的样貌，渴望夺取一切敌人的意志。下界骑士团曾深受这些家伙们的困扰。传闻他们曾"
"在一天内控制了一整个狂战士军团，扭转了作战局势。\n"
"可惜局部战斗上的胜利未能完成扎赉特的复仇，扎赉特死后，大部分反逆者收编至下界骑士团，未被收编的、逃离围剿的反逆者们为争夺谁是心灵军团正"
"统打的不可开交。"
msgstr ""
"Elites of the Reverser army. The Angry Reversers remember Zalat's teachings, emulate their leader's appearance, and crave the power to "
"seize the will of all their enemies. The Nether Knight Order was once deeply troubled by these creatures. Rumor has it that they once "
"took control of an entire Berserker legion in a single day, turning the tide of battle.\n"
"\n"
"Unfortunately, their victory on the local front wasn't enough to complete Zalat's revenge. After Zalat died, most of the Reversers "
"were absorbed into the Nether Knight Order. Those who escaped the purge, however, have been fighting endlessly among themselves — each "
"faction claiming to be the true successor of the PsiCorps."

#. Header for enemies mvz2:NetherTroopCarrier
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid "下界运兵车能够快速冲入战场并碾碎途中器械，每受到一定伤害释放一个怪物，爆炸后释放大量怪物。"
msgstr ""
"The Nether Troop Carrier can quickly charge onto the battlefield and crush any contraptions in its path. It releases one monster for "
"each certain amount of damage it takes, and upon exploding, it unleashes a horde of monsters."

#. Properties for enemies mvz2:NetherTroopCarrier
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"生命：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_health\" />，低于1000时每秒失去60生命</color>\n"
"速度：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_speed\" /></color>\n"
"碾压伤害：<color=red>10000000</color>\n"
"弱点：<color=red>尖刺方块</color>\n"
"受伤召唤：<color=red>奇袭者头颅、下界弓箭手、狂战士、反逆者、下界战士、无头骑士</color>\n"
"亡语召唤：<color=red>灵魂头王、下界冲锋者、愤怒的反逆者</color>"
msgstr ""
"Toughness: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_health\" /> — loses 60 health per second when below 1,000</color>\n"
"Speed: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_speed\" /></color>\n"
"Crush Damage: <color=red>10,000,000</color>\n"
"Weakness: <color=red>Spike Block</color>\n"
"Summon on Damage: <color=red>Raider Skull, Nether Archer, Berserker, Reverser, Nether Warrior, Dullahan</color>\n"
"Summon on Death: <color=red>Anubiskull, Nether Vanguard, Angry Reverser</color>"

#. Flavor for enemies mvz2:NetherTroopCarrier
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"该载具很明显普通的下界战车不一样，引擎和运兵舱似乎都经过了特殊的改装，似乎不是史蒂芬爷所为。\n"
"库尔咒对该载具表示疑惑。\n"
"\n"
"<color=white>在不起眼的地方上刻着一行小字：米罗威尼特</color>"
msgstr ""
"This vehicle is obviously different from common Hell Chariots. The engine and cabin seemed to be refitted specially, and not by "
"Stevendad.\n"
"\n"
"Cuerzor is puzzled with this vehicle\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"A line of small characters carved in an inconspicuous place: Miro·Winnet"

#. Header for enemies mvz2:bedserker
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid "床战士能够制造惊天动地的大爆炸。"
msgstr "Bedserker can unleash an earth-shattering explosion."

#. Flavor for enemies mvz2:bedserker
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid "对于床战士我们知之甚少，可能所有看到他的调查员都吓哭了吧。"
msgstr "Little is known about the Bedserker. Perhaps every investigator who saw him was simply too scared to report back."

#. Header for enemies mvz2:WitherSkeletonHorse
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid "凋零骷髅马能以极快的速度跳过并摧毁你的防线。"
msgstr "Wither Skeleton Horses can jump over and destroy your defenses at breakneck speed."

#. Properties for enemies mvz2:WitherSkeletonHorse
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"生命：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_health\" /></color>\n"
"速度：<color=red>奔跑时3，行走时1.5</color>\n"
"特点：<color=red>跳跃时能够持续对小范围内的器械造成伤害。</color>"
msgstr ""
"Toughness: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_health\" /></color>\n"
"Speed: <color=red>3 when running, 1.5 when walking</color>\n"
"Special: <color=red>Deals continuous damage to contraptions within a small area while jumping.</color>"

#. Flavor for enemies mvz2:WitherSkeletonHorse
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"足够好运的冒险家能够在雷雨天见到<ref=[enemies]mvz2:skeleton_horse>骷髅马</ref>，而这种生物则是许多冒险家穷其一生也闻所未闻的。\n"
"凋零骷髅马又被称为绝命马，它们在跳跃时能够展开凋零气息并杀伤越过的目标。与<ref=[enemies]mvz2:skeleton_horse>骷髅马</ref>不同，凋零骷髅"
"马一般性格极为暴戾，稍有不慎就会引发它的情绪爆发，并带来死亡的结局。\n"
"近些年来，因猪灵领地的扩大和凋灵骷髅的再征服运动，不熄的战火让凋零骷髅马在下界野外灭绝，现存少量个体只存在于一些重要的下界要塞。\n"
"\n"
"<color=grey>这次方块异变中也有他们的身影，但...我不认为他们这个数量是濒危的程度。</color>"
msgstr ""
"Adventurers lucky enough to encounter a <ref=[enemies]mvz2:skeleton_horse>Skeleton Horse</ref> on a thunderstorm night are few and far "
"between — but even they have likely never heard of this creature in their entire lives.\n"
"\n"
"The Wither Skeleton Horse, also known as the Doom Steed, radiates a withering aura when it leaps, devastating everything it passes "
"over. Unlike the <ref=[enemies]mvz2:skeleton_horse>Skeleton Horse</ref>, the Wither Skeleton Horse is notoriously violent by nature. "
"The slightest provocation can trigger its rage — which always ends in death.\n"
"\n"
"In recent years, due to the expansion of Piglin territory and the Reclaimation Crusade of the Wither Skeletons, the unending flames of "
"war have driven the Wither Skeleton Horse to extinction in the Nether wastes. A handful of surviving individuals now exist only in a "
"few major Nether fortresses.\n"
"\n"
"<color=grey>They've also shown up during this Block Incident... but I don't think their numbers qualify as \"endangered\" just yet.</"
"color>"

#. Header for enemies mvz2:AssaultDullahan
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid "无头强袭骑士能够在短时间内冲垮你的阵型。"
msgstr "Assault Dullahan can shatter your formation in a short amount of time."

#. Properties for enemies mvz2:AssaultDullahan
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"生命：<color=red>本体450，马800，头颅300</color>\n"
"速度：<color=red>1</color>\n"
"特点：<color=red>身体攻击时持续对小范围内的器械造成伤害。</color>"
msgstr ""
"Toughness: <color=red>Body: 450, Horse: 800, Head: 300</color>\n"
"Speed: <color=red>1</color>\n"
"Special: <color=red>Deals continuous damage to contraptions within a small area while the body attacks.</color>"

#. Flavor for enemies mvz2:AssaultDullahan
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"无头强袭骑士是精英中的精英，他们胯下的战马是稀有的<ref=[enemies]mvz2:WitherSkeletonHorse>凋零骷髅马</ref>，他的攻击时展开的领域能够杀伤"
"一切贫弱的实体，纵使身体倒下，<ref=[enemies]mvz2:BerserkerHead>头颅</ref>也会传播死亡。他们死亡后能够爆炸的"
"<ref=[enemies]mvz2:BerserkerHead>头颅</ref>能给人挥之不去的梦魇。每一位见到强袭骑士的愚者都会付出生命的代价。\n"
"不过因为诸多原因，该类军队现已停止训练。\n"
"\n"
"<color=grey>——这段话信息来源不明，而我仍能在XXX看到他们。</color>"
msgstr ""
"Assault Dullahans are the elite of the elite. The warhorses they ride are the rare <ref=[enemies]mvz2:WitherSkeletonHorse>Wither "
"Skeleton Horses</ref>. The field they unleash while attacking can eradicate any frail entity — and even if their body falls, their "
"<ref=[enemies]mvz2:BerserkerHead>head</ref> will still spread death. The explosive <ref=[enemies]mvz2:BerserkerHead>heads</ref> they "
"leave behind upon death bring lingering nightmares. Every fool who lays eyes on an Assault Dullahan pays with their life.\n"
"\n"
"However, for various reasons, this type of unit has now ceased training.\n"
"\n"
"<color=grey>— The source of this information is unclear. Yet I can still see them in the XXX.</color>"

#. Header for enemies mvz2:BerserkerHead
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid "爆裂头颅能够在死后发生可怕的爆炸"
msgstr "Berserker Head can cause a terrible explosion upon death."

#. Properties for enemies mvz2:BerserkerHead
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"生命：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_health\" /></color>\n"
"速度：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_speed\" /></color>\n"
"伤害：<color=red>100，爆炸伤害600</color>"
msgstr ""
"Toughness: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_health\" /></color>\n"
"Speed: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_speed\" /></color>\n"
"Damage: <color=red>100, explosion deals 600 damage</color>"

#. Flavor for enemies mvz2:BerserkerHead
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"爆裂头颅正如其名，是会爆裂的头颅。许多人一见到爆裂头颅便会不自觉的认为他们是<ref=[enemies]mvz2:berserker>狂战士</ref>的头颅——其实不全"
"是。部分凋零骷髅使用了一些邪术，让自己的头颅变得易爆。另一些凋零骷髅用不起邪术，买了些tnt塞在自己的头颅里。\n"
"反正结果都差不多"
msgstr ""
"Berserker Heads are exactly what their name suggests: heads that explode. Many people, upon seeing a Berserker Head, instinctively "
"assume they are the heads of <ref=[enemies]mvz2:berserker>Berserkers</ref> — but that's not entirely the case. Some Wither Skeletons "
"use dark magic to make their own heads explosive. Others can't afford such magic, so they just stuff a bit of TNT into their heads "
"instead.\n"
"\n"
"Either way, the result is pretty much the same."

#. Header for enemies mvz2:WintherMage
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid "凋灵巫师能够发射凋灵头颅并召唤陨石。"
msgstr "WINther Mage can launch Wither Skulls and summon meteors."

#. Properties for enemies mvz2:WintherMage
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"生命：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_health\" /></color>\n"
"速度：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_speed\" /></color>\n"
"伤害：<color=red>凋灵头颅400，传播凋零30s，每秒10</color>"
msgstr ""
"Toughness: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_health\" /></color>\n"
"Speed: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_speed\" /></color>\n"
"Damage: <color=red>Wither Skull: 400, inflicts Wither for 30 seconds, dealing 10 damage per second</color>"

#. Flavor for enemies mvz2:WintherMage
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"首先先记住他们叫凋灵巫师，不叫凋零法师。\n"
"凋灵巫师能够使用独特的凋灵巫术，包括召唤凋灵头颅、召唤地狱火陨石，单论个体而言他并没有太大的威胁，他最致命也最拿手的好戏是：“凋零”效"
"果。\n"
"凋零效果会不断榨取实体的生命，并在实体病入膏肓时引爆实体，被引爆的实体还会接着传播凋零效果，若不做出干涉，如疫病一样的凋零效果会将所到"
"之处变为真正的地狱。\n"
"\n"
"<color=grey>他们是凋灵骷髅。</color>"
msgstr ""
"First things first — remember, they're called WINther Mages, not Wither Mages.\n"
"\n"
"WINther Mages wield a unique form of WINther sorcery, including summoning Wither Skulls and calling down Hellfire Meteors. On their "
"own, an individual WINther Mage isn't much of a threat — but their deadliest trick is the Wither effect.\n"
"\n"
"The Wither effect constantly drains the life from any entity. When the victim is on the brink of death, the effect detonates them — "
"and the explosion spreads the Wither effect further. Left unchecked, like a plague, the Wither effect will turn everything it touches "
"into a living hell.\n"
"\n"
"<color=grey>They are WINther Skeletons.</color>"

#. Header for enemies mvz2:KingofReverser
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid "反逆者之王能不时召唤凋零骷髅军队，并能发射使器械反叛的精神球体。"
msgstr ""
"King of Reverser can occasionally summon armies of Wither Skeletons and fire mind-control orbs that turn contraptions against you."

#. Flavor for enemies mvz2:KingofReverser
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"与大多数凋零骷髅不同，你现在所看到的敌怪反逆者之王并未收编到下界骑士团的战斗序列当中。他们是独立为战的军事单位，曾属于扎赉特的心灵军"
"团。\n"
"扎赉特作古后，这些单位并没有向下界骑士团投降，在逃离围剿之后，这些反逆者各自找到了不同的扎赉特复制体，虽然主体已死，但克隆人和反逆者们"
"并不打算就此作罢，他们利用自己的控制能力重新拉起了一支军队并各自为战。迄今仍是地狱中不可忽视的不稳定因素。\n"
"\n"
"<color=grey>我想之后你要做好与心灵军团作战的准备。</color>"
msgstr ""
"Unlike most Wither Skeletons, the enemy you see before you — the King of Reverser — was never absorbed into the combat ranks of the "
"Nether Knight Order. They are independent military units, once part of Zalat's PsiCorps.\n"
"\n"
"After Zalat passed away, these units did not surrender to the Nether Knight Order. Following their escape from the purge, these "
"Reversers each found different clones of Zalat. Though the original is dead, the clones and the Reversers have no intention of giving "
"up. Using their mind-control abilities, they have raised new armies — each fighting for their own cause. To this day, they remain an "
"unpredictable and destabilizing force in the Nether that cannot be ignored.\n"
"\n"
"<color=grey>I think you'd better prepare yourself for a fight against the PsiCorps.</color>"

#. Header for enemies mvz2:MonkZombie
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid "武僧僵尸每日的习武让他刀枪不惧，心坚如铜"
msgstr "Monk Zombie's daily martial arts training makes him impervious to blades and arrows, with a heart as firm as copper."

#. Flavor for enemies mvz2:MonkZombie
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"站桩，蹲马步，静坐，外加吃脑子，这些构成了武僧僵尸的每天任务\n"
"然而他因破戒吃脑子又被老祖师罚吃素，这让他现在只有吃脑子的想法，不会被任何花言巧语所蛊惑。"
msgstr ""
"Stance training, horse stance, meditation — and eating brains. These make up Monk Zombie's daily routine.\n"
"\n"
"But after being caught breaking his vow to eat brains, his master punished him by forcing him to go vegetarian. Now, the only thing on "
"his mind is eating brains — and no amount of sweet talk will ever sway him."

#. Header for enemies mvz2:LeatherMonkZombie
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid "武僧皮帽僵尸拥有能抵抗子弹的皮帽护甲。"
msgstr "Leather Cap Monk Zombies have a leather cap that blocks projectiles."

#. Flavor for enemies mvz2:LeatherMonkZombie
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid "你以为武僧就不用头戴护甲了吗？你错了，其实他以为那是他用的斗笠。"
msgstr "You think a monk doesn't need a helmet? You'd be wrong. He thinks it's just a bamboo hat he happens to wear."

#. Header for enemies mvz2:IronMonkZombie
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid "武僧铁盔僵尸的铁盔给他提供了极高的防护。"
msgstr "The iron helmet of the Iron Helmet Monk Zombie provides him with extremely high protection."

#. Flavor for enemies mvz2:IronMonkZombie
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid "这种僵尸带的铁桶其实是个反着的矿车，他负责拿这个矿车给庙里烧水用。"
msgstr "The iron bucket this zombie wears is actually an upside-down minecart. He uses it to carry water for the temple's boiler."

#. Header for enemies mvz2:TorchKongfuZombie
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid "功夫火把僵尸的火把能够快速烧毁易燃器械。"
msgstr "Torch Kongfu Zombie's torch can quickly burn down flammable contraptions."

#. Flavor for enemies mvz2:TorchKongfuZombie
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"和大部分僵尸不一样，功夫火把僵尸有智力控制自己的胳膊放下，虽然没有血液循环，但他觉得这样对自己的胳膊好。\n"
"听说功夫火把僵尸算是<ref=[enemies]mvz2:ExplorerZombie>探险家僵尸</ref>的远亲...但是<ref=[enemies]mvz2:ExplorerZombie>探险家僵尸</ref>是"
"什么僵尸啊？"
msgstr ""
"Unlike most zombies, Torch Kongfu Zombie has enough intelligence to deliberately lower his arm. He has no blood circulation, but he "
"feels it's better for his arm.\n"
"\n"
"I heard that Torch Kongfu Zombie is a distant relative of the <ref=[enemies]mvz2:ExplorerZombie>Explorer Zombie</ref>... but what kind "
"of zombie is an Explorer Zombie anyway?"

#. Header for enemies mvz2:reflective_barrier_zombie
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid "反射壁僵尸使用反射壁保护自己，并对飞来的子弹作出反击。"
msgstr "Reflective Barrier Zombies use reflective barriers to protect themselves and counter incoming bullets."

#. Properties for enemies mvz2:reflective_barrier_zombie
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"生命：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_health\" />+<var id=\"shield_hp\" /></color>\n"
"速度：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_speed\" /></color>\n"
"特点：<color=red>子弹击中反射壁并消失后，产生伤害相同的子弹进行回击</color>"
msgstr ""
"Toughness: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_health\" />+<var id=\"shield_hp\" /></color>\n"
"Speed: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_speed\" /></color>\n"
"Special: <color=red>When a projectile hits the reflective barrier and disappears, fire a bullet with the same damage back</color>"

#. Flavor for enemies mvz2:reflective_barrier_zombie
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"“我诅咒你永世不得超生！”\n"
"“反弹！”\n"
"“再反弹！”\n"
"“反弹回去！”\n"
"“再弹！”\n"
"\n"
"不知为什么，有生物称呼他们为反射\"壁王\"\n"
"此外，虽然他们搞到了一套武僧的衣服，但他们实际上武功不强、不是功夫僵尸，只能算是编外弟子。"
msgstr ""
"\"I curse you to never find peace in the afterlife!\"\n"
"\"Reflect!\"\n"
"\"Re-reflect!\"\n"
"\"Reflect back!\"\n"
"\"Reflect again!\"\n"
"\n"
"For some reason, some creatures call them the \"Reflect Kings\".\n"
"\n"
"Also, although they've managed to get their hands on a set of monk robes, they aren't actually skilled in martial arts and aren't real "
"kungfu zombies — just honorary disciples at best."

#. Header for enemies mvz2:wicked_hermit_zombie
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid "邪仙僵尸出场时会召唤一只<ref=[enemies]mvz2:talisman_zombie>灵符僵尸</ref>，在灵符僵尸死后会传送到最左侧，反向破坏你的阵型。"
msgstr ""
"Wicked Hermit Zombie will summon a <ref=[enemies]mvz2:talisman_zombie>Talisman Zombie</ref> once it enters the field. It will teleport "
"to the left side once the Talisman Zombie dies, destroying your defense from behind."

#. Properties for enemies mvz2:wicked_hermit_zombie
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"生命：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_health\" />+<var id=\"armor_hp\" /></color>\n"
"速度：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_speed\" /></color>\n"
"特点：<color=red>自带灵符僵尸。灵符僵尸死后传送到最左侧，从后方攻击</color>"
msgstr ""
"Toughness: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_health\" />+<var id=\"armor_hp\" /></color>\n"
"Speed: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_speed\" /></color>\n"
"Special: <color=red>Comes with a Talisman Zombie. Teleports to the left side once the Talisman Zombie dies, attacking from behind</"
"color>"

#. Flavor for enemies mvz2:wicked_hermit_zombie
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"邪仙僵尸生前害怕死亡，因此他打算成为邪仙，逃避死亡的命运。\n"
"即使是在他死后，这份执念也依然没有结束。他变成了僵尸，为的就是继续生前的进程。\n"
"终于，他成为了邪仙，现在他再也不用害怕死亡了！\n"
"……你就不觉得哪里不对吗？"
msgstr ""
"The Wicked Hermit Zombie was afraid of death when he was alive, so he planned to become a wicked hermit to escape his fate.\n"
"Even after death, that obsession has not ended. He became a zombie in order to continue his pursuit from his past life.\n"
"In the end, he became a wicked hermit, and now he no longer has to be afraid of death again!\n"
"...Don’t you think something is off?"

#. Header for enemies mvz2:talisman_zombie
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid "灵符僵尸跳跃前进，并能够在攻击的同时恢复生命值。"
msgstr "Talisman Zombie jumps forward to move. It also heals itself by attacking."

#. Properties for enemies mvz2:talisman_zombie
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"生命：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_health\" /></color>\n"
"速度：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_speed\" /></color>\n"
"特点：<color=red>攻击时恢复等量生命值</color>"
msgstr ""
"Toughness: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_health\" /></color>\n"
"Speed: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_speed\" /></color>\n"
"Special: <color=red>Restore toughness equal to damage dealt</color>"

#. Flavor for enemies mvz2:talisman_zombie
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"你知道的，伙计——只要在那个灵符上写上任何东西，它就会按照上面写的事情去照办。\n"
"比如……写上“不要照着这句话做”。"
msgstr ""
"Y'know, as long as you write anything on that talisman, Talisman Zombie will do what it says.\n"
"For example... write \"Don't do what this paper says\"."

#. Header for enemies mvz2:shikaisen_zombie
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid "尸解仙僵尸在生命较低时会将竹杖插入地面，形成可以复活周围所有怪物的图腾。"
msgstr ""
"Shikaisen Zombie plunges its bamboo staff into the ground at low health, to create a totem that revives all nearby defeated monsters."

#. Properties for enemies mvz2:shikaisen_zombie
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"生命：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_health\" /></color>\n"
"竹杖耐久：<color=red><var local=\"staff_hp\" /></color>\n"
"特点：<color=red>生命低于50%时将竹杖插入地面，竹杖会以自己的耐久为代价复活周围死亡并倒下的怪物</color>\n"
"弱点：<color=red>火焰会直接烧掉竹杖</color>"
msgstr ""
"Toughness: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_health\" /></color>\n"
"Staff Toughness: <color=red><var local=\"staff_hp\" /></color>\n"
"Special: <color=red>Plunges its staff into the ground when health drops below 50%, reviving all nearby defeated monsters at the cost "
"of its own toughness</color>\n"
"Weakness: <color=red>Fire instantly burns the staff</color>"

#. Flavor for enemies mvz2:shikaisen_zombie
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"尸解仙指的是将自己的灵魂转移到某样物品，并且在等到某个合适的时机重塑肉身而复活的修仙方式。\n"
"也就是说这些倒霉蛋本来应该是能成仙的。\n"
"\n"
"此外，他们非常擅长做仰卧起坐。"
msgstr ""
"Shikaisen refers to a method of cultivation where one transfers their soul into an object, then waits for the right moment to reshape "
"their physical body and achieve resurrection.\n"
"\n"
"In other words, these unlucky souls were originally supposed to become immortals.\n"
"\n"
"Also, they're really good at doing sit-ups."

#. Header for enemies mvz2:skeleton_warrior
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid "骷髅战士能够被死灵墓碑召唤前来作战。"
msgstr "Skeleton Warriors can be summoned by the Necrotombstone to fight for you."

#. Properties for enemies mvz2:skeleton_warrior
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"生命：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_health\" />+<var id=\"helmet_hp\" />（头盔）+<var id=\"shield_hp\" />（盾）</color>\n"
"速度：<color=red><var id=\"entity_speed\" /></color>"
msgstr ""
"Toughness: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_health\" /> + <var id=\"helmet_hp\" /> (Helmet) + <var id=\"shield_hp\" /> (Shield)</"
"color>\n"
"Speed: <color=red><var id=\"entity_speed\" /></color>"

#. Flavor for enemies mvz2:skeleton_warrior
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"\"为什么你不穿衣服？\"\n"
"\"我把衣服卖了拿来买武器了\"\n"
"\"你有没有发现你那武器没有给你加一点攻击力？你的攻击力还是100\"\n"
"\"说不定未来就107107了\""
msgstr ""
"\"Why aren't you wearing any clothes?\"\n"
"\"I sold them to buy this weapon.\"\n"
"\"Did you notice that weapon doesn't increase your attack power at all? Your damage is still 100.\"\n"
"\"Maybe it'll be 107107 in the future.\""

#. Header for enemies mvz2:skeleton_mage
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid "不同的骷髅法师能够使用不同种类的法术。"
msgstr "Different Skeleton Mages can use different types of spells."

#. Properties for enemies mvz2:skeleton_mage
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"生命：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_health\" /></color>\n"
"速度：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_speed\" /></color>\n"
"伤害：<color=red>冰锥20，闪电球20，火弹80</color>"
msgstr ""
"Toughness: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_health\" /></color>\n"
"Speed: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_speed\" /></color>\n"
"Damage: <color=red>Icebolt: 20, Chargedbolt: 20, Fireball: 80</color>"

#. Flavor for enemies mvz2:skeleton_mage
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid "\"我很喜欢这衣服，不卖。\""
msgstr "\"I really like this outfit. Not for sale.\""

#. Header for enemies mvz2:SixQiZombie
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid "六气僵尸的境界可以让他们刀枪不入。"
msgstr "SixQi Zombie's mastery of the Six Energies makes them impervious to blades and arrows."

#. Properties for enemies mvz2:SixQiZombie
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"生命：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_health\" /></color>\n"
"速度：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_speed\" /></color>\n"
"特点：<color=red>拥有99%的伤害抗性。</color>\n"
"弱点：<color=red>黑洞炸弹可以秒杀。</color>"
msgstr ""
"Toughness: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_health\" /></color>\n"
"Speed: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_speed\" /></color>\n"
"Special: <color=red>Has 99% damage resistance.</color>\n"
"Weakness: <color=red>Can be instantly killed by Black Hole Bomb.</color>"

#. Flavor for enemies mvz2:SixQiZombie
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"夫列子御风而行，泠然善也，旬有五日而后反。彼于致福者，未数数然也。此虽免乎行，犹有所待者也。若夫乘天地之正，而御六气之辩，以游无穷者，"
"彼且恶乎待哉？\n"
"故曰：至人无己，神人无功，圣人无名。"
msgstr ""
"There was Liezi, who rode on the wind and pursued his way, with an admirable indifference to all external things, returning, however, "
"after fifteen days, to his place. In regard to the things that are supposed to contribute to happiness, he was free from all "
"endeavours to obtain them; but though he had not to walk, there was still something for which he had to wait. But suppose one who "
"mounts on the ether of heaven and earth in its normal operation, and drives along the six elemental energies of the changing seasons, "
"thus enjoying himself in the illimitable — what has he to wait for? Therefore it is said: 'The Perfect man has no thought of self; the "
"Spirit-like man, none of merit; the Sagely-minded man, none of fame.'"

#. Header for enemies mvz2:emperor_zombie
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid "皇帝僵尸使用手中的圣剑来给予周围的友方单位圣盾，使它们免疫下一次受到的伤害。"
msgstr "Emperor Zombie uses the Holy Sword to grant Divine Shields to nearby friendly units, making them immune to the next damage."

#. Properties for enemies mvz2:emperor_zombie
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"生命：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_health\" />+<var id=\"armor_hp\" /></color>\n"
"速度：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_speed\" /></color>\n"
"施法冷却：<color=red>5秒</color>\n"
"特点：<color=red>一次最多给予10个周围的友方单位圣盾，抵消下一次受到的伤害</color>"
msgstr ""
"Toughness: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_health\" />+<var id=\"armor_hp\" /></color>\n"
"Cast Cooldown: <color=red>5 seconds</color>\n"
"Special: <color=red>Gives divine shields to up to 10 nearby friendly units, negating the next damage they take</color>"

#. Flavor for enemies mvz2:emperor_zombie
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"他并不是什么大国的皇帝，就是一个僵尸小圈子里面，天天被捧的高高的，实际上就只会套盾，被碰一下就破防，还以为自己有多大能耐的土皇帝罢"
"了。\n"
"<color=red>【图鉴 已被禁言，有效期是永久】</color>"
msgstr ""
"He isn't the emperor of any great nation—just a petty tyrant within a small clique of zombies.\n"
"Constantly praised and elevated by his peers, he believes himself to be all-powerful, but in reality, he only knows how to apply "
"shields. His fragile defenses crumble at the slightest touch, yet he clings to the delusion of his own grandeur.\n"
"<color=red>【@Almanac has been permanently muted】</color>"

#. Header for enemies mvz2:Hemperor
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid "天子僵尸使用手中的圣剑来给予周围的友方单位再生效果，使它们每秒回复60点血。"
msgstr ""
"Hemperor uses the Holy Sword in its hand to grant a regeneration effect to nearby friendly units, restoring 60 health per second."

#. Properties for enemies mvz2:Hemperor
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"生命：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_health\" />+<var id=\"armor_hp\" /></color>\n"
"速度：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_speed\" /></color>\n"
"施法冷却：<color=red>5秒</color>\n"
"特点：<color=red>一次最多给予10个周围的友方60/s的再生效果。</color>"
msgstr ""
"Toughness: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_health\" /> + <var id=\"armor_hp\" /></color>\n"
"Speed: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_speed\" /></color>\n"
"Cast Cooldown: <color=red>5 seconds</color>\n"
"Special: <color=red>Grants a regeneration effect of 60/s to up to 10 nearby friendly units at once.</color>"

#. Flavor for enemies mvz2:Hemperor
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"他同样不是什么大国的皇帝，只是个有点闲钱的僵尸演员，这身衣服看着很霸气，实际上造价不出50个绿宝石，而他掏了8000个钻石买了这件衣服。"
msgstr ""
"He's no emperor of some great nation either — just a zombie actor with a bit of spare cash. This outfit may look imposing, but it "
"actually cost less than 50 emeralds to make. Yet he paid 8,000 diamonds for it."

#. Header for enemies mvz2:PirateZombie
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid "醉醺醺的海盗僵尸会扑向你的防线。"
msgstr "The tipsy Pirate Zombie will lunge toward your defenses."

#. Properties for enemies mvz2:PirateZombie
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"生命：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_health\" /></color>\n"
"速度：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_speed\" /></color>\n"
"伤害：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_damage\" /></color>"
msgstr ""
"Toughness: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_health\" /></color>\n"
"Speed: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_speed\" /></color>\n"
"Damage: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_damage\" /></color>"

#. Flavor for enemies mvz2:PirateZombie
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"浑身朗姆酒气的海盗僵尸走过来说了这么一段话：\n"
"“想紧跟海盗时尚风潮可不那么简单，不过请记住，只要你站在潮湿的甲板上那就已经很‘潮’了。”"
msgstr ""
"The rum-soaked Pirate Zombie shuffled over and said:\n"
"\"Keeping up with the latest pirate trends is always tricky. But remember — standing on a wet deck is already pretty 'cool'. \""

#. Header for enemies mvz2:LeatherPirateZombie
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid "醉醺醺的海盗皮帽僵尸会扑向你的防线。"
msgstr "The tipsy Leather Cap Pirate Zombie will lunge toward your defenses."

#. Flavor for enemies mvz2:LeatherPirateZombie
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"海盗皮帽僵尸长着一张大众脸。当问及他最喜欢吃什么，他认真思索片刻，紧了紧皮帽，说“啦嗷需脑子撕。。”\n"
"作为邻居，也许可以让他来借个杯子？"
msgstr ""
"Leather Cap Pirate Zombie is a simple zombie. When asked what his favorite dish is, he'd think for a moment, straighten his ascot, and "
"say, \"Rrurrarrbrains.\" \n"
"Perhaps he could borrow a cup, neighbor?"

#. Header for enemies mvz2:PirateSkeleton
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid "不那么醉醺醺的海盗骷髅会扑向你的防线。"
msgstr "The slightly less tipsy Pirate Skeleton will lunge toward your defenses."

#. Flavor for enemies mvz2:PirateSkeleton
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"纵观一圈看下来：艾弗瑞领导的海盗无一不是醉醺醺的，即使是骷髅也散发着一身酒气...\n"
"骷髅明明没有胃，他们喝酒是图什么呢？"
msgstr ""
"Taking a step back: every pirate led by Avery is drunk through and through — even the skeletons reek of booze...\n"
"\n"
"Skeletons don't even have stomachs. What's the point of them drinking?"

#. Header for enemies mvz2:PirateBucketSkeleton
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid "不那么醉醺醺的海盗木桶骷髅会扑向你的防线。"
msgstr "The slightly less tipsy Pirate Bucket Skeleton will lunge toward your defenses."

#. Flavor for enemies mvz2:PirateBucketSkeleton
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"我怀疑这家伙是按桶喝的酒，你看犯罪证据还带在他的头上呢。\n"
"<color=grey>呃，如果这骷髅是泡酒物呢？</color>"
msgstr ""
"I suspect this guy drinks by the barrel — and you can see the evidence right on his head.\n"
"\n"
"<color=grey>Uh... what if the skeleton itself is the thing being pickled in the alcohol?</color>"

#. Name for enemies mvz2:undead_flying_object
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.name"
msgid "不死飞行物"
msgstr "Undead Flying Object"

#. Header for enemies mvz2:undead_flying_object
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid "不死飞行物从空中来袭并对你进行干扰。在那之后它们就会离开。"
msgstr "Undead Flying Objects invade from the sky and harass you. Afterwards, they leave."

#. Properties for enemies mvz2:undead_flying_object
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"生命：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_health\" /></color>\n"
"红色：<color=red>放出僵尸</color>\n"
"绿色：<color=red>绑架器械</color>\n"
"蓝色：<color=red>吸取掉落物</color>\n"
"彩色：<color=red>变成两个随机颜色的不死飞行物</color>"
msgstr ""
"Toughness: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_health\" /></color>\n"
"Red: <color=red>Releases a zombie</color>\n"
"Green: <color=red>Abducts a contraption</color>\n"
"Blue: <color=red>Absorbs pickups</color>\n"
"Rainbow: <color=red>Splits into two UFOs of random colors</color>"

#. Flavor for enemies mvz2:undead_flying_object
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid "如果你的农场里大面积地种植了小麦，或者圈养了很多的奶牛，那你可一定要小心这帮家伙了。"
msgstr "Watch out for these if you have large patches of wheat planted in your fields, or keep herds of cows!"

#. Header for enemies mvz2:zombie_cloud
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid "僵尸云飞在空中，向下降雨形成水迹，踩到水迹的怪物会向前滑动。"
msgstr ""
"Zombie Cloud floats in the sky, releasing rain that creates puddles on the ground. Monsters stepping on these puddles will slide "
"forward."

#. Properties for enemies mvz2:zombie_cloud
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid "生命：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_health\" /></color>"
msgstr "Toughness: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_health\" /></color>"

#. Flavor for enemies mvz2:zombie_cloud
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid "至少这朵云没有对你竖中指。"
msgstr "At least this cloud doesn’t flip you off."

#. Header for enemies mvz2:HeavyGutant
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid "突变重炮手可以粉碎你的器械，并在血量低至一半时投掷炸弹。"
msgstr "Heavy Gutant can crush your contraptions and throw bombs when its health drops to half."

#. Flavor for enemies mvz2:HeavyGutant
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"他在海盗选美大赛上获得了第二名，输给了<ref=[enemies]mvz2:MusketeerZombie>火枪手僵尸</ref>，原因是因为他脸上有疤（恼）\n"
"\n"
"大概是因为他长得太丑了所以没有小鬼愿意爬他身上，他于是选择拿炮弹的弹药当投掷的小鬼。\n"
"还好他们没有意识到炮管里该装正经TNT。"
msgstr ""
"He placed second in the Pirate Beauty Pageant, losing to the <ref=[enemies]mvz2:MusketeerZombie>Musketeer Zombie</ref>, because he has "
"a scar on his face (annoyed).\n"
"\n"
"Probably because he's too ugly, no Imp is willing to climb on him — so he uses cannonballs as his throwing ammunition instead.\n"
"\n"
"Good thing they never realized the cannons should probably be loaded with actual TNT."

#. Header for enemies mvz2:cannoneer_zombie
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid "炮手僵尸的重型铁炮可以帮他阻挡子弹，并且每隔一段时间便会发射一只<ref=[enemies]mvz2:cannonball_zombie>炮弹僵尸</ref>。"
msgstr ""
"The bulky cannons of Cannoneer Zombies block bullets and fire a <ref=[enemies]mvz2:cannonball_zombie>Zombie Cannonball</ref> every "
"once in a while."

#. Properties for enemies mvz2:cannoneer_zombie
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"生命：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_health\" />+<var id=\"shield_hp\" /></color>\n"
"速度：<color=red>0.5，1（失去铁炮后）</color>\n"
"发射间隔：<color=red>8秒</color>"
msgstr ""
"Toughness: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_health\" />+<var id=\"shield_hp\" /> (Cannon)</color>\n"
"Speed: <color=red><var local=\"cannon_speed\" />, <var id=\"mvz2:entity_speed\" /> (After losing the cannon)</color>\n"
"Fire Interval: <color=red>8 seconds</color>"

#. Flavor for enemies mvz2:cannoneer_zombie
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid "曾经开发过一款手机游戏，不过可惜的是，那款游戏很快就停服了。"
msgstr "Had once developed a mobile game, but unfortunately, that game was shut down rather quickly."

#. Header for enemies mvz2:cannonball_zombie
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid "炮弹僵尸由<ref=[enemies]mvz2:cannoneer_zombie>炮手僵尸</ref>发射而来。它们飘浮在空中，并且会像普通的僵尸一样攻击器械。"
msgstr ""
"Zombie Cannonballs are launched into the battlefield by Cannoneer Zombies. They levitate in the air and attack like regular zombies."

#. Flavor for enemies mvz2:cannonball_zombie
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"没错，炮弹也是一只僵尸！\n"
"而且特别害怕被脚踩！"
msgstr ""
"Yes, indeed! This cannonball is also a ZOMBIE!\n"
"And it's especially afraid of being stomped on!"

#. Header for enemies mvz2:SailorZombie
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid "水手僵尸走路时会留下水迹，踩到水迹的怪物会向前滑动。"
msgstr "Sailor Zombie leaves puddles of water when walking. Monsters that step on them will slide forward."

#. Flavor for enemies mvz2:SailorZombie
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"水手僵尸和海盗团里的<ref=[enemies]mvz2:PirateIMP>小崽子们</ref>关系很好，他经常和<ref=[enemies]mvz2:PirateIMP>小鬼们</ref>玩出海游"
"戏：\n"
"Are ya ready, kids?（小鬼们，都准备好了吗？）\n"
"Aye-aye, Captain!（是——的，船长！）\n"
"I can't hear you!（我听不见！）\n"
"AYE-AYE, CAPTAIN!（是——的，船长！）\n"
"Oooooohhhhh————AHHHHH！ I'm sorry,Pop-Captain! I was wrong!（<ref=[enemies]mvz2:pop_captain>船长</ref>我没错）"
msgstr ""
"Sailor Zombie gets along really well with the <ref=[enemies]mvz2:PirateIMP>little rascals</ref> in the pirate crew. He often plays the "
"\"sailing game\" with the <ref=[enemies]mvz2:PirateIMP>little imps</ref>:\n"
"\n"
"\"Are ya ready, kids?\"\n"
"\"Aye-aye, Captain!\"\n"
"\"I can't hear you!\"\n"
"\"AYE-AYE, CAPTAIN!\"\n"
"\"Oooooohhhhh————AHHHHH! Sorry, Pop Captain! I was wrong!\"(<ref=[enemies]mvz2:pop_captain>Pop Captain</ref>, I was not wrong!)"

#. Header for enemies mvz2:MusketeerZombie
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid "火枪手会朝你的器械发射子弹，子弹打完后会正常走向你的阵线。"
msgstr ""
"Musketeer Zombie will fire bullets at your contraptions. When it runs out of bullets, it will simply walk toward your defenses like a "
"normal zombie."

#. Properties for enemies mvz2:MusketeerZombie
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"生命：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_health\" /></color>\n"
"速度：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_speed\" /></color>\n"
"伤害：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_damage\" /></color>\n"
"特点：<color=red>有10发火枪弹药，每次发射一发，射击完毕后会正常近战攻击</color>"
msgstr ""
"Toughness: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_health\" /></color>\n"
"Speed: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_speed\" /></color>\n"
"Damage: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_damage\" /></color>\n"
"Special: <color=red>Has 10 musket rounds. Fires one shot per attack. When ammunition is exhausted, switches to regular melee attacks.</"
"color>"

#. Flavor for enemies mvz2:MusketeerZombie
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"火枪手僵尸宣称自己脸上的疤是在一次牛仔决斗时受的伤，并称自己是狂野西部最强的快枪手。可惜这里是海盗港湾，他不是最强的。\n"
"其实，他脸上的疤是他在玩枪斗术时给自己弄伤的。\n"
"\n"
"<color=grey>不知道为什么，有人管他叫马斯克僵尸。</color>"
msgstr ""
"Musketeer Zombie claims that the scar on his face is from a duel in the Wild West, and boasts that he's the fastest gunslinger on the "
"frontier. Too bad this is Pirate Seas — he's not the fastest here.\n"
"\n"
"The truth is, he got that scar while practicing his \"gun-kata\" and accidentally shot himself.\n"
"\n"
"<color=grey>For some reason, some people call him \"Elon Musketeer.\"</color>"

#. Flavor for enemies mvz2:MusketeerZombie
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid "似乎就是这家伙卖给小鬼们枪支的。"
msgstr "And it seems he's the one who sold the imps their guns."

#. Header for enemies mvz2:pop_captain
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid "大力船长僵尸会使用铁锚将遇到的器械打飞到上方或下方的一行。"
msgstr "Pop Captains use their anchors to knock contraptions they encounter onto the upper or lower lane."

#. Properties for enemies mvz2:pop_captain
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"生命：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_health\" /></color>\n"
"伤害：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_damage\" />（冲击）</color>\n"
"速度：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_speed\" /></color>\n"
"特殊：<color=red>若被移动的器械移动到已有器械的位置，原来的器械将直接被摧毁。</color>"
msgstr ""
"Toughness: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_health\" /></color>\n"
"Damage: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_damage\" /> (Impact)</color>\n"
"Speed: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_speed\" /></color>\n"
"Special: <color=red>Knocking a contraption onto the targeted tile will destroy existing contraptions on that tile</color>"

#. Flavor for enemies mvz2:pop_captain
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"他以前当水手的时候喜欢吃菠菜，不过自从他当了船长之后，他就更喜欢吃橘子了。\n"
"此外我强调一下，他是一艘船的船长，是艾弗瑞的手下，不是整个莱伯塔利亚的船长，那是艾弗瑞。"
msgstr ""
"His real name is Tain.\n"
"\n"
"Back when he was a sailor, he loved eating spinach. But ever since he became captain, he's preferred oranges.\n"
"\n"
"And just to be clear — he's the captain of one ship, a subordinate of Avery. He's not the captain of all Libertalia — that's Avery's "
"title."

#. Header for enemies mvz2:Endermite
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid "末影螨能够躲过大部分子弹。"
msgstr "Endermites can evade most projectiles."

#. Flavor for enemies mvz2:Endermite
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"你可能觉得这个螨虫实在太小了，我也这么觉得，他甚至没有怪物头颅大。\n"
"这家伙绝对是个擦弹好手。"
msgstr ""
"You might think this mite is way too small — and I agree. It's not even as big as a monster's head.\n"
"\n"
"This guy is definitely a master of grazing."

#. Header for enemies mvz2:ChiefCannoneerZombie
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid "炮长僵尸会使用他的炮长加农炮发射小鬼。"
msgstr "Chief Cannoneer Zombie uses his Chief Cannon to launch Imps."

#. Properties for enemies mvz2:ChiefCannoneerZombie
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"生命：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_health\" />+<var id=\"shield_hp\" /></color>\n"
"速度：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_speed\" /></color>"
msgstr ""
"Toughness: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_health\" />+<var id=\"shield_hp\" /></color>\n"
"Speed: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_speed\" /></color>"

#. Flavor for enemies mvz2:ChiefCannoneerZombie
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"炮长僵尸是所有<ref=[enemies]mvz2:cannoneer_zombie>炮手僵尸</ref>的老大，他的职责包括但不限于叫其他<ref=[enemies]mvz2:cannoneer_zombie>"
"炮手僵尸</ref>干活、叫<ref=[enemies]mvz2:PirateIMP>海盗小鬼僵尸</ref>进炮筒里干活、叫<ref=[enemies]mvz2:PirateBucketSkeleton>海盗木桶骷"
"髅</ref>从桶里出来干活、叫<ref=[enemies]mvz2:HeavyGutant>重炮手</ref>丢点正常的东西并干活、被水渍滑倒并叫"
"<ref=[enemies]mvz2:SailorZombie>水手</ref>干活、讨好<ref=[enemies]mvz2:pop_captain>船长</ref>....这个可不敢叫他干活。\n"
"炮长僵尸可不是每个僵尸都能当的，想在船上混到这个职位需要熟练掌握加农炮的使用和维修技巧、熟练清理死在里面的<ref=[enemies]mvz2:PirateIMP>"
"小鬼</ref>。还有不那么重要的因素——得到<ref=[enemies]mvz2:pop_captain>船长</ref>的好感。"
msgstr ""
"Chief Cannoneer Zombie is the boss of all <ref=[enemies]mvz2:cannoneer_zombie>cannoneer zombies</ref>. His duties include, but are not "
"limited to: ordering other <ref=[enemies]mvz2:cannoneer_zombie>cannoneer zombies</ref> to work, stuffing "
"<ref=[enemies]mvz2:PirateIMP>Pirate Imps</ref> into cannons to work, telling <ref=[enemies]mvz2:PirateBucketSkeleton>Pirate Bucket "
"Skeletons</ref> to get out of their buckets and work, telling the <ref=[enemies]mvz2:HeavyGutant>Heavy Gutant</ref> to throw something "
"normal and work, slipping on puddles and calling the <ref=[enemies]mvz2:SailorZombie>Sailor</ref> to work, and sucking up to the "
"<ref=[enemies]mvz2:pop_captain>Pop Captain</ref>... though he would never dare order him to do anything.\n"
"\n"
"Not just any zombie can become a Chief Cannoneer. To reach this rank on a ship, you need to master the use and maintenance of cannons, "
"and be skilled at cleaning out the <ref=[enemies]mvz2:PirateIMP>Imps</ref> that die inside them. Oh, and there's one less important "
"factor — earning the <ref=[enemies]mvz2:pop_captain>Pop Captain</ref>'s favor."

#. Header for enemies mvz2:PirateIMP
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid "海盗小鬼僵尸会使用只有一发子弹的火枪射击。"
msgstr "Pirate Imp fires a musket with only one shot."

#. Flavor for enemies mvz2:PirateIMP
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"虽然海盗小鬼僵尸们从小就在海盗团里打杂，没有上过学，但这不妨碍他们对进入学校学习的向往。有些小鬼会用自己的零花钱购买自己未来上学可能用"
"到的文具。\n"
"对的，那枪是他的文具。"
msgstr ""
"Although Pirate Imps have been doing odd jobs in the pirate crew since they were young and never went to school, that doesn't stop "
"them from dreaming of getting an education. Some Imps even spend their pocket money on school supplies they might need in the future.\n"
"\n"
"That's right — the gun is his school supply. Gotta protect that Second Amendment, right?"

#. Header for enemies mvz2:KogasaZombie
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid "小伞僵尸会空降至战场上，并吓晕被攻击的实体。"
msgstr "Kogasa Zombie will airdrop onto the battlefield and stun any entity it attacks."

#. Properties for enemies mvz2:KogasaZombie
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"生命：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_health\" /></color>\n"
"速度：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_speed\" /></color>\n"
"伤害：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_damage\" /></color>\n"
"特点：<color=red>被攻击的实体会眩晕5s</color>"
msgstr ""
"Toughness: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_health\" /></color>\n"
"Speed: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_speed\" /></color>\n"
"Damage: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_damage\" /></color>\n"
"Special: <color=red>Stuns the attacked entity for 5 seconds</color>"

#. Flavor for enemies mvz2:KogasaZombie
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid "啊呀，骇死我力！"
msgstr "Ahhh, I'm so scared!"

#. Header for enemies mvz2:mega_mutant_zombie
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid "超级突变僵尸可以粉碎你的器械，并在血量低至一半时投掷小鬼僵尸"
msgstr "Mega Mutant Zombie can crush your contraptions and throw an Imp when its health drops to half."

#. Flavor for enemies mvz2:mega_mutant_zombie
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"超级突变僵尸生来就是力量的二倍化身，他以自己的二倍力量为荣，他徒手便能手撕二个黑曜石，他是无数二倍器械和二倍玩家的梦魇。如此强大的怪"
"物，谁能想到他在背地里很喜欢二倍的小猫咪？\n"
"可是被他抱过二倍的猫咪不知为何都去世了。\n"
"\n"
"呃，上述文本我没在抖机灵啊(存疑)，超级突变僵尸可是古早换皮怪，就是换了个眼睛就有二倍血量！\n"
"\n"
"<color=white>红瞳真可爱。</color>"
msgstr ""
"Mega Mutant Zombie was born as the double embodiment of strength. He takes pride in his double power — with his bare hands, he can "
"tear apart two Obsidians. He is the nightmare of countless double contraptions and double players. Who would have thought that such a "
"powerful monster secretly loves double the little cats?\n"
"\n"
"But for some reason, every cat he has double-hugged ended up dead.\n"
"\n"
"Uh... I'm not just joking around here (maybe). Mega Mutant Zombie is an old-school reskin — just different eyes, but double the "
"health!\n"
"\n"
"<color=white>Red eyes are so cute.</color>"

#. Header for enemies mvz2:TeslaTrooper
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid "磁暴步兵会电击他的敌人。"
msgstr "Tesla Trooper will shock its enemies."

#. Properties for enemies mvz2:TeslaTrooper
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"生命：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_health\" /></color>\n"
"速度：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_speed\" /></color>\n"
"特殊：<color=red>被攻击的器械会短路5秒，被攻击的怪物会停顿1秒；电击水域会对周围水域也造成伤害</color>"
msgstr ""
"Toughness: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_health\" /></color>\n"
"Speed: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_speed\" /></color>\n"
"Special: <color=red>Contraptions hit by its attack are short-circuited for 5 seconds. Monsters hit by its attack are stunned for 1 "
"second. Electrified water also damages nearby bodies of water.</color>"

#. Flavor for enemies mvz2:TeslaTrooper
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"这些穿戴特殊作业设备的骷髅，能够在稍远一些的距离操纵电力攻击它的敌人。被电击的对象一般有以下几种反应：\n"
"1.因强电而晕眩或是失去原有能力\n"
"2.吸收电能并强化自身\n"
"3.做一次X光并变成灰烬\n"
"<s>4.问能不能换一个最小的电</s>\n"
"\n"
"我为什么会觉得这些家伙是库尔咒训练的。"
msgstr ""
"These skeletons, wearing specialized gear, can manipulate electricity to attack their enemies from range. Generally, the target struck "
"by electricity will react in one of the following ways:\n"
"\n"
"1. Stunned or lose their abilities due to the high voltage\n"
"2. Absorb the electricity and become empowered\n"
"3. Turn into a skeleton in an X-ray for a split second, then crumble to ash\n"
"<s>4. Ask if they can have the smallest shock instead</s>\n"
"\n"
"Why do I get the feeling that Cuerzor trained these guys?"

#. Header for enemies mvz2:MutantVillager
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid "不幸成为<color=#8B008B>拉恩</color>实验品的突变村民可以粉碎你的器械，并在血量低至一半时投掷小鬼玩家模型"
msgstr ""
"Poor Mutant Villagers, unfortunate test subjects of <color=#8B008B>Rahn</color>, can crush your contraptions and throw an Imp "
"Mannequin when their health drops to half."

#. Flavor for enemies mvz2:MutantVillager
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"或许这是<ref=[misc]mvz2:villager>戴夫</ref>带着幼年<ref=[misc]mvz2:steve>史蒂夫</ref>出去玩的珍贵录像。\n"
"\n"
"就经验而言，一般只有僵尸种族有自然生成的突变体型，你现在所见到的突变村民虽然伤害到了你的眼睛，但他本身也是一位受害者\n"
"你未来可能需要保护他们。"
msgstr ""
"Perhaps this is precious footage of <ref=[misc]mvz2:villager>Dave</ref> taking young <ref=[misc]mvz2:steve>Steve</ref> out to play.\n"
"\n"
"From experience, usually only the zombie race has naturally occurring mutant variants. The Mutant Villager you see now, as much as it "
"hurts your eyes, is also a victim.\n"
"\n"
"You may need to protect them in the future."

#. Header for enemies mvz2:MegaMutantVillager
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid "不幸成为<color=#8B008B>拉恩</color>实验品的超级突变村民可以粉碎你的器械,并在血量低至一半时投掷超级小鬼玩家模型"
msgstr ""
"Mega Mutant Villagers, unfortunate test subjects of <color=#8B008B>Rahn</color>, can crush your contraptions and throw a Mega Imp "
"Mannequin when their health drops to half."

#. Flavor for enemies mvz2:MegaMutantVillager
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"或许这是哲学家<ref=[misc]mvz2:villager>戴夫</ref>带着幼年<ref=[misc]mvz2:steve>史蒂夫</ref>去两个街区以外的皮衣俱乐部玩的珍贵录像。\n"
"\n"
"讲正经的，你所能看到的有血肉的突变怪物大多和<color=#8B008B>拉恩</color>脱不开关系"
msgstr ""
"Perhaps this is precious footage of <ref=[misc]mvz2:villager>Dave</ref>, the Gachi philosopher, taking young "
"<ref=[misc]mvz2:steve>Steve</ref> to the leather club two blocks away.\n"
"\n"
"On a serious note, most of the fleshy mutant monsters you see are connected to <color=#8B008B>Rahn</color> in one way or another."

#. Header for enemies mvz2:VillagerGhast
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid "不幸成为<color=#8B008B>拉恩</color>实验品的村民恶魂能够飞在天上并对你的器械进行轰炸，死亡后掉落钱币。"
msgstr ""
"The poor Villager Ghast, an unfortunate test subject of <color=#8B008B>Rahn</color>, can fly through the sky and bombard your "
"contraptions. It drops coins upon death."

#. Flavor for enemies mvz2:VillagerGhast
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"这种东西的存在真是对人生理上和心理上的双重亵渎.\n"
"\n"
"不过他们掉的钱倒是挺有用的就是了。"
msgstr ""
"The existence of these things is a double blasphemy — both physically and psychologically.\n"
"\n"
"That said, the money they drop is pretty useful."

#. Header for enemies mvz2:Mannequin
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid "玩家模型会在受到一定伤害时释放自己的器械，死亡时放置<ref=[enemies]mvz2:MannequinTNT>玩家模型TNT</ref>。"
msgstr ""
"Mannequins will release their own contraptions after taking a certain amount of damage, and upon death, will place a "
"<ref=[enemies]mvz2:MannequinTNT>Mannequin TNT</ref>."

#. Flavor for enemies mvz2:Mannequin
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"不知为何长得和<ref=[misc]mvz2:steve>史蒂夫</ref>很像的...实体，能够在受到伤害时释放自己的器械，死后还会立刻放出点燃的..."
"<ref=[enemies]mvz2:MannequinTNT>劣质tnt</ref>\n"
"凭什么它们的器械可以重叠放置啊？\n"
"\n"
"<color=blue>我没记错的话，城里的学者说我的种族是人类，而我是他多年以来看到的唯一一个人类</color>\n"
"<color=blue>那这些和我相似的家伙是什么？哪来的？为什么不能和我交流？</color>"
msgstr ""
"For some reason, these... entities look a lot like <ref=[misc]mvz2:steve>Steve</ref>. They can release their own contraptions when "
"damaged, and upon death, immediately drop a lit... low-quality <ref=[enemies]mvz2:MannequinTNT>TNT</ref>.\n"
"\n"
"Why can they stack their contraptions on the same tile?!\n"
"\n"
"<color=blue>If I remember correctly, the scholar in town said my race is Human, and that I'm the only Human he's seen in years.</"
"color>\n"
"<color=blue>Then what are these things that look just like me? Where did they come from? Why can't they talk to me?</color>"

#. Header for enemies mvz2:MutantMannequin
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"突变玩家模型可以粉碎你的器械，会在受到一定伤害时释放自己的器械，并在血量低至一半时投掷<ref=[enemies]mvz2:ImpMannequin>小鬼玩家模型</"
"ref>"
msgstr ""
"Mutant Mannequin can crush your contraptions. It will release its own contraptions when damaged, and will throw an "
"<ref=[enemies]mvz2:ImpMannequin>Imp Mannequin</ref> when its health drops to half."

#. Flavor for enemies mvz2:MutantMannequin
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"不知为何和<ref=[misc]mvz2:steve>史蒂夫</ref>、突变僵尸长得很像的实体，看来人类和僵尸之间确实是有亲缘？\n"
"\n"
"<color=grey>我没见过这种体型的玩家，也不知道这种体型的玩家是怎么来的</color>\n"
"<color=grey>他们看起来不像普通玩家模型突变而来的。</color>\n"
"\n"
"<color=white>他背上背的是什么？</color>"
msgstr ""
"An entity that, for some reason, looks a lot like both <ref=[misc]mvz2:steve>Steve</ref> and a Mutant Zombie. So humans and zombies "
"really are related?\n"
"\n"
"<color=grey>I've never seen a player of this size, and I have no idea how they came to be.</color>\n"
"<color=grey>They don't look like they mutated from a regular Mannequin.</color>\n"
"\n"
"<color=white>What's that on its back?</color>"

#. Header for enemies mvz2:ImpMannequin
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"快速移动的小鬼玩家模型可以被突变怪物丢到战场当中，会在受到一定伤害时释放自己的器械，死亡时放置<ref=[enemies]mvz2:MannequinTNT>玩家模型"
"TNT</ref>。"
msgstr ""
"Fast-moving Imp Mannequins can be thrown into the battlefield by mutant monsters. They will release their own contraptions when "
"damaged, and upon death, will place a <ref=[enemies]mvz2:MannequinTNT>Mannequin TNT</ref>."

#. Flavor for enemies mvz2:ImpMannequin
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"不知为何和<ref=[misc]mvz2:steve>史蒂夫</ref>小时候长得很像的实体。<color=blue>(这不是我！！！)</color>\n"
"和其他同类型实体相比能放置的器械少了一些，或许高级器械都有未成年限制不能玩？"
msgstr ""
"An entity that, for some reason, looks a lot like <ref=[misc]mvz2:steve>Steve</ref> when he was young. <color=blue>(That's not me!!!)</"
"color>\n"
"\n"
"Compared to other entities of the same type, it can place fewer contraptions. Maybe advanced contraptions have an age restriction?"

#. Header for enemies mvz2:MegaImpMannequin
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"快速移动的超级小鬼玩家模型可以被突变怪物丢到战场当中，会在受到一定伤害时释放自己的高级器械，死亡时放置<ref=[enemies]mvz2:MannequinTNT>"
"玩家模型TNT</ref>。"
msgstr ""
"Fast-moving Mega Imp Mannequins can be thrown into the battlefield by mutant monsters. They will release their advanced contraptions "
"when damaged, and upon death, will place a <ref=[enemies]mvz2:MannequinTNT>Mannequin TNT</ref>."

#. Flavor for enemies mvz2:MegaImpMannequin
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid "看来这个小鬼过了未成年限制，可以玩年龄更大一些、更刺激的器械了。"
msgstr "Looks like this little guy has passed the age restriction and can now play with some older, more intense contraptions."

#. Header for enemies mvz2:MannequinTNT
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid "玩家模型TNT会由玩家模型们放置并爆炸造成伤害"
msgstr "Mannequin TNT is placed by Mannequins and explodes to deal damage."

#. Properties for enemies mvz2:MannequinTNT
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"生命：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_health\" /></color>\n"
"半径：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:FireRange\" />格</color>\n"
"伤害：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_damage\" /></color>"
msgstr ""
"Toughness: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_health\" /></color>\n"
"Radius: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:FireRange\" /> blocks</color>\n"
"Damage: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_damage\" /></color>"

#. Flavor for enemies mvz2:MannequinTNT
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"是的，他是敌怪而非器械，你不能用吞噬者把他抢过来。\n"
"这种tnt应该是对面的玩家模型们没有足够的材料，往沙子里掺了土，导致tnt的威力下降了，不过炸起来无论如何都很烦人就是了。\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"<color=grey>我有阴谋论啊，你看这个实体的名字叫做玩家模型TNT，而它的颜色和其他玩家模型一样。</color>\n"
"<color=grey>这是否说明玩家模型TNT和玩家模型是同种■■？</color>"
msgstr ""
"That's right — it's an enemy, not a contraption. You can't claim it with the Devourer.\n"
"\n"
"This TNT was probably made by the opposing Mannequins when they didn't have enough materials. They mixed dirt into the sand, which "
"lowered its explosive power. Still, it's annoying no matter how you look at it.\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"<color=grey>I have a conspiracy theory: this entity's name is Mannequin TNT, and its color is the same as other Mannequins.</color>\n"
"<color=grey>Does that mean Mannequin TNT and Mannequins are the same kind of ■■?</color>"

#. Header for enemies mvz2:RandomZombie
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid "随机僵尸血量归零后会变成其他怪物。"
msgstr "When a Random Zombie's health drops to zero, it transforms into another monster."

#. Flavor for enemies mvz2:RandomZombie
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"怪物们显然也是喜欢过万圣节的，不少怪物就喜欢把南瓜带在头上，让其他怪物猜一猜南瓜后面的是谁。就和开盲盒一样豪丸\n"
"为了你好，别问为什么它叫随机僵尸却能变成骷髅和其他怪物"
msgstr ""
"Monsters clearly love Halloween too. Many of them like to wear pumpkins on their heads, making others guess who's behind the pumpkin. "
"It's like opening a blind box — so much fun.\n"
"\n"
"For your own good, don't ask why something called a Random Zombie can turn into a Skeleton or other monsters."

#. Header for enemies mvz2:RandomImp
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid "随机小鬼僵尸血量归零后会变成其他小鬼类怪物。"
msgstr "When a Random Imp's health drops to zero, it transforms into another Imp-type monster."

#. Flavor for enemies mvz2:RandomImp
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid "这帮坏小鬼来找你们讨要糖了。"
msgstr "These naughty little imps have come to trick-or-treat."

#. Header for enemies mvz2:RandomMutant
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid "突变随机僵尸血量归零后会变成其他突变类怪物。"
msgstr "When a Random Mutant's health drops to zero, it transforms into another Mutant-type monster."

#. Flavor for enemies mvz2:RandomMutant
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"这个突变怪物的伪装做的不是特别好，血量太低了。\n"
"\n"
"嗯...好吧，我觉得应该不是突变类怪物带上了南瓜头。\n"
"这看上去就是这家伙死后原地召唤其他突变怪物。"
msgstr ""
"This mutant monster's disguise isn't very good — its health is just too low.\n"
"\n"
"Well... okay, I don't think it's a Mutant-type monster wearing a pumpkin head.\n"
"It looks more like this thing just spawns other mutant monsters on the spot when it dies."

#. Header for enemies mvz2:RandomSkeleton
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid "随机骷髅血量归零后会变成其他骷髅。"
msgstr "When a Random Skeleton's health drops to zero, it transforms into another Skeleton."

#. Flavor for enemies mvz2:RandomSkeleton
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"比起僵尸们喜欢过万圣节，骷髅们更喜欢过圣诞节（大抵是因为圣诞节服装防寒）。他们为圣诞节准备了精心的服装，这份服装的价格一般能买下几只无"
"弓的骷髅。\n"
"所以当你打破他们的衣服时，他们真的会很生气，以至于变成其他骷髅。"
msgstr ""
"Unlike zombies who prefer Halloween, skeletons seem to enjoy Christmas more — probably because Christmas outfits keep them warm. They "
"prepare elaborate costumes for the holiday, and the price of one outfit could buy several bowless skeletons.\n"
"\n"
"So when you tear apart their clothes, they get genuinely angry — angry enough to turn into another kind of skeleton."

#. Header for enemies mvz2:RandomKingSkeleton
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid "随机国王骷髅血量归零后会变成其他强大的骷髅。"
msgstr "When a Random King Skeleton's health drops to zero, it transforms into another powerful Skeleton."

#. Flavor for enemies mvz2:RandomKingSkeleton
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "enemies.description"
msgid ""
"不同于其他穷鬼<ref=[enemies]mvz2:KingSkeleton>骷髅国王</ref>，随机国王骷髅真的很有钱，他能给自己整一套金衣服，不是镀金，而是纯金！\n"
"这让你打破他的衣服时，他会变得更加愤怒，以至于骷髅种类都有可能改变"
msgstr ""
"Unlike other broke <ref=[enemies]mvz2:KingSkeleton>King Skeletons</ref>, the Random King Skeleton is actually rich. He can afford a "
"full set of golden clothes — not gold-plated, but solid gold!\n"
"\n"
"So when you tear apart his clothes, he gets even angrier — angry enough to change his very skeleton type."

#. Header for artifacts mvz2:almanac
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "artifacts.description"
msgid "<ref=[misc]mvz2:orant>欧兰特</ref>曾经拥有的一本魔法图鉴，会自动记录遇到的所有事物。"
msgstr "A magical almanac once held by <ref=[misc]mvz2:orant>Orant</ref>. Automatically records everything that you come across."

#. Properties for artifacts mvz2:almanac
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "artifacts.description"
msgid "效果：<color=red>战斗开始时，本场战斗每出现2种怪物，获得25能量</color>"
msgstr "Effect: <color=red>+25 energy at the start of the battle for every 2 enemy types present in this battle</color>"

#. Flavor for artifacts mvz2:almanac
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "artifacts.description"
msgid ""
"这本书被记载到了这本书中，而你正在这本书里面看着这本书自己描述这本书。\n"
"当你看着这本书中的这本书的条目而感到头晕目眩时，你正面对着这本书中的这本书对于这本书的描述头晕。\n"
"你该学学语文了。"
msgstr ""
"The book is written in this book, and you are reading an entry in this book about the book itself described by this book.\n"
"When you look at the entry of the book in this book and feel dizzy, you feel dizzy reading the description by this book for the book "
"in this book.\n"
"Time for you to revise your English."

#. Header for artifacts mvz2:hoe
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "artifacts.description"
msgid "农具。"
msgstr "An agricultural tool."

#. Properties for artifacts mvz2:hoe
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "artifacts.description"
msgid "效果：<color=red>每场战斗中，击杀最先出场的怪物</color>"
msgstr "Effect: <color=red>Kills the first monster of every battle</color>"

#. Flavor for artifacts mvz2:hoe
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "artifacts.description"
msgid "踩到了的话被打一下很痛。真的。"
msgstr "If you step on it, it will hurt you a lot. REALLY."

#. Header for artifacts mvz2:dream_key
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "artifacts.description"
msgid "<ref=[misc]mvz2:orant>欧兰特</ref>持有的能够进入其他世界的梦境的钥匙，用于开启一道通往那里的大门。"
msgstr "A key held by <ref=[misc]mvz2:orant>Orant</ref>. Opens the gates to the dreamlands of other worlds."

#. Properties for artifacts mvz2:dream_key
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "artifacts.description"
msgid "效果：<color=red>对器械使用星之碎片会为其恢复所有耐久，并在此期间无敌</color>"
msgstr "Effect: <color=red>Contraptions restore all toughness after being evoked, and is invincible during evocation</color>"

#. Flavor for artifacts mvz2:dream_key
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "artifacts.description"
msgid ""
"能够打开一道通向其他世界的大门的，充满魔力的钥匙。\n"
"但仅能用于前往其他世界的梦境，如果在那里没有类似于管理者的人接应，便无法前往这个世界的现实。\n"
"钥匙上刻着古文：\n"
"于残酷的现实睡去\n"
"于幻想之地\n"
"于光明的尽头\n"
"于梦的苏醒"
msgstr ""
"A key filled with magic that is able to open a doorway to other worlds.\n"
"It can only be used to access the dreams of other worlds however. The reality of the corresponding world cannot be approached via its "
"dream without permission from certain “administrators.”\n"
"There is an ancient inscription engraved on the key:\n"
"To fall asleep in the harsh reality\n"
"To the land of fantasy\n"
"To the end of the light\n"
"To the dream's awakening"

#. Header for artifacts mvz2:the_creatures_heart
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "artifacts.description"
msgid "<ref=[misc]mvz2:frankenstein>科学怪人的怪物</ref>的心脏。"
msgstr "<ref=[misc]mvz2:frankenstein>The Frankenstein's monster</ref>'s heart."

#. Properties for artifacts mvz2:the_creatures_heart
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "artifacts.description"
msgid "效果：<color=red>场上每有一个同类器械，该器械的能量消耗减少5</color>"
msgstr "Effect: <color=red>-5 contraption cost for each same contraption on the battlefield</color>"

#. Flavor for artifacts mvz2:the_creatures_heart
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "artifacts.description"
msgid "……爱……？"
msgstr "...Love...?"

#. Header for artifacts mvz2:sweet_sleep_pillow
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "artifacts.description"
msgid "<ref=[misc]mvz2:doremy>哆来咪</ref>赠予的奇妙枕头，拥有让人安眠的效果。"
msgstr "A wonderful pillow gifted by <ref=[misc]mvz2:doremy>Doremy</ref>, with the ability of making people sleep peacefully."

#. Properties for artifacts mvz2:sweet_sleep_pillow
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "artifacts.description"
msgid "效果：<color=red>器械每秒钟恢复10点耐久</color>"
msgstr "Effect: <color=red>Contraptions restore 10 toughness per second</color>"

#. Flavor for artifacts mvz2:sweet_sleep_pillow
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "artifacts.description"
msgid "好困啊，先不写趣文了。"
msgstr "I'm so sleepy, let's write this flavor later."

#. Header for artifacts mvz2:pagoda_branch
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "artifacts.description"
msgid "槐树上的树枝。"
msgstr "A branch on the pagoda tree."

#. Properties for artifacts mvz2:pagoda_branch
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "artifacts.description"
msgid "效果：<color=red>开始战斗时获得2个星之碎片，但怪物出现数量+200%</color>"
msgstr "Effect: <color=red>+2 starshards at start, but +200% amount of spawned monsters</color>"

#. Flavor for artifacts mvz2:pagoda_branch
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "artifacts.description"
msgid ""
"据说能让你一生荣华富贵，最终却也会因战火流离失所。\n"
"不过，还好这只是一场梦。大槐安国的时光，大梦一场，却走完了人的一生。"
msgstr ""
"Said to bring you a lifetime of glory and wealth, but at the end you will also be displaced by war.\n"
"Fortunately, it was just a dream. The time in Da Huai An Kingdom was just a dream, but it lasted for a whole life."

#. Header for artifacts mvz2:dream_butterfly
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "artifacts.description"
msgid "梦境世界的蝴蝶，两翼异色，分别代表着美梦和噩梦。"
msgstr "A dichromatic butterfly in the Dream World, whose the wings represent sweet dreams and nightmares."

#. Properties for artifacts mvz2:dream_butterfly
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "artifacts.description"
msgid "效果：<color=red>刚放下的器械无敌3秒</color>"
msgstr "Effect: <color=red>Contraptions are invincible for 3 seconds after being built</color>"

#. Flavor for artifacts mvz2:dream_butterfly
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "artifacts.description"
msgid ""
"这种蝴蝶生长在梦境世界，吸取人们的美梦的幸福、放松的甜蜜，沾染噩梦的痛苦、疲劳的花粉。\n"
"蝴蝶的左翼粉色，代表着美梦。上半部分描绘了大槐安国以及其子民的景象，而下半部分则是另一只梦蝶。\n"
"右翼则是红色，代表着噩梦。花纹混沌，其中隐隐约约浮现出人类所恐惧的事物——死亡、骨血、眼睛、尖叫。"
msgstr ""
"This butterfly belongs to the Dream World. It absorbs the felicity and enjoyable relaxations of sweet dreams, staining them with "
"pollen of agony and tiredness of nightmares.\n"
"The pink left wing represents the sweet dreams. The forewing depicts the scenery of Da Huai An Kingdom and her people, while the "
"hindwing depicts another dream butterfly.\n"
"The red right wing represents the nightmares. The patterns are chaotic, faintly hinting at those humanity fears - death, gore, eyes "
"and screams."

#. Header for artifacts mvz2:dark_matter
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "artifacts.description"
msgid "暗物质是宇宙中大量存在的一种不可见的物质。"
msgstr "Dark Matter is an invisible substance that exists in large quantities in the universe."

#. Properties for artifacts mvz2:dark_matter
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "artifacts.description"
msgid "效果：<color=red>器械生产效率×200%，但场景变得黑暗</color>"
msgstr "Effect: <color=red>x200% contraption produce speed, but the battlefield is pitch black</color>"

#. Flavor for artifacts mvz2:dark_matter
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "artifacts.description"
msgid "<color=white>你看不见我</color>"
msgstr "<color=white>You can't see me</color>"

#. Header for artifacts mvz2:bottled_blackhole
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "artifacts.description"
msgid "被装入瓶子中的一个小型黑洞。"
msgstr "A small blackhole packed in a bottle."

#. Properties for artifacts mvz2:bottled_blackhole
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "artifacts.description"
msgid "效果：<color=red>每有一个蓝图空位，器械+10%伤害</color>"
msgstr "Effect: <color=red>+10% contraption damage for each empty blueprint slot</color>"

#. Flavor for artifacts mvz2:bottled_blackhole
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "artifacts.description"
msgid ""
"瓶中的火焰，强化你的攻击；\n"
"瓶中的闪电，精炼你的技能；\n"
"瓶中的旋风，释放你的能力；\n"
"瓶中的黑洞……绑定你的诅咒？"
msgstr ""
"Bottled flame, strengthens your attacks;\n"
"Bottled lightning, refines your skills;\n"
"Bottled tornado, unleashes your abilities;\n"
"Bottled blackhole...binds your curses?"

#. Header for artifacts mvz2:smart_phone
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "artifacts.description"
msgid "从外界流落到<ref=[misc]mvz2:kourindou>香霖堂</ref>的无主智能手机，必要时可以和<ref=[misc]mvz2:tokiko>朱鹭子</ref>通话。"
msgstr ""
"An unclaimed smartphone that drifted into <ref=[misc]mvz2:kourindou>Kourindou</ref> from the outside world. It can contact "
"<ref=[misc]mvz2:tokiko>Tokiko</ref> in emergencies."

#. Properties for artifacts mvz2:smart_phone
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "artifacts.description"
msgid "效果：<color=red>你在最后一波开始前每有10能量，关卡结束时便获得10金钱</color>"
msgstr "Effect: <color=red>Gain 10 money at the end of the level for every 10 energy you have before the final wave begins</color>"

#. Flavor for artifacts mvz2:smart_phone
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "artifacts.description"
msgid ""
"这部手机上装着电话啊，联系人啊，短信啊这些手机必备的应用程序。不过有一个好像有点奇怪，它叫……《MC大战僵尸2》？\n"
"不知道这是什么应用。"
msgstr ""
"This phone comes preinstalled with all the essential apps—phone, contacts, messages—but there's one oddball here called... "
"<i>Minecraft vs. Zombies 2</i>?\n"
"No clue what this is."

#. Header for artifacts mvz2:inverted_mirror
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "artifacts.description"
msgid "被放反了的镜子。"
msgstr "An upside-down mirror."

#. Properties for artifacts mvz2:inverted_mirror
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "artifacts.description"
msgid "效果：<color=red>敌人发射的子弹可以击中其他敌人</color>"
msgstr "Effect: <color=red>Projectiles shot by enemies can hit other enemies</color>"

#. Flavor for artifacts mvz2:inverted_mirror
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "artifacts.description"
msgid "<rotate=\"180\">让我这样看，你很开心吗？</rotate>"
msgstr "<rotate=\"180\">Having a laugh torturing our necks, are we?</rotate>"

#. Header for artifacts mvz2:miracle_mallet_replica
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "artifacts.description"
msgid ""
"<ref=[misc]mvz2:shinmyoumaru>针妙丸</ref>公主赏赐有功之臣史蒂夫的宝物，万宝槌的仿制品，曾被<ref=[misc]mvz2:seija>正邪</ref>用于逃离通"
"缉。"
msgstr ""
"A replica of the Mallet (treasure bestowed by Princess <ref=[misc]mvz2:shinmyoumaru>Shinmyoumaru</ref> upon her meritorious vassal "
"Steve), which was once wielded by <ref=[misc]mvz2:seija>Seija</ref> to evade pursuit."

#. Properties for artifacts mvz2:miracle_mallet_replica
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "artifacts.description"
msgid "效果：<color=red>+15%器械伤害</color>"
msgstr "Effect: <color=red>+15% contraption damage</color>"

#. Flavor for artifacts mvz2:miracle_mallet_replica
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "artifacts.description"
msgid ""
"万宝槌的仿制品，没有什么魔力，只能普通地造成物理伤害。\n"
"\n"
"却说那<ref=[misc]mvz2:seija>小人</ref>参见<ref=[misc]mvz2:shinmyoumaru>小人</ref>，图谋以小搏大。蚍蜉欲撼参天木，终作金靴踏下尘。\n"
"<ref=[misc]mvz2:shinmyoumaru>小人</ref>遭缚，<ref=[misc]mvz2:seija>小人</ref>遁形。小人间彼此算计，最终却成了知己。\n"
"然族民百姓叫苦不迭，城内苍生忧心忡忡。\n"
"亡者之劫已解，天下信任尽失。\n"
"一城之君，怎会落得这般下场？"
msgstr ""
"The replica of the Miracle Mallet. Contains no magic and can only be used to cause physical harm.\n"
"\n"
"<ref=[misc]mvz2:shinmyoumaru>The meager princess</ref> in the clouds, and <ref=[misc]mvz2:seija>she</ref> who filled her head with the "
"clouds. These lowly ones soared towards the heavens, but tragically never saw the light.\n"
"<ref=[misc]mvz2:shinmyoumaru>One</ref> confined, <ref=[misc]mvz2:seija>one</ref> escaped. Yet, from their deception blossomed "
"kinship.\n"
"And so, the castle wept, fraught with worry.\n"
"The calamity of the dead had passed and all trust in her lost.\n"
"Ruler of the castle, for what reason did you fall from grace?"

#. Header for artifacts mvz2:nether_star
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "artifacts.description"
msgid "<ref=[misc]mvz2:wither>凋灵</ref>的掉落物，闪亮的星形物体。"
msgstr "Trophy of <ref=[misc]mvz2:wither>the Wither</ref>, a shiny star-shaped object."

#. Properties for artifacts mvz2:nether_star
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "artifacts.description"
msgid "效果：<color=red>每有4个星之碎片被使用，生成一个星之碎片</color>"
msgstr "Effect: <color=red>Spawns a starshard for every 4 used starshards</color>"

#. Flavor for artifacts mvz2:nether_star
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "artifacts.description"
msgid ""
"看上去似乎是<ref=[misc]mvz2:starshard.miracle_mallet>星之碎片</ref>的完整版，但是这两者的成分似乎完全不一样。\n"
"那么星之碎片到底是什么东西……？"
msgstr ""
"It may look like the star that became <ref=[misc]mvz2:starshard.miracle_mallet>starshards</ref>, but the composition of the two seems "
"completely different.\n"
"So what exactly are the starshards...?"

#. Header for artifacts mvz2:broken_lantern
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "artifacts.description"
msgid ""
"<ref=[misc]mvz2:shining_needle_castle>辉针城</ref>内装饰用的灯笼，被扯坏了。会减少发光器械的光照范围，但提升它们的生产速度和攻击速度。"
msgstr ""
"A lantern used for decoration in <ref=[misc]mvz2:shining_needle_castle>Shining Needle Castle</ref>, it was torn apart. It reduces "
"light range, but increases produce speed and attack speed for glowing contraptions."

#. Properties for artifacts mvz2:broken_lantern
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "artifacts.description"
msgid "效果：<color=red><tag id=\"mvz2:light_source\" />发光的器械+25%生产速度和攻击速度，但×50%光照范围</color>"
msgstr ""
"Effect: <color=red>+25% produce speed and attack speed, but x50% light range for <tag id=\"mvz2:light_source\"/>glowing contraptions</"
"color>"

#. Flavor for artifacts mvz2:broken_lantern
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "artifacts.description"
msgid "呃，还是别告诉<ref=[misc]mvz2:shinmyoumaru>针妙丸</ref>了吧，她可能会生气的。"
msgstr "Uh, better not tell <ref=[misc]mvz2:shinmyoumaru>Shinmyoumaru</ref> about this. She might get mad."

#. Header for artifacts mvz2:manipulative_talismans
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "artifacts.description"
msgid "<ref=[misc]mvz2:seiga>青娥</ref>赠送的一叠符箓，据说可以控制僵尸。"
msgstr "A stack of talismans gifted by <ref=[misc]mvz2:seiga>Seiga</ref>, which is said to be able to control zombies."

#. Properties for artifacts mvz2:manipulative_talismans
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "artifacts.description"
msgid "效果：<color=red>敌方怪物死亡并倒下时，有10%的概率复活并变为友方</color>"
msgstr "Effect: <color=red>Enemy monsters have 10% chance to be revived as friendly ones when they die and faint</color>"

#. Flavor for artifacts mvz2:manipulative_talismans
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "artifacts.description"
msgid ""
"“这是我们之间的秘密哦……”\n"
"她这么告诉你。\n"
"\n"
"但是，可不止你们两个人之间可以有秘密。\n"
"<b>一个人也是可以有秘密的。</b>"
msgstr ""
"\"This is a secret between us...\"\n"
"She told you so.\n"
"\n"
"However, it's not just between the two of you that can have secrets.\n"
"<b>A single person can have secrets too.</b>"

#. Header for artifacts mvz2:greedy_vacuum
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "artifacts.description"
msgid "一种会自动吸取能量粉末，以及星之碎片的装置。"
msgstr "A device that automatically collects energy powder and starshards."

#. Properties for artifacts mvz2:greedy_vacuum
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "artifacts.description"
msgid "效果：<color=red>自动收集能量掉落物以及星之碎片</color>"
msgstr "Effect: <color=red>Auto-collects energy pickups and starshards</color>"

#. Flavor for artifacts mvz2:greedy_vacuum
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "artifacts.description"
msgid ""
"为什么它没有自动吸取宝石的功能？\n"
"你知道的，做人不能太贪。"
msgstr ""
"Why can't it auto-collect gems?\n"
"You know, no need to be greedy."

#. Header for artifacts mvz2:lightbomb
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "artifacts.description"
msgid "<ref=[misc]mvz2:miko>神子</ref>赠送的一种武器，在爆炸时会产生炫目的光芒。"
msgstr "A special weapon gifted by <ref=[misc]mvz2:miko>Miko</ref>, that produces dazzling light when it explodes."

#. Properties for artifacts mvz2:lightbomb
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "artifacts.description"
msgid "效果：<color=red>器械自爆时，对所有敌人额外造成等同于该器械能量消耗的伤害</color>"
msgstr ""
"Effect: <color=red>Whenever a contraption is detonated, deal an additional damage equal to its energy cost to ALL enemies</color>"

#. Flavor for artifacts mvz2:lightbomb
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "artifacts.description"
msgid ""
"神子说，\n"
"首先拔出神圣保险栓。\n"
"接下来数到十七，不能多，也不能少。\n"
"数到十七，你应当数到十七，\n"
"你数到的数字是十七。\n"
"你既不可数十六，也不可数十八，\n"
"除非你接下来数到十七。\n"
"十九已经是数多了。\n"
"一旦数到十七，成为第十七个被数到的数。\n"
"把你的圣光炸弹高高地扔向敌人，\n"
"让这些在我眼前作乱的敌人，\n"
"付出代价。"
msgstr ""
"And Miko spake, saying, \n"
"First shalt thou take out the Holy Pin. \n"
"Then, shalt thou count to seventeen. No more. No less.\n"
"Seventeen shalt be the number thou shalt count,\n"
"and the number of the counting shall be seventeen.\n"
"Eighteen shalt thou not count, neither count thou sixteen, excepting that thou then proceed to seventeen.\n"
"Nineteen is right out.\n"
"Once at the number seventeen,\n"
"being the seventeenth number be reached,\n"
"then, lobbest thou thy Lightbomb towards thy foe,\n"
"who, being naughty in My sight,\n"
"shall snuff it."

#. Header for artifacts mvz2:eye_of_the_giant
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "artifacts.description"
msgid "<ref=[misc]mvz2:the_giant>巨人</ref>的眼睛。"
msgstr "Eyeball of <ref=[misc]mvz2:the_giant>the Giant</ref>."

#. Properties for artifacts mvz2:eye_of_the_giant
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "artifacts.description"
msgid "效果：<color=red>器械x250%伤害，但x50%攻击速度</color>"
msgstr "Effect: <color=red>x250% damage, but x50% attack speed for contraptions</color>"

#. Flavor for artifacts mvz2:eye_of_the_giant
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "artifacts.description"
msgid ""
"巨人的眼睛盯着你看——它似乎有话想对你说。\n"
"\n"
"“朋友啊，你觉得，像<ref=[misc]mvz2:seiga>青娥</ref>那样的家伙，在经历了这种事情过后，会悔过自新，选择当一个好人吗？”\n"
"“会？呵呵，那你就错了。”\n"
"“只要利益足够诱人，这种人就只会愈发、愈发的贪婪——”\n"
"<color=red>“然后，永无止境地<b>贪婪</b>下去！！！”</color>\n"
"\n"
"眼睛愤怒地缩紧了瞳孔。"
msgstr ""
"The eye of the Giant stares at you - as if it has something to say to you.\n"
"\n"
"\"My friend, do you think someone like <ref=[misc]mvz2:seiga>Seiga</ref> would repent and turn over a new leaf after such an ordeal, "
"choosing to become a good person?\"\n"
"\"Will they? Then you're mistaken.\"\n"
"\"As long as the benefits are enticing enough, such people will only grow increasingly, increasingly greedy—\"\n"
"<color=red>\"And remain <b>GREEDY</b> ENDLESSLY!!!\"</color>\n"
"\n"
"The eye angrily constricts its pupil."

#. Header for artifacts mvz2:ufo_toy
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "artifacts.description"
msgid "一个带有魔力的四棱锥玩具。"
msgstr "A magical pyramid-shaped toy."

#. Properties for artifacts mvz2:ufo_toy
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "artifacts.description"
msgid "效果：<color=red>拾取三个同色宝石后，再生成一个同色的宝石</color>"
msgstr "Effect: <color=red>Whenever you collect 3 gems of the same color, spawn another gem of that same color</color>"

#. Flavor for artifacts mvz2:ufo_toy
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "artifacts.description"
msgid ""
"这个玩具形状是个四棱锥。它的底部有四个不同颜色的飞碟凹槽，每个颜色的凹槽里面都有三个飞碟。\n"
"四个侧面中，每个侧面都有三个凹槽，凹槽周围分别被涂上了不同的颜色：<color=red>红红红</color>、<color=green>绿绿绿</color>、<color=blue>"
"蓝蓝蓝</color>、<color=red>红</color><color=green>绿</color><color=blue>蓝</color>。\n"
"你问我这个玩具怎么玩？很简单，只需要把2个<color=red>红色</color>的和1个<color=blue>蓝色</color>的飞碟放在同一面的凹槽上就行了！"
msgstr ""
"This toy is shaped like a pyramid. Its base has four slots for UFO chips, each slot designated for a different color, and each holds "
"three UFO chips.\n"
"Each of the four sides features three slots, with the surrounding areas painted in distinct color schemes: <color=red>Red-Red-Red</"
"color>, <color=green>Green-Green-Green</color>, <color=blue>Blue-Blue-Blue</color>, and <color=red>Red</color>-<color=green>Green</"
"color>-<color=blue>Blue</color>.\n"
"How to play? Simply place two <color=red>Red</color> chips and one <color=blue>Blue</color> chip into the slots on the same side!"

#. Header for artifacts mvz2:dowsing_rods
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "artifacts.description"
msgid "用于寻找宝物的工具。"
msgstr "Tools used to search for treasures."

#. Properties for artifacts mvz2:dowsing_rods
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "artifacts.description"
msgid ""
"效果：<color=red>击杀怪物时有25%概率掉落额外资源</color>\n"
"绿宝石：<color=red>35%</color>\n"
"红宝石：<color=red>9%</color>\n"
"钻石：<color=red>1%</color>\n"
"3红石：<color=red>30%</color>\n"
"随机蓝图：<color=red>25%</color>"
msgstr ""
"Effect: <color=red>Monsters have 25% chance to drop additional resources</color>\n"
"Emerald: <color=red>35%</color>\n"
"Ruby: <color=red>9%</color>\n"
"Diamond: <color=red>1%</color>\n"
"3 Redstones: <color=red>30%</color>\n"
"Random Blueprint: <color=red>25%</color>"

#. Flavor for artifacts mvz2:dowsing_rods
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "artifacts.description"
msgid "现在我要使用这个东西调查你的身体！"
msgstr "I'm going to run this over you, and see what we find."

#. Header for artifacts mvz2:sorcerers_scroll
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "artifacts.description"
msgid "<ref=[misc]mvz2:byakuren>白莲</ref>赠送的魔法物品，通过咏唱来强化人的肉体。"
msgstr "A magical item given by <ref=[misc]mvz2:byakuren>Byakuren</ref>, which strengthens the human body through chanting."

#. Properties for artifacts mvz2:sorcerers_scroll
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "artifacts.description"
msgid ""
"效果：<color=red>星之碎片的效果改为格斗术</color>\n"
"横向拖动：<color=red>冲拳，对一整行内的敌人造成1200点伤害并将其击飞</color>\n"
"向下拖动：<color=red>俯冲，对半径1.5格内的敌人造成1800点伤害</color>\n"
"向上拖动：<color=red>上勾拳，对半径2.5格内的敌人造成400点伤害并将其击飞</color>"
msgstr ""
"Effect: <color=red>Changes the effect of Starshards into fighting techniques</color>\n"
"Horizontal drag: <color=red>Punch, deals 1200 damage to all enemies in an entire row and knocks them back</color>\n"
"Downward drag: <color=red>Dive, deals 1800 damage to all enemies within a 1.5-tile radius</color>\n"
"Upward drag: <color=red>Uppercut, deals 400 damage to all enemies within a 2.5-tile radius and knocks them back</color>"

#. Flavor for artifacts mvz2:sorcerers_scroll
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "artifacts.description"
msgid ""
"白莲在被封印到魔界的期间，曾使用魔界的物质制作过这样一款魔人经卷。\n"
"这经卷完全由经文组成，没有纸这种文字载体。魔界的物质大多有自我意识，那魔人经卷也因此拥有自我意识，可以自动咏唱经文。\n"
"而在那之后，白莲试着仿照魔人经卷制作仿制品，然而没有魔界中的物质，因此就算充满魔力，这仿制品的效果也比之前的差上许多。\n"
"不过，足以让史蒂夫这样的普通人类变成“超人”了。"
msgstr ""
"During her time sealed in Makai, Byakuren used materials from there to create the Sorcerer's Sutra Scroll.\n"
"This scroll was composed entirely of sutras, without using any paper as a medium. Since most materials in Makai possess self-"
"awareness, the Sorcerer's Sutra Scroll consequently also possesses self-awareness, being capable of automatically chanting sutras.\n"
"After that, Byakuren attempted to create a replica of the Sorcerer's Sutra Scroll, but without using the materials from Makai, so even "
"if it was brimming with magic, this replica's effect was still much weaker than the original.\n"
"However, it is still sufficient to turn an ordinary human like Steve into a \"superhuman\"."

#. Header for artifacts mvz2:dragon_tooth
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "artifacts.description"
msgid "<ref=[misc]mvz2:red_dragon>红龙</ref>在打斗中掉下来的一颗牙齿。"
msgstr "A tooth that fell from <ref=[misc]mvz2:red_dragon>Red Dragon</ref> during the fight."

#. Properties for artifacts mvz2:dragon_tooth
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "artifacts.description"
msgid "效果：<color=red>生命值为50%或以下的敌人受到的伤害x200%</color>"
msgstr "Effect: <color=red>Enemies with 50% or less toughness take x200% damage</color>"

#. Flavor for artifacts mvz2:dragon_tooth
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "artifacts.description"
msgid ""
"多年前，高僧手持母亲的牙齿，陷入轮回。\n"
"而如今，少年举起孩子的牙齿，助其解脱。\n"
"这最后的“仿制品”你也拿到了。它的主人完全没有它母亲那般仁慈，口中喷出的满是残暴，对于弱者毫无任何慈悲之心。\n"
"此仇，永世无法平息。"
msgstr ""
"Years ago, as the high monk grasped the tooth of the mother, she became trapped in the cycle of repetition.\n"
"Now, as Steve raises the tooth of the child in his hand, the cycle is broken.\n"
"Even this final “replica” has been obtained by you. Unlike his kind mother, the tooth's owner spat out nothing but brutality from his "
"mouth, showing no mercy at all to the weak.\n"
"This eternal vengeance will never find its end."

#. Header for artifacts mvz2:ShrunkenHead
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "artifacts.description"
msgid "萎缩头颅。"
msgstr "Shrunken Head"

#. Properties for artifacts mvz2:ShrunkenHead
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "artifacts.description"
msgid "效果：<color=red>周期性为场上我方怪物赋予骨质头盔</color>"
msgstr "Effect: <color=red>Periodically grants bone helmets to friendly monsters on the field.</color>"

#. Flavor for artifacts mvz2:ShrunkenHead
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "artifacts.description"
msgid "死灵法师整的都是什么玩意...不能来点阳间的吗"
msgstr "What kind of stuff are the Necromancers messing with... Can't we get something from the living world for once?"

#. Header for artifacts mvz2:AngelsFeather
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "artifacts.description"
msgid "天使的羽毛。"
msgstr "Angel's Feather."

#. Properties for artifacts mvz2:AngelsFeather
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "artifacts.description"
msgid "效果：<color=red>周期性为场上我方实体赋予圣盾</color>"
msgstr "Effect: <color=red>Periodically grants Divine Shields to friendly entities on the field.</color>"

#. Flavor for artifacts mvz2:AngelsFeather
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "artifacts.description"
msgid "愿我不在你身边的时候它能好好保护你"
msgstr "May it protect you well when I'm not by your side."

#. Header for artifacts mvz2:wither_skeleton_skull
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "artifacts.description"
msgid "凋灵骷髅的头颅。"
msgstr "A wither skeleton's skull."

#. Properties for artifacts mvz2:wither_skeleton_skull
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "artifacts.description"
msgid "效果：<color=red>×80%蓝图消耗，但新放下的器械的最大耐久×60%</color>"
msgstr "Effect: <color=red>x80% blueprint cost, but x60% max toughness of newly built contraptions</color>"

#. Flavor for artifacts mvz2:wither_skeleton_skull
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "artifacts.description"
msgid "多么惊悚恐怖的骷髅头！"
msgstr "What a spooky scary skull!"

#. Header for artifacts mvz2:FrankensteinBrain
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "artifacts.description"
msgid "科学怪人的大脑。"
msgstr "Frankenstein's Brain."

#. Properties for artifacts mvz2:FrankensteinBrain
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "artifacts.description"
msgid "效果：<color=red>场上每有一个同类器械，该器械的能量消耗增加10，所有器械的冷却时间+33%，最大血量+25%</color>"
msgstr ""
"Effect: <color=red>For each same contraption on the battlefield, this contraption's energy cost increases by 10. Additionally, all "
"contraptions have +33% cooldown time and +25% maximum Toughness.</color>"

#. Flavor for artifacts mvz2:FrankensteinBrain
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "artifacts.description"
msgid ""
"即使肉体已经死亡，这个大脑也在不断汲取能量并活跃。\n"
"希望这不意味着他知道发生了什么。"
msgstr ""
"Even though the body has died, this brain continues to absorb energy and remain active.\n"
"\n"
"Let's hope that doesn't mean it knows what's happening."

#. Header for artifacts mvz2:NightmareMask
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "artifacts.description"
msgid "梦魇的面具。"
msgstr "Nightmare's Mask."

#. Properties for artifacts mvz2:NightmareMask
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "artifacts.description"
msgid "效果：<color=red>敌人的攻击速度下降20%，但有33%概率不受到本次伤害。</color>"
msgstr "Effect: <color=red>Enemies' attack speed is reduced by 20%, but they have a 33% chance to negate damage when hit.</color>"

#. Flavor for artifacts mvz2:NightmareMask
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "artifacts.description"
msgid "你确定你在攻击敌人吗？"
msgstr "Are you sure you're actually hitting the enemy?"

#. Header for artifacts mvz2:WitherHeartShield
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "artifacts.description"
msgid "凋灵护心盾。"
msgstr "Wither Heart Shield"

#. Properties for artifacts mvz2:WitherHeartShield
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "artifacts.description"
msgid "效果：<color=red>使敌方非飞行怪物常态减少受到的75%伤害，但在攻击时额外受到25%的伤害，使我方怪物额外受到75%的伤害。</color>"
msgstr ""
"Effect: <color=red>Reduces damage taken by non-flying enemies by 75% by default, but they take an additional 25% damage while "
"attacking. Additionally, friendly monsters take 75% more damage.</color>"

#. Flavor for artifacts mvz2:WitherHeartShield
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "artifacts.description"
msgid "这面盾牌以不公平的形式护卫着凋灵的\"心脏\"。"
msgstr "This shield protects the \"heart\" of the Wither in an unfair way."

#. Header for artifacts mvz2:ShadowCellCore
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "artifacts.description"
msgid "暗影细胞核心。"
msgstr "Shadow Cell Core."

#. Properties for artifacts mvz2:ShadowCellCore
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "artifacts.description"
msgid "效果：<color=red>敌人死亡时会生成各种各样的头颅。</color>"
msgstr "Effect: <color=red>Enemies spawn various types of heads upon death.</color>"

#. Flavor for artifacts mvz2:ShadowCellCore
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "artifacts.description"
msgid "暗影细胞核心能够唤醒怪物的有效部分。尸体复活不可怕，尸体的单独一部分复活才可怕。"
msgstr ""
"The Shadow Cell Core can awaken the functional parts of monsters. A corpse coming back to life isn't scary — what's truly terrifying "
"is when individual parts of a corpse come back on their own."

#. Properties for artifacts mvz2:LeftHandBow
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "artifacts.description"
msgid "效果：<color=red>使得怪物拥有难以置信的攻击速度。</color>"
msgstr "Effect: <color=red>Grants monsters an incredibly high attack speed.</color>"

#. Flavor for artifacts mvz2:LeftHandBow
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "artifacts.description"
msgid ""
"吓哭了\n"
"<color=blue>正在播放：恋人を射ち堕とした日 (射杀恋人的那天)</color>\n"
"\n"
"<color=white>有这个后我们就可以不用出左弓版了！</color>"
msgstr ""
"Terrified to tears.\n"
"<color=blue>Now playing: \"The Day I Shot Down a Lover\"</color>\n"
"\n"
"<color=white>Now that we have this, we don't need to make a Left Hand Bow mod anymore!</color>"

#. Flavor for artifacts mvz2:HerobrineSkull
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "artifacts.description"
msgid "<color=red><size=300%><b>    面对我</b></size></color>"
msgstr "<color=red><size=300%><b>   FACE ME</b></size></color>"

#. Name for almanac group mvz2:bosses
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "almanac.group_name"
msgid "头目"
msgstr "Bosses"

#. Name for misc mvz2:frankenstein
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.name"
msgid "科学怪人的怪物"
msgstr "The Creature"

#. Header for misc mvz2:frankenstein
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.description"
msgid "尸块组成的怪物，科幻小说中的杀人魔。"
msgstr "A monster made up of corpses, famously known to be responsible for a number of death cases in science fiction."

#. Properties for misc mvz2:frankenstein
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.description"
msgid ""
"生命：<color=red><var local=\"hp\" /></color>\n"
"特殊：<color=red>放电攻击总是瞄准<ref=[contraptions]mvz2:tnt>TNT</ref>；钢铁身躯反弹特定子弹</color>"
msgstr ""
"Toughness: <color=red><var local=\"hp\" /></color>\n"
"Special: <color=red>Lightning attacks always targets <ref=[contraptions]mvz2:tnt>TNT</ref>; Steel body deflects certain bullets</color>"

#. Flavor for misc mvz2:frankenstein
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.description"
msgid ""
"由于<ref=[misc]mvz2:orant>欧兰特</ref>设置了权限，本条目的部分内容不予显示。\n"
"她的过去与你无关。"
msgstr ""
"Some contents of this entry will not be displayed due to the restrictions set by <ref=[misc]mvz2:orant>Orant</ref>.\n"
"Her past has nothing to do with you."

#. Name for misc mvz2:nightmare_boss
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.name"
msgid "梦魇"
msgstr "Nightmare"

#. Header for misc mvz2:nightmare_boss
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.description"
msgid "梦魇是具有蒙骗感官和腐蚀能力的恐怖魔物，具有无数的化身。"
msgstr "Nightmare is a terrible monster that is able to deceive senses and corrosion, with countless incarnations."

#. Properties for misc mvz2:nightmare_boss
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.description"
msgid ""
"生命：<color=red><var local=\"hp1\" />+<var local=\"hp2\" /></color>\n"
"阶段1：<color=red>召唤传送门，扭曲蓝图，并在受伤一定程度后强制要求你选择负面效果</color>\n"
"阶段2：<color=red>限时击杀，并且需要阻止碾压墙</color>"
msgstr ""
"Toughness: <color=red><var local=\"hp1\" />+<var local=\"hp2\" /></color>\n"
"Phase 1: <color=red>Summon portals, twist the blueprints, and force you to choose a negative effect after being damage for a certain "
"value</color>\n"
"Phase 2: <color=red>Time limited, and you have to stop the crushing walls</color>"

#. Flavor for misc mvz2:nightmare_boss
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.description"
msgid ""
"从前，有个国王做了一场噩梦。梦里他看到一个来自星空的，扭曲而无形的怪物。它化作一匹马在他的土地上狂奔，污染身后的土地。\n"
"国王醒来后立刻找来了占卜师，占卜师称：“这是相当不祥的噩兆。这匹怪物化作的马预示着国家会被怪物入侵并毁灭。”\n"
"国王大吃一惊，随后便让官员发布了悬赏，召集勇者清除王国领土旁的所有怪物。\n"
"一位骑士看到了悬赏，他踏入那华丽而宏伟的王宫，向国王请求参战。国王便赐予了他一副链甲和皮革的马铠。将任务交付于他。\n"
"骑士离开王宫，骑上自己的马，便准备出发了。"
msgstr ""
"There was once a king who had a nightmare. He dreamed of a monster, twisted and formless, coming from beyond the stars. Taking the "
"shape of a horse, it galloped, corrupting all land behind it.\n"
"When the king awoke, he sought out a diviner posthaste. \"This is quite the ill omen, \" said the diviner, \"that the monster took on "
"a horse's form suggests it will invade the kingdom, and destroy it.\"\n"
"Dismayed, the king ordered for a bounty to be put out, and gathered brave souls from all across the kingdom to exterminate all "
"monsters in the vicinity of the kingdom.\n"
"One such knight saw the bounty and stepped into the king's illustrious palace, to whom he pleaded to join the battle. Bestowing upon "
"him a set of chainmail and leather horse armor, the king entrusted this task to him.\n"
"The knight left the palace, mounted his trusty steed and set out on his journey."

#. Name for misc mvz2:wither
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.name"
msgid "凋灵"
msgstr "Wither"

#. Header for misc mvz2:wither
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.description"
msgid "凋灵代表着死亡和枯萎，它会抹除一切生命的迹象。"
msgstr "Wither represents death and withering. It will erase all signs of life."

#. Properties for misc mvz2:wither
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.description"
msgid ""
"生命：<color=red><var local=\"hp\" />，每秒恢复15</color>\n"
"阶段1：<color=red>飞行，发射凋灵头颅，冲刺，啃咬</color>\n"
"阶段2：<color=red>落地，免疫子弹，发射凋灵头颅，冲刺，啃咬，召唤<ref=[misc]mvz2:bedserker>床战士</ref></color>"
msgstr ""
"Toughness: <color=red><var local=\"hp\" />, restores 15 per second</color>\n"
"Phase 1: <color=red>Fly, fire wither skulls, dash, eat your contraptions</color>\n"
"Phase 2: <color=red>Land, Immune to bullets, fire wither skulls, dash, eat your contraptions, summon "
"<ref=[misc]mvz2:bedserker>bedserkers</ref></color>"

#. Flavor for misc mvz2:wither
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.description"
msgid ""
"单枪匹马对付众多的怪物并不是个好主意，骑士打算去招募一些帮手。\n"
"在出发之前，骑士突然被一个人拦住了。他定睛一看，那个人正是国王的占卜师。\n"
"占卜师露出诡异的微笑：“勇者先生，我有一物可以助你一臂之力。”他拿出了一个黑色的骷髅护身符。“这是我专门为你所准备的护身符，请收下吧。”\n"
"“这个有什么用？”骑士问。\n"
"“反转。”\n"
"“什么？”骑士有些不解。\n"
"“呵呵呵，没什么。它的真正用途，你最后会知道的。”占卜师离开了。\n"
"骑士握着手中的护身符。黑色的骷髅头中，闪烁着白色的，诡异的光。"
msgstr ""
"It would have been unwise to take on so many monsters by himself, so the knight sought to enlist aid.\n"
"Just before setting off, a person suddenly stopped him. The knight recognize him as none other than the king's diviner.\n"
"The diviner's lips formed an uncanny smile: \"I have here a boon for you, Brave Hero.\" He produced a protective charm in the shape of "
"a black skull. \"'Tis a charm I had prepared specially for you. Please, accept it.\"\n"
"\"What does it do?\" the knight asked.\n"
"\"It reverses.\"\n"
"\"What?\" said the knight, perplexed.\n"
"\"Hohoh, pay it no mind. You shall know its true purpose when the time comes.\" The diviner left.\n"
"The knight held the protective charm. Within the black skull shined a bright, uncanny white light."

#. Name for misc mvz2:the_giant
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.name"
msgid "巨人"
msgstr "The Giant"

#. Header for misc mvz2:the_giant
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.description"
msgid "巨人是众多僵尸的集合体，它吞噬、吞噬，要吃掉一切。"
msgstr "The Giant is an amalgamation of numerous zombies. It devours and devours, wanting to eat everything."

#. Properties for misc mvz2:the_giant
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.description"
msgid ""
"生命：<color=red><var local=\"hp1\" />+<var local=\"hp2\" /></color>\n"
"阶段1：<color=red>直线尸块；眼弹；重砸；吼叫；喷雾</color>\n"
"阶段2：<color=red>跳跃尸块；眼弹；重砸；吃豆人变形；贪吃蛇变形</color>\n"
"阶段3：<color=red>爬行</color>"
msgstr ""
"Toughness: <color=red><var local=\"hp1\" />+<var local=\"hp2\" /></color>\n"
"Phase 1: <color=red>Straight cells; Eye bullets; Smash; Roar; Breath</color>\n"
"Phase 2: <color=red>Jumping cells; Eye bullets; Smash; Pac-Man transformation; Snake transformation</color>\n"
"Phase 3: <color=red>Crawl</color>"

#. Flavor for misc mvz2:the_giant
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.description"
msgid ""
"骑士招募了六个同伴，开始了讨伐怪物的征途。\n"
"这天，他们斩除了很多野外的怪物，晚上来到了一处偏远处。正打算休息时，却突然听到悬崖下面传来了声音。\n"
"骑士上前一看，发现居然有很多人的尸体堆积在这里，不由得大吃一惊。这些人的尸体全部都骨瘦如柴，在这尸堆之上，还有一颗黑色的球体在上空盘"
"旋。\n"
"“这些人很可能是几年前大饥荒时被饿死的人。”有一位同伴似乎了解一些事情。\n"
"“当时人们颗粒无收，民不聊生。有人请求王室放出一些食粮，却遭到了拒绝，甚至把这些人的尸体集中处理掉了。”\n"
"骑士想起之前那宏伟的皇宫和外面的泔水，皱了皱眉头。\n"
"这些尸体上不断渗出黑色的怨念，汇聚到那颗黑色的球体中。那颗球体越来越大，最后把所有的尸体都吞噬，融合成了一只巨大的僵尸。他发出饥饿的哀"
"嚎，向他们的队伍发起攻击。\n"
"所有人都举起了武器，准备和这位巨人战斗。\n"
"他们和巨人一直战斗到天亮。最后，巨人的核心被摧毁，所有尸体又再一次散落到悬崖下方。只不过这次，再也没有怨念出现了。\n"
"骑士往下面扔了一点食物，随后带着大家离开了。\n"
"“他们已经饿了很久了，就让他们吃一点吧。”"
msgstr ""
"The Knight recruited six companions and set out on a journey to slay monsters.\n"
"That day, they slew many wild monsters and arrived at a remote place by nightfall. Just as they were about to rest, they suddenly "
"heard sounds coming from beneath the cliff.\n"
"The Knight stepped forward to take a look and was shocked to find many thin skeletal bodies piled up there. Above this pile of "
"corpses, there was a black sphere hovering in the air. \n"
"\"These people were most likely those who starved to death during the great famine years ago.\" One companion seemed to know something "
"about it.\n"
"\"Back then, people had no harvest and suffered terribly. Some begged the royal family to give out some food, but were refused. They "
"even disposed the bodies in mass graves.\"\n"
"The Knight frowned as he recalled that magnificent royal palace and the foul waste outside.\n"
"Black resentment kept seeping from these corpses, gathering into the black sphere. The sphere grew larger and larger until  finally, "
"it devoured all the corpses, merging into a giant zombie. It let a ravenous howl, attacking the group.\n"
"Everyone raised their weapons, ready to fight the Giant.\n"
"They kept fighting the Giant until dawn. Finally, the Giant's core was destroyed, and the corpses tumbled back down beneath the cliff. "
"This time however, no trace of resentment lingered.\n"
"The knight tossed some food down below, then led the group away.\n"
"\"They've been starving for ages. Let them have this much to eat.\""

#. Name for misc mvz2:red_dragon
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.name"
msgid "红龙"
msgstr "The Red Dragon"

#. Header for misc mvz2:red_dragon
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.description"
msgid "红龙是一头喷火的猛兽，为了报杀母之仇，定要摧毁幻想乡的一切。"
msgstr "The Red Dragon is a ferocious beast that breathes fire. To avenge its mother, it swears to destroy all of Gensokyo."

#. Properties for misc mvz2:red_dragon
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.description"
msgid ""
"生命：<color=red><var local=\"hp\" /></color>\n"
"阶段1：<color=red>火焰弹、龙卷风、吞食、火焰吐息</color>\n"
"阶段2：<color=red>巨型火球、火焰龙卷风、火焰流星、飞空、扫尾</color>"
msgstr ""
"Toughness: <color=red><var local=\"hp\" /></color>\n"
"Phase 1: <color=red>Fire Charges, Tornado, Devour, Fire Breath</color>\n"
"Phase 2: <color=red>Giant Fire Ball, Flame Tornado, Meteor, Fly, Tail Swipe</color>"

#. Flavor for misc mvz2:red_dragon
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.description"
msgid ""
"骑士一行人踏入了一处巨大的山洞，他们举着火把慢慢前进着。\n"
"山洞中遍布着很多骸骨。有羊的，牛的，其他怪物的，遍地都是——但好像唯独没有人的头骨。\n"
"骑士听着深处的动静，最终带领队伍找到了他们的目标——一头红龙。\n"
"红龙见到他们，十分惊讶。它张开口，说出了人类的语言：\n"
"“你们这些人类，来到这里是想做什么？这里不是你们应该来的地方！”\n"
"有一位同伴争先答到：\n"
"“国王的梦预示着王国会被怪物毁灭，因此，我们以国王的名义，要取你的龙头！”\n"
"红龙瞪大了眼睛，随后又突然尖锐起来。那眼中包含的是悲哀，还有——愤怒。\n"
"“我曾亲眼看见我的母亲死于你们人类之手。她杀死了很多的人类，导致人类群起而攻之。从那时，我就对你们人类产生了畏惧之心。“\n"
"“一百年来，我一直避免招惹你们，我本以为这样就不会引来杀身之祸。如今，你们却因为一场无聊的梦便要我的命？”\n"
"“这就是我所应得的东西？！只是因为你们这群人类自诩为高等生灵？！”\n"
"红龙的愤怒化作火焰从口中喷出，瞬间点燃了整片巢穴。\n"
"在那场火焰和钢铁交织的战斗中，红龙逐渐落入下风。最后红龙被骑士刺中喉咙，倒在了地上。\n"
"“贪婪……会成为你们人类的坟墓……”\n"
"“我……诅咒……你们……”\n"
"红龙就这样闭上了眼睛。\n"
"龙巢的火熄灭了。同伴们将龙的尸体分解，把它的牙、眼、爪、骨、鳞、和心脏作为战利品收集了起来。\n"
"骑士默默看着他们兴奋的样子，最后却什么也没要。"
msgstr ""
"The Knight and his group ventured into a giant cave, slowly advancing deeper with torches in their hands.\n"
"The cave was filled with countless skeletal remains of sheep, cows, and other monsters. They were scattered throughout the ground, yet "
"there did not seem to be any human skulls.\n"
"The Knight listened to the movements of the depths and eventually led his team to their target—a red dragon.\n"
"The Red Dragon was very surprised to see them. It opened its mouth and spoke in the tongue of humans:\n"
"\"You humans, what do you think you're doing here? This is no place for your kind!\"\n"
"A companion rushed to answer:\n"
"\"The King's dream foretells the kingdom's imminent destruction by monsters. Thus, in the name of the King, we have come for your head!"
"\"\n"
"The Red Dragon's eyes widened, then suddenly sharpened. Those eyes were filled with sorrow—and rage.\n"
"\"I witnessed my mother's death at the hands of you humans. She killed many of your kind, which led to them rising against her. From "
"that point on, I have developed a fear of you humans.\"\n"
"\"For a hundred years, I have avoided provoking you so that no harm would come to me. Yet today, you come for my life because of some "
"stupid dream?\"\n"
"\"Is this what I deserve?! Just because you humans deem yourselves to be superior beings?!\"\n"
"The Red Dragon's fury manifested into flames breathed from its mouth, instantly setting its entire lair ablaze.\n"
"In that fierce battle where fire and steel clashed, the Red Dragon slowly fell into a disadvantage. In the end, with a final stab to "
"the throat by the Knight, the Red Dragon collapsed to the ground.\n"
"\"Greed... will become you humans' grave...\"\n"
"\"This is my... curse... to you all...\"\n"
"With that, the Red Dragon's eyes fell shut.\n"
"The fire in the dragon's lair died out. The Knight's companions dismembered the Dragon's corpse, collecting its teeth, eyes, claws, "
"bones, scales, and heart as their trophies.\n"
"The Knight watched their exhilaration in silence. In the end, he claimed nothing for himself."

#. Name for almanac group mvz2:misc_entities
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "almanac.group_name"
msgid "杂项实体"
msgstr "Misc Entities"

#. Name for misc mvz2:miner
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.name"
msgid "矿场"
msgstr "Miner"

#. Header for misc mvz2:miner
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.description"
msgid "史蒂夫制造的自动矿场，会在白天的时候自动挖掘红石矿。"
msgstr "Steve's automated miner, which automatically digs for redstone during the day."

#. Properties for misc mvz2:miner
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.description"
msgid ""
"生产时间：<color=red>10秒</color>\n"
"提供能量：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:redstone_value\"/></color>"
msgstr ""
"Produce time: <color=red>10 seconds</color>\n"
"Energy production: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:redstone_value\"/></color>"

#. Flavor for misc mvz2:miner
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.description"
msgid ""
"史蒂夫精通机械，这台自动矿场出自他的手中。依靠太阳能工作，自动寻找地下存储的红石矿，然后将其运输到地表。\n"
"……不过既然它需要太阳能，为什么不直接把太阳能变成能量呢？"
msgstr ""
"Steve is good at mechanics, and this miner is built by him. With the help of solar energy, it can automatically find the underground "
"deposits of redstone ore, and then transport it to the surface for energy.\n"
"...But since it needs solar energy, why not directly turn solar energy into energy?"

#. Name for misc mvz2:minecart
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.name"
msgid "矿车"
msgstr "Minecart"

#. Header for misc mvz2:minecart
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.description"
msgid "史蒂夫家里的最后防线，当怪物突破器械阵线后会碾压前方一行的敌人。"
msgstr "Steve’s House’s last line of defense. It will crush all enemies in the lane when they get too close to the house."

#. Flavor for misc mvz2:minecart
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.description"
msgid ""
"“爷爷，这个上面有个熔炉的矿车是什么啊？”\n"
"“孩子，坐下，让我给你讲个故事。”\n"
"“那是我年轻的时候的故事……”"
msgstr ""
"There was a time when Minecarts with Furnaces were a thing.\n"
"Only the cool kids will remember this."

#. Name for misc mvz2:gargoyle_statue
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.name"
msgid "石像鬼雕像"
msgstr "Gargoyle Statue"

#. Header for misc mvz2:gargoyle_statue
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.description"
msgid "石像鬼雕像会在最后一波时变成石像鬼。"
msgstr "Gargoyles will be revived from statues when the final wave comes."

#. Properties for misc mvz2:gargoyle_statue
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.description"
msgid "耐久：<color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_health\" /></color>"
msgstr "Toughness: <color=red><var id=\"mvz2:entity_health\" /></color>"

#. Flavor for misc mvz2:gargoyle_statue
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.description"
msgid ""
"<ref=[misc]mvz2:eternal_night_swamp>永夜沼泽</ref>的诅咒不止将天空定格在了午夜，它也把地下的石块塑造成雕像的形状，将它们移出地面。这些"
"雕像一旦受到魔电的冲击，便会被赋予生命而变成活物。"
msgstr ""
"The curse of <ref=[misc]mvz2:eternal_night_swamp>Eternal Night Swamp</ref> doesn't only freeze the time of the midnight sky. It also "
"shapes the stones underground into statues, and make them rise from the ground. Once the enchanted lightning strikes these statues, "
"they will be given life and become living creatures."

#. Name for misc mvz2:pumpkin_carriage
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.name"
msgid "南瓜马车"
msgstr "Pumpkin Carriage"

#. Header for misc mvz2:pumpkin_carriage
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.description"
msgid "<ref=[misc]mvz2:eternal_night_swamp>永夜沼泽</ref>的最后防线，会发出绿色光芒，当怪物突破器械阵线后会碾压前方一行的敌人。"
msgstr ""
"The last line of defense in the <ref=[misc]mvz2:eternal_night_swamp>Swamp</ref>. It emits a green glow, and will crush all enemies in "
"the lane when they get too close to the house."

#. Flavor for misc mvz2:pumpkin_carriage
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.description"
msgid "南瓜中的永恒火焰无法被水浇灭，被风吹灭或者被其他化学反应影响。如果你想藏身的话最好把它扔了——这玩意真的关不掉。"
msgstr ""
"The eternal flame inside the pumpkins cannot be extinguished by water, blown out by wind or affected by chemical reactions. But some "
"people just can't sleep with it - it shines so bright and you literally can’t turn this thing off."

#. Name for misc mvz2:napstablook
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.name"
msgid "小幽灵"
msgstr "Napstablook"

#. Header for misc mvz2:napstablook
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.description"
msgid "小幽灵会在你使用铁剑击中它时生气，然后麻痹你的剑。"
msgstr "Napstablook will get ANGERY when you hit it with your sword, paralyzing the sword for a short while."

#. Flavor for misc mvz2:napstablook
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.description"
msgid "只是个路过的幽灵而已。"
msgstr "Just a ghost passing by."

#. Name for misc mvz2:nyan_cat
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.name"
msgid "彩虹猫"
msgstr "Nyan Cat"

#. Header for misc mvz2:nyan_cat
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.description"
msgid "彩虹猫能萌死任何接触到的敌人。"
msgstr "Nyan Cats are soooo cute that they make any enemy touching it die."

#. Flavor for misc mvz2:nyan_cat
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.description"
msgid "NyanNyanNyanNyanNyanNyanNyanNyanNyanNyanNyanNyanNyanNyanNyanNyanNyanNyanNyanNyanNyanNyanNyanNyanNyanNyanNyanNyanNyanNyanNyanNyan"
msgstr "NyanNyanNyanNyanNyanNyanNyanNyanNyanNyanNyanNyanNyanNyanNyanNyanNyanNyanNyanNyanNyanNyanNyanNyanNyanNyanNyanNyanNyanNyanNyanNyan"

#. Name for misc mvz2:boat_zombie
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.name"
msgid "船僵尸"
msgstr "Boat Zombie"

#. Header for misc mvz2:boat_zombie
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.description"
msgid "船僵尸能够浮在水上——甚至是云上作战。"
msgstr "Boat Zombies can float on water—and even atop clouds."

#. Flavor for misc mvz2:boat_zombie
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.description"
msgid "直接把自己身子穿在船上真的不会漏水么？当然不会咕噜咕噜咕噜"
msgstr "Wouldn't there be leaks if they put their bodies directly onto the boats? Of course not—glug glug glug"

#. Flavor for misc mvz2:boat_zombie
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.description"
msgid "它是怎么浮在空中的？我的朋友，你都已经在天上乘船了，船僵尸能浮在空中又怎么样呢？"
msgstr "How do they float in the air? My friend, you're already on a ship in the sky, so what if they float in the air too?"

#. Name for misc mvz2:nyaightmare
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.name"
msgid "噩梦猫"
msgstr "Nyaightmare"

#. Header for misc mvz2:nyaightmare
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.description"
msgid "噩梦猫会刺死任何它所恨的人。"
msgstr "Nyaightmares will pierce anyone it hates to death."

#. Flavor for misc mvz2:nyaightmare
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.description"
msgid "“我恨你。”"
msgstr "\"I HATE YOU.\""

#. Name for misc mvz2:bowl_chariot
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.name"
msgid "碗车"
msgstr "Bowl Cart"

#. Header for misc mvz2:bowl_chariot
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.description"
msgid "碗车在碰到敌人后会冲锋，并把碗里的巨石掉出来二次打击敌人。"
msgstr ""
"The bowl cart is activated when an enemy touches it. It also drops a boulder from within the bowl to deal a second blow to enemies."

#. Flavor for misc mvz2:bowl_chariot
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.description"
msgid "之前的小人族剩下的部分防御工事，不过巨石的效果对凋灵骷髅们没什么作用就是了——甚至还不如直接用车撞死它们。"
msgstr ""
"A remnant of the inchling's defenses. However, boulders have proved quite ineffective against wither skeletons—crushing them with the "
"cart itself would have more of an effect."

#. Name for misc mvz2:reverse_satellite
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.name"
msgid "反则卫星"
msgstr "Reversal Satellite"

#. Header for misc mvz2:reverse_satellite
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.description"
msgid "反则卫星是在一大波怪物出现后，在<ref=[misc]mvz2:shining_needle_castle>辉针城</ref>中出现的可疑飞行物，会将你的视野180度旋转。"
msgstr ""
"Reversal Satellites are suspicious flying objects found in the <ref=[misc]mvz2:shining_needle_castle>Shining Needle Castle</ref>. They "
"spawn following a huge wave of zombies, and turn your vision upside down."

#. Properties for misc mvz2:reverse_satellite
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.description"
msgid ""
"生命：<color=red><var local=\"hp\" /></color>\n"
"停留时间：<color=red>30秒</color>"
msgstr ""
"Toughness: <color=red><var local=\"hp\" /></color>\n"
"Stay Time: <color=red>30 seconds</color>"

#. Flavor for misc mvz2:reverse_satellite
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.description"
msgid ""
"这些卫星似乎是城内的凋灵骷髅根据辉针城的魔力制成的武器，用于干扰敌人的判断。\n"
"……不过话说回来，凋灵骷髅们居然有这种智慧？这种科技水平？\n"
"……甚至还可以影响人们的认知？"
msgstr ""
"Forged seemingly by the hands of Wither Skeletons, these satellites are imbued with the arcane energies of the castle, a weapon to "
"confound and disorient.\n"
"\n"
"Yet one cannot help but marvel: since when have these withered fiends possessed such cunning? Such mastery of technology, warping the "
"very fabric of perception?"

#. Name for misc mvz2:ballista
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.name"
msgid "小型弩车"
msgstr "Mini Ballista"

#. Header for misc mvz2:ballista
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.description"
msgid "小型弩车在碰到敌人后会发射致命弩箭，并向前冲锋碾压敌人。"
msgstr "Mini ballista launches deadly bolts upon collision with enemies, then charges forward to crush them."

#. Properties for misc mvz2:ballista
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.description"
msgid "伤害：<color=red>58115310</color>"
msgstr "Damage: <color=red>58115310</color>"

#. Flavor for misc mvz2:ballista
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.description"
msgid "你别问为什么能直接压死还要发射弩箭，不然这就不叫“画蛇添足”了。"
msgstr ""
"Don’t need to be so high-strung about shooting a seemingly extra bolt when it could’ve just crushed the monsters outright - it’s a "
"rule of thumb to always leave a parting shot."

#. Name for misc mvz2:monster_spawner
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.name"
msgid "刷怪笼"
msgstr "Monster Spawner"

#. Header for misc mvz2:monster_spawner
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.description"
msgid "刷怪笼会在一大波怪物来临时召唤一只其内部的怪物。"
msgstr "Spawner will summon a monster inside it when a huge wave of monsters is approaching."

#. Flavor for misc mvz2:monster_spawner
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.description"
msgid "我的水桶、告示牌和灵魂沙呢？"
msgstr "Where're my water buckets, signs and soul sands?"

#. Name for misc mvz2:unzan_fist
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.name"
msgid "云山之拳"
msgstr "Unzan's Fist"

#. Header for misc mvz2:unzan_fist
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.description"
msgid "云山之拳在碰到敌人后会向前发射，击杀并打飞一行的敌怪。"
msgstr "Unzan's Fist launches forward upon contact with an enemy, killing and knocking back a row of monsters."

#. Flavor for misc mvz2:unzan_fist
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.description"
msgid ""
"云山是由云朵变化过来的僧侣妖怪，守护在僧侣云居 一轮身旁。\n"
"在命莲寺众人的讨论和计划下，云山为圣辇船提供了一些云朵拳头作为最终防线。\n"
"可别小看这些拳头，被击飞的怪物一下子可是能飞十万八千里。"
msgstr ""
"Unzan is a monk youkai transformed from clouds who guards Ichirin Kumoi.\n"
"Through discussions and planning by the members of Myouren Temple, Unzan provided the Palanquin Ship some cloud fists as a final line "
"of defense.\n"
"Don't underestimate these fists—monsters punched by them will get knocked back 108,000 li away in an instant."

#. Name for misc mvz2:paratrooper_zombie
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.name"
msgid "伞兵僵尸"
msgstr "Paratrooper Zombie"

#. Header for misc mvz2:paratrooper_zombie
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.description"
msgid "伞兵僵尸会在圣辇船的每一大波怪物到来时从天而降，然后将雨伞作为护盾。"
msgstr ""
"Paratrooper Zombies descend from the sky during each huge wave of monsters on the Palanquin Ship, using their umbrellas as shields."

#. Properties for misc mvz2:paratrooper_zombie
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.description"
msgid ""
"生命：<color=red><var local=\"hp\"/>+<var local=\"shield_hp\" />（雨伞）+？（随机头盔）</color>\n"
"速度：<color=red><var local=\"speed\"/></color>"
msgstr ""
"Toughness: <color=red><var local=\"hp\"/>+<var local=\"shield_hp\" /> (umbrella)+? (random helmet)</color>\n"
"Speed: <color=red><var local=\"speed\"/></color>"

#. Flavor for misc mvz2:paratrooper_zombie
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.description"
msgid "危险动作，<ref=[enemies]mvz2:imp>小鬼僵尸</ref>请勿轻易尝试。"
msgstr "Dangerous action. <ref=[enemies]mvz2:imp>Imps</ref> should not attempt this."

#. Name for almanac group mvz2:characters
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "almanac.group_name"
msgid "人物"
msgstr "Characters"

#. Name for misc mvz2:villager
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.name"
msgid "村民"
msgstr "Villager"

#. Header for misc mvz2:villager
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.description"
msgid "与史蒂夫共同生活的白衣村民，原名戴夫。"
msgstr "A crazy villager in a white outfit who lives together with Steve. His name is Dave."

#. Properties for misc mvz2:villager
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.description"
msgid ""
"原画师：<color=red>Cuerzor58</color>\n"
"皮肤画师：<color=red>我想喝柠檬水</color>"
msgstr ""
"Vanilla Artist: <color=red>Cuerzor58</color>\n"
"Skin Artist: <color=red>我想喝柠檬水</color>"

#. Flavor for misc mvz2:villager
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.description"
msgid ""
"史蒂夫从小到大的抚养者，在几年前突然变得疯狂，言行举止无法被人理解。\n"
"常与史蒂夫提起幻想乡的事情，而在今天终于踏上了征途。"
msgstr ""
"Steve's caregiver since he was young, suddenly went crazy a few years ago and couldn't be understood.\n"
"Often discussed with Steve about Gensokyo, and finally embarked on their journey today."

#. Name for misc mvz2:orant
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.name"
msgid "欧兰特"
msgstr "Orant"

#. Header for misc mvz2:orant
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.description"
msgid "欧兰特是一名灵魂术士，可以操纵恐惧和灵魂。"
msgstr "Orant is a soul sorceress, can manipulate fear and souls."

#. Properties for misc mvz2:orant
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.description"
msgid "画师：<color=red>Cuerzor58</color>"
msgstr "Artist: <color=red>Cuerzor58</color>"

#. Flavor for misc mvz2:orant
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.description"
msgid ""
"她不想让你知道她太多的事情。\n"
"只需要知道她常和灵魂与恐惧作伴就可以了。"
msgstr ""
"She doesn't want you to know too much about her.\n"
"All you need to know is that she is with souls and fear."

#. Name for misc mvz2:doremy
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.name"
msgid "哆来咪·苏伊特"
msgstr "Doremy Sweet"

#. Header for misc mvz2:doremy
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.description"
msgid "哆来咪·苏伊特是梦境世界的管理者，管理着人们的梦境。"
msgstr "Doremy Sweet is the administrator of Dream World, and manages everyone's dreams."

#. Flavor for misc mvz2:doremy
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.description"
msgid ""
"看管着梦境世界的貘妖怪，能够观察、改变或吞食人的梦境。\n"
"被真身前来的史蒂夫和<ref=[misc]mvz2:villager>村民</ref>两人吓了一跳，但似乎从史蒂夫身上看到了一些有趣的梦。"
msgstr ""
"A baku who administers the Dream World, has the ability to observe, change and consume others' dreams.\n"
"Was shocked by Steve and <ref=[misc]mvz2:villager>Villager</ref> who arrived in their physical bodies, but she seems to have seen some "
"interesting dreams from Steve."

#. Name for misc mvz2:tokiko
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.name"
msgid "朱鹭子"
msgstr "Tokiko"

#. Header for misc mvz2:tokiko
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.description"
msgid "常在<ref=[misc]mvz2:kourindou>香霖堂</ref>附近活动的读书妖怪，在<ref=[misc]mvz2:rinnosuke>霖之助</ref>失踪后成为了香霖堂的店主。"
msgstr ""
"A book-reading youkai who often hangs out near <ref=[misc]mvz2:kourindou>Kourindou</ref>. She took over Kourindou when "
"<ref=[misc]mvz2:rinnosuke>Rinnosuke</ref> disappeared."

#. Flavor for misc mvz2:tokiko
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.description"
msgid ""
"她其实原本并没有名字，被大家叫多了“朱鹭子”，这世上便就有了“朱鹭子”。\n"
"鸟脑袋，有些呆呆的。比较天真，喜欢看童话故事。\n"
"喜欢看书，书被抢走了的话还会大发雷霆。\n"
"所以不要随便抢别人的书哦。"
msgstr ""
"She originally didn't have a name, but since everyone calls her \"Tokiko\", the world would come to know her as \"Tokiko\".\n"
"She's a birdbrain and a bit of an airhead. An innocent girl who loves to read fairy tales.\n"
"Very much loves to read. Her wrath when her books are taken away is like no other.\n"
"So think twice before you steal someone's book."

#. Name for misc mvz2:seija
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.name"
msgid "鬼人 正邪"
msgstr "Seija Kijin"

#. Header for misc mvz2:seija
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.description"
msgid "一名天邪鬼，曾利用了<ref=[misc]mvz2:shinmyoumaru>针妙丸</ref>，妄图使用万宝槌的力量颠覆幻想乡的强弱规则。"
msgstr ""
"An amanojaku who once manipulated <ref=[misc]mvz2:shinmyoumaru>Shinmyoumaru</ref>, and sought to overturn the hierarchy of society in "
"Gensokyo with the power of the Miracle Mallet."

#. Flavor for misc mvz2:seija
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.description"
msgid ""
"正邪是一名天邪鬼。天邪鬼这种妖怪性格扭曲，喜欢和正常人反着干，渴望着把一切事物逆转过去。\n"
"曾为了颠覆幻想乡的格局而利用了针妙丸，使用了她的万宝槌，甚至动员了幻想乡的弱势妖怪妄图推翻一切。\n"
"不过，最终这种荒唐的闹剧还是遭到了幻想乡众人的镇压，她自己也因此曾遭到通缉。\n"
"如今她在四处游荡，成了个不受任何人欢迎的家伙。然而，天邪鬼对“逆转”的那种渴望，似乎也并不会轻易被熄灭就是了。"
msgstr ""
"Seija is an amanojaku, whose very existence is a defiance of the natural order. A creature born to revel in reversal.\n"
"\n"
"The weak would rise, the strong would fall — such was her mad dream. She manipulated Shinmyoumaru in order to wield her mallet of "
"boundless potential, rallied the downtrodden youkais, and set her sights on a world turned upside down.\n"
"\n"
"However, the denizens of Gensokyo united, and quelled her ridiculous plot. Branded a criminal, she now wanders, a fugitive endorsed by "
"none. But beware — the fire of defiance is not so easily extinguished."

#. Flavor for misc mvz2:seija
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.description"
msgid ""
"在史蒂夫从<ref=[misc]mvz2:palanquin_ship>圣辇船</ref>坠落之后，似乎是她救了史蒂夫。\n"
"然而此举并不是出于好心，而是盯上了史蒂夫身上的<ref=[misc]mvz2:starshard.ufo_fragment>星之碎片</ref>。\n"
"“只要拥有这些星之碎片，说不定就能恢复针妙丸的地位，再颠覆整个幻想乡。”\n"
"她这样想着。"
msgstr ""
"After Steve fell from the <ref=[misc]mvz2:palanquin_ship>Palanquin Ship</ref>, it seemed that she was the one who saved him.\n"
"However, this wasn't an act out of kindness, but rather because she had her eyes on the "
"<ref=[misc]mvz2:starshard.ufo_fragment>Starshards</ref> that Steve carries.\n"
"\"As long as I have these Starshards, I might be able to restore Shinmyoumaru's status and overturn the entire Gensokyo.\" This was "
"what she thought."

#. Name for misc mvz2:shinmyoumaru
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.name"
msgid "少名 针妙丸"
msgstr "Shinmyoumaru Sukuna"

#. Header for misc mvz2:shinmyoumaru
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.description"
msgid "一寸法师的后代，辉针城的城主，如今小人族的领导者。"
msgstr "A descendant of Issun-boshi, the ruler of Shining Needle Castle, the current leader of the inchlings."

#. Flavor for misc mvz2:shinmyoumaru
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.description"
msgid ""
"针妙丸是第一位小人族——一寸法师的后代。\n"
"曾因为听信了天邪鬼——<ref=[misc]mvz2:seija>鬼人 正邪</ref>的谗言，使用了万宝槌的力量给幻想乡造成了混乱，因此曾被前来解决异变的一众人俘"
"获。\n"
"后来参与了针对鬼人正邪的围剿，但在之后，两人还是成为了朋友。\n"
"曾也有小人族的先祖遗忘一寸法师的祖训，试图利用万宝槌的力量改变一切，但是却付出了惨痛的代价。如今针妙丸也遗忘了这段历史，重蹈覆辙。\n"
"不过，至少在她这一代，这些教训是再也忘不掉的了。"
msgstr ""
"Shinmyoumaru is a descendant of Issun-boshi, the first ever inchling.\n"
"\n"
"Once, she heeded the honeyed lies of <ref=[misc]mvz2:seija>Seija Kijin</ref>, an amanojaku, and unleashed the power of the Miracle "
"Mallet upon Gensokyo, shifting the balance of all things. For her transgressions, she was captured by those who rose to resolve the "
"incident.\n"
"\n"
"She later joined the very force that sought to bring Seija to justice. And though their paths were once opposed, they now walk as… "
"friends.\n"
"\n"
"Her ancestors, too, once forgot the teachings of Issun-boshi, wielding the mallet's power for their grand ambitions. And like them, "
"Shinmyoumaru paid a heavy price for her hubris. The lessons of the past, though forgotten, have a way of repeating themselves. \n"
"\n"
"But now, in her time, those lessons are etched in blood and memory — never to be forgotten again."

#. Name for misc mvz2:futo
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.name"
msgid "物部 布都"
msgstr "Mononobe no Futo"

#. Header for misc mvz2:futo
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.description"
msgid "日本古代大氏族物部氏的后人，<ref=[misc]mvz2:miko>丰聪耳 神子</ref>的手下。"
msgstr "A descendant of Japan's ancient Mononobe clan and a follower of <ref=[misc]mvz2:miko>Toyosatomimi no Miko</ref>."

#. Properties for misc mvz2:futo
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.description"
msgid "画师：<color=red>小幽喜欢口乙烯</color>"
msgstr "Artist: <color=red>小幽喜欢口乙烯</color>"

#. Flavor for misc mvz2:futo
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.description"
msgid ""
"一千余年前，伴随着其主丰聪耳神子成为尸解仙，陷入长眠。后来在多年前，于梦殿大祀庙随丰聪耳神子等人一起复活。\n"
"思考方式比较古董，千年后的很多事情都无法理解，古文和现代语法混杂的讲话方式也有些让人听不懂。\n"
"后来也被时代的浪潮推动，开始慢慢习惯现代的生活了，变成了一位看起来稍微有点傻傻的女孩。"
msgstr ""
"Over a thousand years ago, she fell into a deep slumber alongside her master Toyosatomimi no Miko, who became a Shikaisen. Later on, "
"many years earlier, she was revived with Toyosatomimi no Miko and the others at the Hall of Dreams' Great Mausoleum.\n"
"Her way of thinking is relatively old-fashioned, making it hard for her to comprehend many things after a thousand years. Her mixed "
"style of speech with classical and modern grammar can also be difficult to understand.\n"
"As time passed, she slowly adapted to modern life, becoming a girl who seems just a little silly."

#. Name for misc mvz2:marisa
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.name"
msgid "雾雨 魔理沙"
msgstr "Marisa Kirisame"

#. Header for misc mvz2:marisa
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.description"
msgid "一位普通的魔法使，也是<ref=[misc]mvz2:rinnosuke>森近 霖之助</ref>曾经的好友。"
msgstr "An ordinary magician, and also a former good friend of <ref=[misc]mvz2:rinnosuke>Rinnosuke Morichika</ref>."

#. Flavor for misc mvz2:marisa
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.description"
msgid ""
"在幻想乡四处游荡、采集的人类，职业是魔法使（而非种族）。\n"
"曾经和森近 霖之助关系很好，后来也因他的失踪翻遍了整个幻想乡，无果。\n"
"随后她为霖之助立了衣冠冢，隔三岔五就会去纪念一次。"
msgstr ""
"A human who wanders around Gensokyo collecting various items. Her profession is a magician (not the race).\n"
"She was once on very good terms with Rinnosuke Morichika, but after his disappearance, she searched all over Gensokyo for him, but to "
"no avail.\n"
"Afterwards, she built a memorial for Rinnosuke and would visit him every now and then to commemorate him."

#. Name for misc mvz2:miko
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.name"
msgid "丰聪耳 神子"
msgstr "Toyosatomimi no Miko"

#. Header for misc mvz2:miko
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.description"
msgid "日本千年前的大圣人，后来通过尸解法成为了尸解仙，来到了幻想乡。"
msgstr "A great saint from Japan a thousand years ago, who later became a Shikaisen through Shijie method, came to Gensokyo."

#. Properties for misc mvz2:miko
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.description"
msgid "画师：<color=red>三花花</color>"
msgstr "Artist: <color=red>三花花</color>"

#. Flavor for misc mvz2:miko
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.description"
msgid ""
"千年以前，神子诞生在这世界上。年幼的她能听懂所有人的倾诉，并给出一针见血的见解，她自己也因这个传言而被人们奉为圣人。\n"
"后来她开始惧怕、不满人类的有限寿命，听从了<ref=[misc]mvz2:seiga>青娥</ref>的建议，表面推崇佛教，背地里通过道教手段而达到不死的目的。之"
"后她和<ref=[misc]mvz2:futo>物部 布都</ref>、苏我 屠自古一起通过尸解的方法陷入长眠。\n"
"之后在幻想乡又和佛教徒产生了矛盾，被干扰了复活。但随着事态发展，两派之间的关系也有所缓和。\n"
"而这次，她们两者达成合作，一起抵御来自幻想乡外的巨物威胁。"
msgstr ""
"Thousands of years ago, Miko was born into this world. She could understand everyone's feelings and give accurate insights, then she "
"herself was regarded as a saint because of this rumor.\n"
"In time, she became afraid and dissatisfied with the limited lifespan of human beings. Following <ref=[misc]mvz2:seiga>Seiga</ref>'s "
"advice, she advocated Buddhism on the surface while secretly used Taoist methods to achieve immortality. After that, she fell into a "
"long sleep through Shijie method along with <ref=[misc]mvz2:futo>Mononobe no Futo</ref> and Soga no Tojiko.\n"
"Later, she had conflicts with the Buddhists in Gensokyo and her resurrection was interfered with. But as the events unfolded, tensions "
"between the two factions eased.\n"
"And this time, they have joined forces—to stand together against a giant threat from outside Gensokyo."

#. Name for misc mvz2:seiga
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.name"
msgid "霍 青娥"
msgstr "Seiga Kaku"

#. Header for misc mvz2:seiga
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.description"
msgid "一名使用邪术的邪仙。"
msgstr "A wicked hermit using wicked arts."

#. Flavor for misc mvz2:seiga
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.description"
msgid ""
"她本是一位中国古代的普通人类女性，自幼便深深受道教吸引。\n"
"后来她成了婚，却又因为想要成仙而郁郁寡欢。那之后她使用假死的法术欺骗了家人，离开了自己的家。\n"
"最终她也确实成为了仙人，但是她性格邪恶，路途不正，最后成为的是一名邪仙。\n"
"那之后她向<ref=[misc]mvz2:miko>神子</ref>建议了道教，让她信奉了道教，神子一行人也成为了尸解仙。\n"
"据说，她也可以使用许多邪术，包括使用灵符来操纵僵尸。"
msgstr ""
"She was originally an ordinary human woman in ancient China, and she has been deeply attracted to Taoism since childhood.\n"
"She later became married, but then became depressed because she wanted to become a Hermit. After that, she used a spell to fake her "
"death to trick her family and left her home.\n"
"In the end, she did become a Hermit, but she had an evil personality and a twisted path, thus becoming a Wicked Hermit.\n"
"After that, she introduced <ref=[misc]mvz2:miko>Miko</ref> to Taoism, converted her to Taoism, and became a Shikaisen.\n"
"It is said that she is able to use a variety of wicked arts, including using talismans to manipulate zombies."

#. Name for misc mvz2:mysterious_hologram
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.name"
msgid "神秘影像"
msgstr "Mysterious Hologram"

#. Header for misc mvz2:mysterious_hologram
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.description"
msgid "出现在被僵尸包围的<ref=[misc]mvz2:kourindou>香霖堂</ref>的神秘影像，它对史蒂夫发出了威胁。"
msgstr "A mysterious hologram appeared in <ref=[misc]mvz2:kourindou>Kourindou</ref> surrounded by zombies. It threatened Steve."

#. Flavor for misc mvz2:mysterious_hologram
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.description"
msgid "这到底是什么东西？"
msgstr "What the heck is this?"

#. Name for misc mvz2:shou
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.name"
msgid "寅丸 星"
msgstr "Shou Toramaru"

#. Header for misc mvz2:shou
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.description"
msgid "被<ref=[misc]mvz2:byakuren>圣 白莲</ref>选中的虎妖怪，毘沙门天的弟子。"
msgstr "A tiger youkai taken in by <ref=[misc]mvz2:byakuren>Byakuren Hijiri</ref>, and also a disciple of Bishamonten."

#. Flavor for misc mvz2:shou
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.description"
msgid ""
"她本是一只普通的虎妖怪，被圣 白莲选中而成为了毘沙门天的弟子兼化身。\n"
"她和白莲的关系说起来比较复杂。白莲供奉毘沙门天，而她又选择了星作为弟子，也作为毘沙门天的化身。因此白莲实际上也在供奉她自己的弟子。\n"
"星在工作上十分优秀，表面看上去十分冷静而威严，然而其实是个很感性的家伙。\n"
"\n"
"<ref=[misc]mvz2:red_dragon>红龙</ref>出现后，白莲失去了消息，于是星和命莲寺众僧侣商议过后，找到了史蒂夫用来对付空中的"
"<ref=[misc]mvz2:end_ship>末地船</ref>，之后便和村纱（船长）以及史蒂夫踏上了寻找白莲的旅途。"
msgstr ""
"She was originally an ordinary tiger youkai, but was then taken in by Byakuren Hijiri and became a disciple and the avatar of "
"Bishamonten.\n"
"Her relationship with Byakuren is rather complicated. Byakuren worships Bishamonten, and Shou is her disciple, as well as being the "
"avatar of Bishamonten. Thus, Byakuren is essentially worshipping her own disciple.\n"
"Shou performs excellently in her duties. She may look very calm and dignified on the surface, but she is actually a very emotional "
"person.\n"
"\n"
"With the appearance of the <ref=[misc]mvz2:red_dragon>Red Dragon</ref> and the disappearance of Byakuren, Shou discussed with the "
"monks of Myouren Temple and found Steve to deal with the <ref=[misc]mvz2:end_ship>End Ship</ref> in the sky. After that, she, Captain "
"Murasa and Steve set out on a journey to find Byakuren."

#. Name for misc mvz2:nue
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.name"
msgid "封兽 鵺"
msgstr "Nue Houjuu"

#. Header for misc mvz2:nue
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.description"
msgid "命莲寺的妖怪，有着让物体变得无法识别的能力。"
msgstr "A youkai of Myouren Temple, capable of making objects unidentifiable."

#. Flavor for misc mvz2:nue
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.description"
msgid ""
"鵺（yè）是一名神秘的大妖怪，在之后才加入到命莲寺，因此与命莲寺中的其他人并不合群。\n"
"喜欢找乐子、妨碍他人做事，常常会使用自己的能力干扰他人行动。\n"
"被她施加能力的物体，会失去原本的认知特征，在别人眼里会把它视作是自己认为合理的物体——比如飞在空中的奇怪物体，别人会把它看作是飞碟。\n"
"\n"
"然而，在异变发生后，她的性格大变，变得十分消极和恍惚，认为这一切都没有任何意义。\n"
"到底是发生了什么？"
msgstr ""
"Nue is a mysterious great youkai who joined the Myouren Temple later on, so she doesn't fit in well with the others there.\n"
"She enjoys causing mischief and getting in others' way, often using her abilities to interfere with what people are doing.\n"
"Objects affected by her ability lose their original identifiable characteristics, and are perceived by others as whatever they "
"consider most plausible—for example, a strange object flying in the sky would be seen as a flying saucer.\n"
"\n"
"However, after the incident began, her personality changed drastically. She became deeply pessimistic and dazed, believing that "
"nothing mattered anymore.\n"
"What exactly happened?"

#. Name for misc mvz2:sekibanki
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.name"
msgid "赤蛮奇"
msgstr "Sekibanki"

#. Header for misc mvz2:sekibanki
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.description"
msgid "居住在人类村庄的妖怪，拥有让自己的头飞行的能力。"
msgstr "A youkai living in the Human Village, possessing the ability to make her head fly."

#. Flavor for misc mvz2:sekibanki
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.description"
msgid ""
"赤蛮奇伪装成普通人类而居住在人类村庄，在这里过着平凡的生活。\n"
"拥有身首分离，并让头飞行的能力，据说还有非常多的其他头颅可用。\n"
"\n"
"在史蒂夫坠船并离开一座<ref=[misc]mvz2:abandoned_house>废弃的房屋</ref>后，她发现了史蒂夫，并质问史蒂夫为什么会从这间屋子里走出来，然而"
"她却没有透露询问这件事的原因。\n"
"人类村庄发生过什么吗？"
msgstr ""
"Sekibanki disguises herself as an ordinary human in the Human Village, living a simple life there.\n"
"She possesses the ability to detach her head from her body and make it fly. It is said that she can also multiply her heads.\n"
"\n"
"After Steve fell from the ship and came out of an <ref=[misc]mvz2:abandoned_house>abandoned house</ref>, she found Steve and "
"questioned why he had come out of that house, yet she didn't reveal the reason for asking.\n"
"Did something happen in the Human Village?"

#. Name for misc mvz2:byakuren
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.name"
msgid "圣 白莲"
msgstr "Byakuren Hijiri"

#. Header for misc mvz2:byakuren
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.description"
msgid "命莲寺的住持，法力无边的高僧。"
msgstr "The head priest of Myouren Temple, as well as a high monk with limitless magical power."

#. Flavor for misc mvz2:byakuren
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.description"
msgid ""
"白莲的弟弟——命莲，也是一位法力高强的僧人，但最后还是寿限已至，离世了。\n"
"因此白莲开始恐惧死亡，她作为一名研习佛法的僧人，最后竟靠着妖怪的力量达成了不老，成为了一名“妖僧”。\n"
"就这样，白莲成为了一位矛盾的存在。然而，即便被人类发现她与妖怪的秘密，即便遭到封印，她还是一如既往地崇敬着佛法，拯救着众生。\n"
"\n"
"三年前，<ref=[misc]mvz2:the_giant>巨人</ref>和<ref=[misc]mvz2:red_dragon>红龙</ref>同时出现，她被请去除掉红龙。然而却也因此陷入因果，在"
"这三年中被缚上了枷锁。"
msgstr ""
"Byakuren's younger brother, Myouren, was also a monk with immense magical power, but he eventually reached the end of his life and "
"passed away.\n"
"Byakuren therefore began to fear death, and as a monk who studies Buddhism, she ultimately relied on the power of youkai to achieve "
"immortality, becoming a \"youkai monk\".\n"
"Thus, Byakuren became a character with irreconcilable opposites. However, after humans have discovered her secret ties with youkai, "
"and even after being sealed away, she continues to revere Buddhism, to liberate all beings.\n"
"\n"
"Three years ago, the <ref=[misc]mvz2:the_giant>Giant</ref> and the <ref=[misc]mvz2:red_dragon>Red Dragon</ref> appeared at the same "
"time, and she was summoned to eliminate the Red Dragon. However, this kept her bound in the chains of causality for the following "
"three years."

#. Name for almanac group mvz2:areas
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "almanac.group_name"
msgid "地点"
msgstr "Locations"

#. Name for misc mvz2:steves_house
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.name"
msgid "史蒂夫的家"
msgstr "Steve's House"

#. Header for misc mvz2:steves_house
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.description"
msgid "这里是史蒂夫和<ref=[misc]mvz2:villager>村民</ref>住的地方。"
msgstr "Steve and <ref=[misc]mvz2:villager>Crazy Villager</ref> live here."

#. Flavor for misc mvz2:steves_house
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.description"
msgid "史蒂夫不受村庄中的其他人欢迎，于是他们搬到了公路附近的一片广阔平原上，开始了两人独居的生活。"
msgstr ""
"Steve is not welcome by other villagers in the former village, so they moved to a wide plain near the road, and started a new life."

#. Name for misc mvz2:eternal_night_swamp
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.name"
msgid "永夜沼泽"
msgstr "Eternal Night Swamp"

#. Header for misc mvz2:eternal_night_swamp
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.description"
msgid "时间停在万圣夜的被诅咒的沼泽，灵魂术士<ref=[misc]mvz2:orant>欧兰特</ref>居住于此。"
msgstr "Time has stopped on Halloween's eve in this cursed swamp, where <ref=[misc]mvz2:orant>Orant</ref>, the soul sorceress lives.  "

#. Flavor for misc mvz2:eternal_night_swamp
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.description"
msgid "由于欧兰特设置了权限，本条目的部分内容不予显示。"
msgstr "Some contents of this entry will not be displayed due to the restrictions set by Orant."

#. Flavor for misc mvz2:eternal_night_swamp
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.description"
msgid "据说，这里存在着一只沼怪，它只会在雨势特别凶猛时出现。然而真正见到它的人少之又少。"
msgstr ""
"It is said that there is a swamp monster here, which only appears when the rain is particularly fierce. However, very few people "
"actually see it."

#. Name for misc mvz2:dream_world
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.name"
msgid "梦境世界"
msgstr "Dream World"

#. Header for misc mvz2:dream_world
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.description"
msgid "梦境世界是由哆来咪管理的，所有人的梦境所处的地方。"
msgstr "Dream World is the world of everyone's dreams. It is administrated by Doremy."

#. Flavor for misc mvz2:dream_world
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.description"
msgid ""
"所有生物的梦境都互相连通，而梦境世界就是这些梦境所处的地方。\n"
"哆来咪监视并管理着梦境世界，阻止任何企图利用梦境世界干扰现实世界，并破坏梦境世界秩序的人。\n"
"史蒂夫和<ref=[misc]mvz2:villager>村民</ref>来到梦境世界后，这里呈现出了水池和草坪的模样，而这里就是他们的主战场。\n"
"\n"
"这里和宇宙相通，某些宇宙中的天体在这里可能会产生奇特的反应。"
msgstr ""
"The dreams of all creatures are interconnected, and the Dream World is where these dreams are located.\n"
"Doremy watches and manages the Dream World, as well as prevents anyone who attempts to use the Dream World to disrupt its order and "
"interfere with the reality world.\n"
"After Steve and <ref=[misc]mvz2:villager>Villager</ref> came to the dream world, the Dream World showed the shape of a pool lawn, "
"which became their main battlefield.\n"
"\n"
"This place is connected to the universe, and some celestial bodies in the universe may produce peculiar reactions here."

#. Name for misc mvz2:nightmare_world
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.name"
msgid "噩梦世界"
msgstr "Nightmare World"

#. Header for misc mvz2:nightmare_world
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.description"
msgid "噩梦世界是被<ref=[misc]mvz2:nightmare>梦魇</ref>所腐化的<ref=[misc]mvz2:dream_world>梦境世界</ref>。"
msgstr "Nightmare World is the <ref=[misc]mvz2:dream_world>Dream World</ref> corrupted by <ref=[misc]mvz2:nightmare>Nightmare</ref>."

#. Flavor for misc mvz2:nightmare_world
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.description"
msgid ""
"<ref=[misc]mvz2:doremy>哆来咪</ref>曾经在几个月前在梦境世界目击到一只黑马，那就是伪装起来的梦魇。然后，梦魇开始了它的腐化，欺骗梦境所有"
"人的眼睛，直到它诅咒哆来咪。"
msgstr ""
"<ref=[misc]mvz2:doremy>Doremy</ref> had seen a black horse in the Dream World a few months ago, which was Nightmare in disguise. "
"Nightmare then began its corruption, and deceived everyone in the Dream World until it cursed Doremy.\n"
"What you now see is the true appearance of the Dream World."

#. Name for misc mvz2:kourindou
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.name"
msgid "香霖堂"
msgstr "Kourindou"

#. Header for misc mvz2:kourindou
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.description"
msgid "香霖堂是幻想乡中的一处商店，专门售卖一些外界来的稀奇物品。"
msgstr "Kourindou is a shop in Gensokyo that specializes in selling peculiar items from the Outside World."

#. Flavor for misc mvz2:kourindou
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.description"
msgid ""
"香霖堂的原主人名为<ref=[misc]mvz2:rinnosuke>森近 霖之助</ref>，现主人为一位无名的读书妖怪，也称<ref=[misc]mvz2:tokiko>朱鹭子</ref>。\n"
"这里常卖一些幻想乡里少见的，被遗忘的外界物品，比如手机、平板电脑、游戏机什么的。\n"
"霖之助本人是知道这些东西能产生什么作用的，但是他个人并不知道如何正确使用它们，这些东西多半也只能用来当切菜板什么的来使用。\n"
"如今这家店被朱鹭子接替，这些东西的用途估计已经没人知道了。\n"
"\n"
"史蒂夫和<ref=[misc]mvz2:villager>村民</ref>来到了这里，并把这里改造成了他们的作战基地。"
msgstr ""
"The original owner of Kourindou was <ref=[misc]mvz2:rinnosuke>Rinnosuke Morichika</ref>. The current owner is an unnamed book-reading "
"youkai, also known as <ref=[misc]mvz2:tokiko>Tokiko</ref>.\n"
"The place often sells forgotten items from the Outside World that are rarely seen in Gensokyo, such as mobile phones, tablet "
"computers, game consoles, etc.\n"
"Rinnosuke is capable of knowing what the purpose of these things are, but he doesn't know how to use them correctly by himself. In "
"most cases, these things can only be used as cutting boards or something similar.\n"
"Now that the shop has been taken over by Tokiko, it's likely that no one knows what these things are really for anymore.\n"
"\n"
"Steve and <ref=[misc]mvz2:villager>Villager</ref> arrived here and converted the place into their base of operations."

#. Name for misc mvz2:shining_needle_castle
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.name"
msgid "辉针城"
msgstr "Shining Needle Castle"

#. Header for misc mvz2:shining_needle_castle
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.description"
msgid "辉针城是小人族们的城池，在一年前遭到了凋灵骷髅们的入侵。"
msgstr "Shining Needle Castle is where the inchlings reside. It was invaded by wither skeletons one year ago."

#. Flavor for misc mvz2:shining_needle_castle
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.description"
msgid ""
"一座倒挂在天上的城池，其来源相当悠久。\n"
"第一代小人族——一寸法师，从鬼手中夺来万宝槌后，因为它是鬼的秘宝，所以一直不敢过多使用。\n"
"后来小人族的后裔遗忘了这一祖训，过量使用了万宝槌的魔力，导致了这座倒城的出现，小人族也被囚禁在了这里。\n"
"再然后，小人族的末裔——<ref=[misc]mvz2:shinmyoumaru>少名 针妙丸</ref>又受到了<ref=[misc]mvz2:seija>天邪鬼</ref>的蛊惑，用万宝槌在幻想乡"
"惹出了大乱子。\n"
"不知道多少年过去之后，小人们会再次遗忘之前的惨痛教训呢？\n"
"\n"
"顺带一提，天花板——哦不，地板上好像有什么东西在微微发光。"
msgstr ""
"An upside-down castle hanging in the air, its origin can be traced back far.\n"
"When the first generation of inchlings—Issun-boushi—came into possession of the Miracle Mallet, he dared not use it as it was the "
"oni's secret treasure.\n"
"This taboo was forgotten by his descendants, who excessively used the Miracle Mallet's magic, causing the upside-down castle to appear "
"and trapping all the inchlings inside.\n"
"Then, the princess of the inchlings—<ref=[misc]mvz2:shinmyoumaru>Shinmyoumaru Sukuna</ref>—was bewitched by an "
"<ref=[misc]mvz2:seija>amanojaku</ref> and used the Miracle Mallet to incite chaos in Gensokyo.\n"
"I wonder, will the inchlings forget this cruel lesson once more, in the future after many years?\n"
"\n"
"By the way, the ceiling—or floor, rather—seems to have something glowing on it."

#. Name for misc mvz2:hall_of_dreams_great_mausoleum
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.name"
msgid "梦殿大祀庙"
msgstr "Hall of Dreams' Great Mausoleum"

#. Header for misc mvz2:hall_of_dreams_great_mausoleum
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.description"
msgid "<ref=[misc]mvz2:futo>物部 布都</ref>和<ref=[misc]mvz2:miko>丰聪耳 神子</ref>曾复活于幻想乡的地点。"
msgstr ""
"Hall of Dreams' Great Mausoleum is where <ref=[misc]mvz2:miko>Toyosatomimi no Miko</ref> and <ref=[misc]mvz2:futo>Mononobe no Futo</"
"ref> were once resurrected in Gensokyo."

#. Flavor for misc mvz2:hall_of_dreams_great_mausoleum
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.description"
msgid ""
"这地方位于命莲寺地下——这并非神子有意为之，佛教徒们为了防止她的复活，故意将命莲寺建在了它的上方。\n"
"如今神子已经复活，她又将梦殿大祀庙搬到了仙界，而这里则成为了遗址。众多欲望的化身——小神灵仍然徘徊在这里，点缀着这里的黑暗。\n"
"如今，这地方又再次被使用，作为封印<ref=[misc]mvz2:the_giant>巨人</ref>的囚笼。\n"
"\n"
"远处似乎有什么金属工具深深嵌在了墙壁上。"
msgstr ""
"This location is located underneath the Myouren Temple—not by Miko's intention, but in order to prevent her resurrection, the "
"Buddhists deliberately built the Myouren Temple on top of it.\n"
"Now that Miko has been resurrected and moved the Hall of Dreams' Great Mausoleum to Senkai, this site has become a ruin. Yet the "
"embodiment of many desires—Little Divine Spirits—still wanders here, dotting the darkness with their presence.\n"
"Now, this place is being used again, as the cage to seal the <ref=[misc]mvz2:the_giant>Giant</ref>.\n"
"\n"
"There seem to be a metallic tool deeply embedded in the wall in the distance."

#. Name for misc mvz2:end_ship
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.name"
msgid "末地船"
msgstr "End Ship"

#. Header for misc mvz2:end_ship
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.description"
msgid "一艘飞翔于幻想乡天空中的船只，时不时会袭击飞在空中的妖怪们。"
msgstr "A ship flying through the sky of Gensokyo, attacking youkai in the sky every so often."

#. Flavor for misc mvz2:end_ship
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.description"
msgid ""
"原本只是会出现在末地中的飞行船只，不知为何竟出现在了幻想乡的空中。\n"
"奇怪的是，上面没有末影人，有的只是普通的、形似海盗的僵尸。\n"
"更加奇怪的是，里面居然有一颗末影水晶以极快的速度来修复船体。\n"
"这导致任何想破坏这艘船的人，必须要先把内部的末影水晶破坏掉，然而这艘船在落入下风时也会选择以极快的速度逃跑。\n"
"总之，关于这艘船的一切，都是个谜。"
msgstr ""
"Originally only appearing in the End dimension. It is unknown how the ship ended up in the skies of Gensokyo.\n"
"What's strange is that there are no Endermen on board, just regular, pirate-like zombies.\n"
"What's even stranger is that the ship holds an End Crystal inside it that rapidly repairs the ship's hull.\n"
"This means that anyone who dares to take down this ship must first destroy the End Crystal inside it. However, when at a disadvantage, "
"the ship will choose to flee at lightning speed.\n"
"Ultimately, everything about this ship, is a mystery."

#. Name for misc mvz2:palanquin_ship
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.name"
msgid "圣辇船"
msgstr "Palanquin Ship"

#. Header for misc mvz2:palanquin_ship
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.description"
msgid "一艘飞翔于天空中的巨大船只。"
msgstr "A giant ship soaring through the sky."

#. Flavor for misc mvz2:palanquin_ship
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.description"
msgid ""
"圣辇船共有两艘。第一艘圣辇船由<ref=[misc]mvz2:byakuren>圣 白莲</ref>使用法力创造，现如今落地变成了命莲寺。虽说仍然可以再变回船的样子，"
"但有一部分人存在去往魔界的需求，需要乘船去往。倘若随意变换寺庙，会造成一些不便。\n"
"因此白莲又用法力创造了第二艘用于在幻想乡和魔界中来往的圣辇船，作为专门的交通工具。\n"
"如今白莲杳无音讯，星和命莲寺众人商讨后，登上圣辇船，踏上了寻找白莲的路途。\n"
"\n"
"据说幻想乡的高空中有外星人来过的传闻。似乎某些传送信号能把它们引出来？"
msgstr ""
"There are two Palanquin Ships in total. The first was created by <ref=[misc]mvz2:byakuren>Byakuren Hijiri</ref> using magic, which has "
"since landed and been renovated into the Myouren Temple. Although it can still transform back into a ship, some people need to travel "
"to Makai and require a ship to get there. Constantly transforming the temple back and forth into a ship would cause some "
"inconvenience.\n"
"Therefore, Byakuren used her magic to create a second Palanquin Ship for traveling between Gensokyo and Makai as a dedicated means of "
"transportation.\n"
"Now that Byakuren has vanished without a trace, after Shou discussed the matter with the members of Myouren Temple, they boarded the "
"Palanquin Ship and set out on a journey to find Byakuren.\n"
"\n"
"There are rumors that aliens have visited the skies above Gensokyo. It seems that certain teleportation signals might be able to draw "
"them out."

#. Name for almanac group mvz2:starshards
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "almanac.group_name"
msgid "星之碎片"
msgstr "Starshard"

#. Name for misc mvz2:starshard.magic_candy
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.name"
msgid "星之碎片：神奇糖果"
msgstr "Starshard: Magic Candy"

#. Header for misc mvz2:starshard.magic_candy
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.description"
msgid "星之碎片会<b>激发</b>你的器械，触发它们的技能，爆发出器械真正的潜力。"
msgstr "Starshards can <b>evoke</b> your contraptions, and make your contraptions burst with superpower."

#. Flavor for misc mvz2:starshard.magic_candy
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.description"
msgid ""
"未知人士留下了一些记录。\n"
"\n"
"星之记录 其一：\n"
"自那件事以来，每当我沉睡于梦中，总会在深不可测的黑暗中看到一个物体，它闪着星形的光，随之它便离我远去。\n"
"我并不理解这是什么意思。后来即使不在梦中，我也总是能看到类似的物体，这十分反常。\n"
"当我离开不属于我的那片土地时，我在一片朦胧中看到了它变成彩虹色的糖果，这与那些星星十分相似，但我仍不能确定这到底是什么。"
msgstr ""
"Records left by an anonymous person.\n"
"\n"
"Star Record 1:\n"
"Since then, whenever I slept, I would always dream of an object in an unfathomable darkness, it shone in the shape of a star, and then "
"went away from me.\n"
"I didn't understand what it means. Later, even when I wasn't dreaming, I could still often see similar objects, which is very "
"abnormal.\n"
"When I left the land that I don't belong to, I saw a rainbow-colored candy in a haze. It was very similar to those stars, but I was "
"still not sure what they were."

#. Name for misc mvz2:starshard.lucid_dream
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.name"
msgid "星之碎片：清明梦"
msgstr "Starshard: Lucid Dream"

#. Flavor for misc mvz2:starshard.lucid_dream
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.description"
msgid ""
"未知人士留下了一些记录。\n"
"\n"
"星之记录 其二：\n"
"我做了一个很古怪的梦。\n"
"我梦见我在一个满是眼睛的紫色空间中，不断漂浮沉沦。我看到一个黄色头发的少女，持着紫色的阳伞坐在空中。\n"
"她似乎正忙于干自己的事情，并没有发现我的存在。我便如此坠入无底的深渊。\n"
"我睁开眼睛，发现自己正在一片粉色花朵的树环绕的空地上。"
msgstr ""
"Records left by an anonymous person.\n"
"\n"
"Star Record 2:\n"
"I had a very strange dream.\n"
"I dreamed that I was floating and sinking in a purple space full of eyes. I saw a girl with yellow hair sitting in the air with a "
"purple parasol.\n"
"She seemed to be busy with her own business and didn't notice me. Then I fell into a bottomless abyss.\n"
"I opened my eyes and found myself in a plain field, surrounded by trees with pink flowers."

#. Name for misc mvz2:starshard.miracle_mallet
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.name"
msgid "星之碎片：万宝槌"
msgstr "Starshard: Miracle Mallet"

#. Flavor for misc mvz2:starshard.miracle_mallet
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.description"
msgid ""
"未知人士留下了一些记录。\n"
"\n"
"星之记录 其三：\n"
"我来到这里已经三年了。这三年来，我一直独居在某个荒无人烟的地方，常打交道的那位店主似乎也没有发现我的真实身份。\n"
"最近几天，我又做了一个梦。\n"
"我梦见，我的朋友回来了，他亲切地对我微笑着。\n"
"然后，我的家人也因为我带来的东西，终于摆脱了苦难。\n"
"周围的人都称赞我，为我感到高兴。仿佛他们之前从来都没对我做过什么一样。\n"
"多么好的愿望啊。我真的希望，我的这个愿望能够实现。\n"
"……如果真的有能实现这些愿望的东西，那才真的有鬼了。"
msgstr ""
"Records left by an anonymous person.\n"
"\n"
"Star Record 3:\n"
"I have now been here for three years. In these three years, I've been staying alone in a lifeless and deserted place. The shopkeeper I "
"would often talk to has no clue about my true identity.\n"
"I had another dream in these recent days.\n"
"I dreamed that my friend had returned and was warmly smiling at me.\n"
"And my family was finally relieved of suffering because of what I brought back.\n"
"Everyone praised and was happy for me. As if they hadn't done anything to me in the past.\n"
"What a nice wish it would be. From the bottom of my heart, I hope my wish would come true.\n"
". . .As if there would be anything that could truly grant this wish. How ludicrous."

#. Name for misc mvz2:starshard.shinrei
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.name"
msgid "星之碎片：小神灵"
msgstr "Starshard: Little Divine Spirit"

#. Flavor for misc mvz2:starshard.shinrei
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.description"
msgid ""
"未知人士留下了一些记录。\n"
"\n"
"星之记录 其四：\n"
"我想回家。\n"
"我已经不知道多少次产生这个念头了。\n"
"这份欲望不断地膨胀，但是，却没有任何人能够回应它。\n"
"最后也只能什么也不剩下。\n"
"这里固然很美，各种奇特的力量也值得进行研究。\n"
"但是，我真的很想回家。"
msgstr ""
"Records left by an anonymous person.\n"
"\n"
"Star Record 4:\n"
"I want to go home.\n"
"I don't know how many times I have had this thought.\n"
"The desire continues to grow, but no one can respond to it.\n"
"In the end, there is nothing left.\n"
"This place is certainly beautiful, and the various strange powers are worth studying.\n"
"Yet I really want to go home."

#. Name for misc mvz2:starshard.ufo_fragment
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.name"
msgid "星之碎片：飞碟碎片"
msgstr "Starshard: UFO Piece"

#. Flavor for misc mvz2:starshard.ufo_fragment
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.description"
msgid ""
"未知人士留下了一些记录。\n"
"\n"
"星之记录 其五：\n"
"这该死的异变还在持续着。\n"
"我没有任何其他选择，只能与它继续进行斗争。\n"
"我发现我的理智似乎出现了裂痕。\n"
"我看到了本不应看到的东西，然后那幻觉又立即消失了。\n"
"那些飞碟还在天上飞着。\n"
"我到底还能撑多久……？"
msgstr ""
"Records left by an anonymous person.\n"
"\n"
"Star Record 5:\n"
"This damn aberration just keeps going on.\n"
"I have no other choices but to continue fighting it.\n"
"I feel cracks forming in my sanity.\n"
"I saw things I shouldn't have seen, then the hallucinations vanished immediately.\n"
"Those saucers are still flying in the sky.\n"
"How much longer can I hold on...?"

#. Name for almanac group mvz2:important
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "almanac.group_name"
msgid "重要物品"
msgstr "Important Items"

#. Name for misc mvz2:ender_chest
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.name"
msgid "末影箱"
msgstr "Ender Chest"

#. Header for misc mvz2:ender_chest
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.description"
msgid "末影箱可以将<ref=[misc]mvz2:villager>村民</ref>的存货取出来，并让他重新开张商店。"
msgstr "The ender chest allows the <ref=[misc]mvz2:villager>villager</ref> to retrieve his stock and reopen his shop."

#. Flavor for misc mvz2:ender_chest
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.description"
msgid ""
"“打怪就能拿到的末影箱？你从哪儿拿来的？”\n"
"“梦里。”"
msgstr ""
"\"A mob dropped this ender chest? Where'd you get it from?\"\n"
"\"In your dreams.\""

#. Name for misc mvz2:nightmare_box
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.name"
msgid "梦魇魔盒"
msgstr "Nightmare Box"

#. Header for misc mvz2:nightmare_box
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.description"
msgid ""
"梦魇魔盒是将<ref=[misc]mvz2:nightmare>梦魇</ref>的黑魔法收集起来制作而成，并可以使<ref=[misc]mvz2:dream_world>梦境世界</ref>变成"
"<ref=[misc]mvz2:nightmare_world>噩梦世界</ref>的容器。"
msgstr ""
"The Nightmare Box is a container made by collecting dark magic from <ref=[misc]mvz2:nightmare>Nightmare</ref>, and can turn the "
"<ref=[misc]mvz2:dream_world>Dream World</ref> into <ref=[misc]mvz2:nightmare_world>Nightmare World</ref>."

#. Flavor for misc mvz2:nightmare_box
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.description"
msgid "梦魇魔盒中不再包含任何有害魔力，它所能做的只有将梦境世界投影成为噩梦世界了。"
msgstr "The Nightmare Box no longer contains any harmful magic. All it can do now is projecting the Nightmare World's image."

#. Name for misc mvz2:gensokyo_map
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.name"
msgid "幻想乡地图"
msgstr "Gensokyo Map"

#. Header for misc mvz2:gensokyo_map
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.description"
msgid "<ref=[misc]mvz2:villager>村民</ref>绘制的幻想乡地图。"
msgstr "A map of Gensokyo drawn by the <ref=[misc]mvz2:villager>Villager</ref>."

#. Flavor for misc mvz2:gensokyo_map
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.description"
msgid ""
"没有比例尺，没有方向标，只靠图例和注记找路的地图。\n"
"能用这张地图的也是神人了。"
msgstr ""
"A map with neither scale nor compass. The only way to find the way is with pictures and markings.\n"
"Being able to use this map is a feat in itself."

#. Name for misc mvz2:obsidian_first_aid
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.name"
msgid "黑曜石修复术"
msgstr "Obsidian First Aid"

#. Header for misc mvz2:obsidian_first_aid
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.description"
msgid "用于修复防御性器械的技术。"
msgstr "A technique used to repair defensive contraptions."

#. Properties for misc mvz2:obsidian_first_aid
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.description"
msgid "效果：<color=red>可以直接在<tag id=\"mvz2:defensive\" />防御性器械上放置同样的器械以为其恢复所有耐久，而无需挖掉器械</color>"
msgstr ""
"Effect: <color=red><tag id=\"mvz2:defensive\"/>Defensive contraptions can be placed directly on the same contraptions to restore all "
"toughness, without the need to be dug up</color>"

#. Flavor for misc mvz2:obsidian_first_aid
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.description"
msgid ""
"“你的修复术好像和我的不太一样，你这是怎么修的？”\n"
"“只要你手速够快，就可以在一瞬间内挖掉器械，再重新放一个。”\n"
"“？”"
msgstr ""
"\"Your repair technique seems to be different from mine, how did you do it?\"\n"
"\"If your hands are fast enough, you can dig the contraption up and place a new one in an instant.\"\n"
"\"?\""

#. Name for almanac group mvz2:lore
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "almanac.group_name"
msgid "剧情"
msgstr "Lore"

#. Name for misc mvz2:blurred_note
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.name"
msgid "模糊的字条"
msgstr "Blurred Note"

#. Header for misc mvz2:blurred_note
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.description"
msgid "<ref=[misc]mvz2:dream_world>梦境世界</ref>捡到的一张纸条，因为身处梦境的原因，无法查看其内容。"
msgstr "A note found in the <ref=[misc]mvz2:dream_world>dream world</ref>. It cannot be viewed due to being in a dream."

#. Flavor for misc mvz2:blurred_note
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.description"
msgid "？？？"
msgstr "???"

#. Flavor for misc mvz2:blurred_note
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.description"
msgid ""
"在<ref=[misc]mvz2:shining_needle_castle>辉针城</ref>结束后的<ref=[misc]mvz2:kourindou>香霖堂</ref>，<ref=[misc]mvz2:villager>村民</ref>"
"曾将这张纸条拿出去看了一眼，然而却又把它慌张地收了起来。"
msgstr ""
"After the end of journey in <ref=[misc]mvz2:shining_needle_castle>Shining Needle Castle</ref>, <ref=[misc]mvz2:villager>Villager</ref> "
"once took out this note and glanced at it in <ref=[misc]mvz2:kourindou>Kourindou</ref>, but then hastily put it away."

#. Name for misc mvz2:grave_in_dream
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.name"
msgid "梦境中的坟墓"
msgstr "Grave in Dream"

#. Header for misc mvz2:grave_in_dream
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.description"
msgid "<ref=[misc]mvz2:kourindou>哆来咪</ref>提到史蒂夫曾在梦中看到过一座坟墓，而且是史蒂夫很小时候就已经见过的墓。"
msgstr ""
"<ref=[misc]mvz2:kourindou>Doremy</ref> mentioned that Steve had seen a grave in his dream, and it was the one Steve had seen when he "
"was very young."

#. Flavor for misc mvz2:grave_in_dream
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.description"
msgid ""
"史蒂夫从一开始便没有父母，他不知不觉中被转移到村庄，被<ref=[misc]mvz2:villager>戴夫</ref>所抚养。\n"
"史蒂夫并不是和村民一样的方块生物，因此常常受到歧视和嘲笑，史蒂夫也因此特别想知道自己的父母是谁。\n"
"似乎，这个谜就要从这场冒险中解开了。"
msgstr ""
"Steve had no parents from the very start of his life. He was unknowingly transferred to the village and was raised by "
"<ref=[misc]mvz2:villager>Dave</ref>.\n"
"Steve was not a blocky creature like the Villager, so he was often discriminated against and ridiculed, while wanting to know who his "
"parents were.\n"
"It seems that this mystery will be solved in this adventure."

#. Name for misc mvz2:explosion_before_3_years
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.name"
msgid "三年前的爆炸"
msgstr "Explosion 3 years ago"

#. Header for misc mvz2:explosion_before_3_years
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.description"
msgid "在三年前，幻想乡内曾经发生过一起巨大的爆炸。"
msgstr "Three years ago, a huge explosion occurred in Gensokyo."

#. Flavor for misc mvz2:explosion_before_3_years
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.description"
msgid ""
"根据<ref=[misc]mvz2:shinmyoumaru>针妙丸</ref>所说，三年前，城下面的某处似乎发生过爆炸，然后这些方块怪物就开始慢慢出现了。\n"
"后来<ref=[misc]mvz2:shining_needle_castle>辉针城</ref>内产生的凋灵骷髅可能也是这件事所导致的。"
msgstr ""
"According to <ref=[misc]mvz2:shinmyoumaru>Shinmyoumaru</ref>, there seemed to be an explosion somewhere under the Castle, and these "
"blocky monsters started to appear.\n"
"This incident may also cause the wither skeletons that appeared in <ref=[misc]mvz2:shining_needle_castle>Shining Needle Castle</ref> "
"later."

#. Name for misc mvz2:two_travelers
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.name"
msgid "两位旅人"
msgstr "Two Travelers"

#. Header for misc mvz2:two_travelers
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.description"
msgid "在四年前，曾有两个旅人来到幻想乡。"
msgstr "Four years ago, two travelers arrived in Gensokyo."

#. Flavor for misc mvz2:two_travelers
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.description"
msgid ""
"据说一位身材娇小，且十分聪慧。另一位好像很擅长和机械打交道。\n"
"他们来到这里，与这里的许多人类和妖怪都交流过，并在这里行商，带来一些从没见过的东西。\n"
"但是，不久之后，异变就发生了。并且他们两个再也没有出现在幻想乡过。"
msgstr ""
"It was said that one was petite and exceptionally intelligent, while the other seemed highly skilled with machinery.\n"
"They interacted with many humans and youkai in the land, engaged in trade, and introduced never-before-seen goods.\n"
"However, shortly afterward, the incident occurred. Since then, neither of them has been seen in Gensokyo again."

#. Name for misc mvz2:murder
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.name"
msgid "凶杀"
msgstr "Murder"

#. Header for misc mvz2:murder
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.description"
msgid "三年前，幻想乡中发生过一场凶杀案。"
msgstr "Three years ago, there was a murder case in the Gensokyo."

#. Flavor for misc mvz2:murder
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.description"
msgid "<ref=[misc]mvz2:futo>布都</ref>无意间透露了这件事。"
msgstr "<ref=[misc]mvz2:futo>Futo</ref> accidentally revealed this."

#. Flavor for misc mvz2:murder
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.description"
msgid "细节尚不知情。"
msgstr "The details are still unknown."

#. Name for misc mvz2:abandoned_house
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.name"
msgid "废弃的房屋"
msgstr "Abandoned House"

#. Header for misc mvz2:abandoned_house
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.description"
msgid "人类村庄中一座废弃的房屋。"
msgstr "An abandoned house in the Human Village."

#. Flavor for misc mvz2:abandoned_house
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.description"
msgid ""
"史蒂夫从<ref=[misc]mvz2:palanquin_ship>圣辇船</ref>中坠落时，被<ref=[misc]mvz2:seija>鬼人 正邪</ref>救到了这处房屋中。\n"
"在他出来之后，遭到了<ref=[misc]mvz2:sekibanki>赤蛮奇</ref>的质问，问他为什么会从这间屋子里出来。\n"
"然而具体发生了什么，史蒂夫并不知情。\n"
"这间屋子发生过什么事情吗？"
msgstr ""
"When Steve fell from the <ref=[misc]mvz2:palanquin_ship>Palanquin Ship</ref>, he was rescued by <ref=[misc]mvz2:seija>Seija Kijin</"
"ref> and brought to this house.\n"
"After he came out, he was questioned by <ref=[misc]mvz2:sekibanki>Sekibanki</ref>, who asked him why he had come out of this house.\n"
"However, Steve had no idea what actually happened.\n"
"Did something happen in this house?"

#. Name for misc mvz2:visitor_which_finding_child
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.name"
msgid "寻找孩子的访客"
msgstr "A Visitor Looking for the Visitor's Child"

#. Header for misc mvz2:visitor_which_finding_child
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.description"
msgid "<ref=[misc]mvz2:byakuren>白莲</ref>透露，四年前，曾有一位访客来访，寻找自己的孩子。"
msgstr "<ref=[misc]mvz2:byakuren>Byakuren</ref> revealed that four years ago, a visitor had come looking for the visitor's child."

#. Flavor for misc mvz2:visitor_which_finding_child
#: Almanac meta file
msgctxt "misc.description"
msgid ""
"史蒂夫解决掉<ref=[misc]mvz2:red_dragon>红龙</ref>的问题后，白莲告诉他，四年前曾有一位访客来访命莲寺。\n"
"那位访客自称灯兰 樱，为了寻找自己的孩子而来。\n"
"在寻子无果后，那位访客便再也没有出现过。不过白莲对于这位访客的存在却仍然抱有乐观态度。"
msgstr ""
"After the resolution with the <ref=[misc]mvz2:red_dragon>Red Dragon</ref>, Byakuren told Steve that four years ago, a visitor had come "
"to Myouren Temple.\n"
"The visitor claimed to be Sakura Touran and had come in search of the visitor's child.\n"
"After failing to find the child, the visitor never appeared again. However, Byakuren remained optimistic about the presence of this "
"visitor."

